const e=[{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"2Silent",uid:1248}],end:"1785163500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785200400",start:"1785132000",title:"Monday",uid:32},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785160800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2799}],pathSegment:"2silent",title:"2Silent",uid:1248},biography:"<p>Whoever says a duo can’t shake the walls hasn't cross paths with Sascha Buchs and Darren Beutler. The two multi-talented Swiss musicians started their careers traditionally on drums and guitar, but quickly realized: we both want to be front and center on the mic! No sooner said than done - trading off flawless vocal harmonies, <i>2Silent</i> has been serving up Modern Rock that is anything but quiet. For their brand-new, hard-hitting 10-track album “Where Roses Weep”, they brought in none other than Grammy-nominated producer Romesh Dodangoda (Bring Me The Horizon), who gave their epic anthems and massive riffs the perfect widescreen, cinematic finish. With nearly half a million Spotify streams under their belt, these guys are blasting across the border to prove that their bombastic sound doesn't just hit hard in headphones. These chart-topping Swiss powerhouses are ready to take you by storm!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wer behauptet, dass ein Duo nicht die Wände wackeln lassen kann, hat die Rechnung ohne Sascha Buchs und Darren Beutler gemacht. Die beiden Schweizer Multitalente starteten ihre Karrieren zwar brav an Drums und Gitarre, stellten aber schnell fest: Wir wollen&nbsp;beide nach vorne ans Mikrofon! Gesagt, getan - im perfekten vokalen Doppelpass servieren 2silent seither modernen Rock, der so gar nicht leise ist. Für ihr brandneues 10-Track-Brett “Where Roses Weep” haben sie sich keinen Geringeren als den Grammy-nominierten Produzenten Romesh Dodangoda (Bring Me the Horizon) geholt, der den epischen Hymnen und fetten Riffs den perfekten Breitwand-Anstrich verpasst hat. Mit fast einer halben Million Spotify-Streams im Rücken kommen die Jungs jetzt über die Grenze geschossen, um zu beweisen, dass ihr bombastischer Sound nicht nur auf Kopfhörern knallt. Diese beiden chartstürmenden Eidgenossen werden euch im Sturm erobern!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/2silent/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=joWd9TgF7ak",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"2silent_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/2silent_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37046}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4764,uri:"https://www.2silent.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4765,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/twosilent/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3pT3euMjE4uLu0CKwfRApA",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/0/csm_2silent_26_426197e02d.jpg",uid:1726},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"5th Avenue",uid:452}],end:"1753642800",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753664400",start:"1753596000",title:"Sunday",uid:30},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1753639200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2538},{artists:[{title:"5th Avenue",uid:452}],end:"1785333600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785330000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2636}],pathSegment:"5th-avenue",title:"5th Avenue",uid:452},biography:"<p>Just in time for the 35th anniversary of W:O:A, we are celebrating the 10th show of one of the first and most loyal bands on the Holy Ground: 5TH AVENUE are coming to Wacken in 2026! The cult rockers from Hamburg will be performing the highlights of their discography, which dates back to the 90s. But even in recent years, Oliver Peters and co. have been as active as ever and have proven with ‘Machine Gun’ and ‘All The Leaves Are Falling’ that their story is far from over. All the more: a night-time stroll along North Germany's 5th Avenue has rarely been so entertaining, exciting and authentic.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Pünktlich zum 35. W:O:A-Jubiläum feiern wir die 10. Show einer der ersten und treusten Bands auf dem Holy Ground: 5th Avenue kommen 2026 nach Wacken! Die Hamburger Kultrocker geben die Highlights ihrer Diskografie zum Besten, welche bis in die 90er zurück reicht. Doch auch in den letzten Jahren sind Oliver Peters und co. umtriebig wie eh und je und haben mit „Machine Gun“ und „All The Leaves Are Falling“ bewiesen, dass ihre Geschichte noch lange nicht auserzählt ist. Im Gegenteil: Ein Nachtspaziergang entlang der norddeutschen 5th Avenue war selten so unterhaltsam, prickelnd und authentisch.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/5th-avenue/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CN0vbL_MEcI&list=RDCN0vbL_MEcI&start_radio=1",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"5th_Avenue25.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2025/5th_Avenue25.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36359}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4548,uri:"https://5thavenue-hamburg.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4549,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/5thAvenueHamburg"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4550,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/5th_avenue_hamburg"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1biWH85uIGqR8Nj7oKU5J9",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/f/csm_5th_Avenue25_9d44c97386.jpg",uid:1644},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"9mm Headshot",uid:1196}],end:"1785427200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785424500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2690}],pathSegment:"9mm-headshot",title:"9mm Headshot",uid:1196},biography:`<p>They’re back — and properly so.</p>\r
<p>With „Sex, Bier &amp; Assi-Rock“, 9mm Headshot&nbsp;aren’t just bringing a brand-new&nbsp;album&nbsp;to&nbsp;the Holy Ground. They’re&nbsp;delivering a manifesto cast in Metal&nbsp;that&nbsp;perfectly sums up&nbsp;the German four-piece: provocative&nbsp;lyrics and uncompromising&nbsp;Rock’n’Roll. The time has&nbsp;come&nbsp;for&nbsp;their&nbsp;return&nbsp;to W:O:A.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Sie sind zurück, und zwar so richtig. Mit „Sex, Bier und Assi-Rock“ hat die Band nicht nur ein neues Album für den Holy Ground im Gepäck, sondern außerdem ein Manifest in Metall gegossen, das den deutschen Vierer perfekt beschreibt. Provokante Texte, kompromissloser Rock’n’Roll - die Zeit ist reif für eine Rückkehr von 9mm Headshot auf das W:O:A.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/9mm-headshot/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GKNviam4HOI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"9mm_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/9mm_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36360}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4551,uri:"https://www.9mmheadshot.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4552,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/9mmheadshot/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4553,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/9mmheadshot/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0hYxXnnFEBBK8JDab4lIEM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/c/csm_9mm_26_b14cffe6c2.jpg",uid:1645},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ad Infinitum",uid:611}],end:"1691064900",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691110800",start:"1691042400",title:"Thursday",uid:14},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1691062200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:969},{artists:[{title:"Ad Infinitum",uid:611}],end:"1785605400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785601800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2779}],pathSegment:"ad-infinitum",title:"Ad Infinitum",uid:611},biography:"<p>AD INFINITUM ist eine Band, mit der man bis ins Unendliche der symphonischen Metal-Welt und darüber hinaus gehen kann. Dass das bestens funktioniert, haben die vier Schweizer um Sängerin Melissa Bonny bereits 2023 auf dem W:O:A bewiesen und kehren zum Festivaljubiläum zurück auf den Holy Ground. Mit den Highlights ihrer ersten drei Alben „Chapter I, II, III“ und dem aktuellen Longplayer „Abyss“ präsentieren sie die perfekte Zusammenstellung für eine bombastische Show irgendwo zwischen Growls und Klargesang, harten Riffs und orchestralen Eskapaden, sowie verwunschener Märchenstunde und ungeschönter Realität.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>AD INFINITUM is a band that takes you on a journey into the infinite world of Symphonic Metal and beyond. The four Swiss musicians, led by singer Melissa Bonny, proved that this formula works perfectly at W:O:A in 2023 and are returning to the Holy Ground for the festival's anniversary. With highlights from their first three albums ‘Chapter I, II, III’ and their current longplayer ‘Abyss’, they present the perfect mixture for a bombastic show somewhere between growls and clean vocals, hard riffs and orchestral escapades, as well as enchanted fairy tales and unvarnished reality.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ad-infinitum/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=POwK89M7PH8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ad_infinitum_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ad_infinitum_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35772}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4503,uri:"https://www.adinfinitumofficial.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4504,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/AdInfinitumMusic/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4505,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/adinfinitumofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2X3qFQFHkm1sOGo5ppIoSD",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/a/csm_ad_infinitum_26_cb9028b792.jpg",uid:1630},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Australien",shortNameDe:"Australien",shortNameEn:"Australia",uid:14}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Airbourne",uid:5}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:77},{artists:[{title:"Airbourne",uid:5}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:395},{artists:[{title:"Airbourne",uid:5}],end:"1785602700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785598200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2745}],pathSegment:"airbourne",title:"Airbourne",uid:5},biography:"<p>We are throwing the party of the year every summer, and who cannot be missed? That's right – the good-vibes crew who bring not only hard-hitting rock ’n’ roll but also the right attitude and serious drinking stamina.<br />Of course, we're talking about Australia's finest, the O’Keeffe brothers – Airbourne! For 22 years, the band has basically been a part of the continent’s cultural heritage and has embraced the virtues of raspy vocals and pure fight riffs – long represented only by AC/DC and Rose Tattoo – better than almost anyone else.&nbsp;Welcome back to the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Wir schmeißen jeden Sommer eine Riesenparty und wer darf da sicherlich nicht fehlen? Richtig – die Gute-Laune-Truppe, die nicht nur beinharten Rock’n’Roll, sondern auch die richtige Attitude und Trinkfestigkeit mitbringt.</p>\r
<p>Die Rede ist von Australia’s Finest, den O’Keeffe Brüdern, Airbourne! Seit 22 Jahren gehört die Band praktisch zum Kulturgut des Kontinents und hat die lange einzig von AC/DC und Rose Tattoo verkörperten Tugenden von Reibeisen-Stimme und astreinen Fight-Riffs besser verinnerlicht als kaum jemand anderes.</p>\r
<p>Willkommen zurück auf dem Holy Ground.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/airbourne/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/@Airbournerock",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Airborn-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Airborn-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34833}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4319,uri:"https://airbournerock.com/home"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4320,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/airbournerock"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4321,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/airbourne/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6urzdpGY5yUimWZsgJUoTb",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/e/csm_Airborn-WOA26_24e9c1f588.jpg",uid:1577},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Frankreich",shortNameDe:"Frankreich",shortNameEn:"France",uid:72}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Alcest",uid:1197}],end:"1785542400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785538800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2726}],pathSegment:"alcest",title:"Alcest",uid:1197},biography:"<p>Picture someone dumping a cloud of shoegaze fog straight into a black‑metal blizzard right in the middle of the muddy Wacken field. That’s basically Alcest. Neige’s project has been crafting shimmering walls of sound where blast beats meet guitar lines that glow like northern lights. With “Les Chants de l’aurore” they bring that dreamy storm to Wacken. Don’t be surprised if the circle pit pauses for a second… just to spin even harder.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Stell dir vor, jemand kippt Shoegaze-Nebel über einen Black‑Metal‑Blizzard – mitten auf dem matschigen Wacken-Acker. Genau da wohnen Alcest. Das Projekt von Neige baut seit Jahren Klangwelten aus Frost, Melancholie und schimmernden Gitarren. Blastbeats treffen auf Soundflächen wie Nordlichter. Mit „Les Chants de l’aurore“ bringen sie diese hypnotische Mischung nach Wacken. Könnte der Moment sein, in dem selbst der Circle Pit kurz innehält – bevor er wieder losdreht.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/alcest/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zLzBcfX5Fwg&list=RDzLzBcfX5Fwg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"alcest_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/alcest_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36361}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4554,uri:"https://alcestmusic.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4555,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alcest.official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4556,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alcestofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0d5ZwMtCer8dQdOPAgWhe7",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/2/csm_alcest_26_ca67b9d832.jpg",uid:1646},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Alestorm",uid:569}],end:"1691249400",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1691245800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1035},{artists:[{title:"Alestorm",uid:569}],end:"1691259300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1691256600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1406},{artists:[{title:"Alestorm",uid:569}],end:"1785628800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785625200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2747}],pathSegment:"alestorm",title:"Alestorm",uid:569},biography:"<p>Some bands write anthems – Alestorm write curses soaked in rum.<br />They pour Speed Folk, Power Metal, and lunacy into one boiling cauldron and grin when it spills.&nbsp;<i>“Seventh Rum of a Seventh Rum”</i> isn’t an album, it’s a drinking oath. Between keytar assaults and shanty choirs hides a pirate heart with a punk sneer. Their shows aren’t gigs, they’re storms that know rhythm. If you see them sober, you missed the point.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Manche Bands schreiben Hymnen – Alestorm schreiben Flüche in Rum.<br />Sie kippen Folk, Power Metal und Wahnsinn in denselben Kessel und lachen, wenn’s überkocht.&nbsp;<i>“Seventh Rum of a Seventh Rum”</i> ist weniger Album als Trinkgelübde. Zwischen Keytar-Attacken und Shanty-Chören liegt echter Seemannsspaß mit anarchischem Unterton.&nbsp;Ihre Shows sind kein Konzert, sondern ein Sturm, der tanzen kann. Wer sie nüchtern erlebt, hat das Konzept nicht verstanden.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/alestorm/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gS-CtzmQHtc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"alestorm_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/alestorm_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35110}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4357,uri:"https://alestorm.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4358,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alestormband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4359,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alestormofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3OpqU68JpZlzvjAJj3B2Da",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/d/csm_alestorm_26_9ddf45fa2e.jpg",uid:1589},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Alfahanne",uid:1184}],end:"1785535200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785531600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2742}],pathSegment:"alfahanne",title:"Alfahanne",uid:1184},biography:`<p>Some things just go perfectly together: beer and barbecue, Holger and Thomas, W:O:A and you!</p>\r
<p>And then there are those connections that are just a little extra special — like the pitch-black fusion of Rock ’n’ Roll and Black Metal that Alfahanne unleash on stage. As tradition demands, this five-piece hails from Sweden, effortlessly blending the signature sounds of that region’s heaviest styles. A feast for the senses — especially your ears!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Manche Sachen gehen besonders gut zusammen: Bier und Grill, Holger und Thomas, das W:O:A und ihr! Und dann gibt es diese Verbindung, die sind noch ein bisschen extra special. Wie zum Beispiel der pechschwarze Mix aus Rock’n’Roll und Black Metal, den Alfahanne auf die Piste bringen. Wie es der gute Ton erwartet, stammt der Fünfer aus Schweden und vereint spielend die Elemente der bekanntesten Stile alles Hartmetallischem aus dieser Ecke der Welt. Ein Fest für alle Sinne – vor allem aber die Ohren!&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/alfahanne/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLR-kBSvRG-bumCw926u-gA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"alfahanne_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/alfahanne_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35765}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4478,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alfahanneofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4479,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alfahanneofficial_"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0DhxBb7HKgksv0K7p3cIFj",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/6/csm_alfahanne_26_9c1f0784c4.jpg",uid:1622},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Alien Ant Farm",uid:1198}],end:"1785409200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785405600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2654}],pathSegment:"alien-ant-farm",title:"Alien Ant Farm",uid:1198},biography:"<p>Alien Ant Farm prove that sometimes all you need is a killer rock groove and a chorus that sticks like duct tape. Sure, everybody knows the “Smooth Criminal” cover. But live the Californians bring way more than nostalgia: crunchy riffs, sing‑along hooks and the kind of bounce that wakes up even the sleepiest Wacken crowd.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Alien Ant Farm sind der Beweis, dass ein guter Rocksong manchmal einfach ein verdammt guter Rocksong sein muss. Grooves, Hooks und jede Menge Energie – irgendwo zwischen Alternative Rock, Nu Metal und Festivalparty. Klar, das „Smooth Criminal“-Cover kennt jeder. Aber live liefern die Kalifornier viel mehr als Nostalgie: Riffs, Mitsing-Refrains und genug Bewegung, um selbst den staubigsten Wacken-Morgen wachzurütteln.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/alien-ant-farm/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CDl9ZMfj6aE&list=RDCDl9ZMfj6aE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"alien_ant_farm_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/alien_ant_farm_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36362}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4557,uri:"https://alienantfarm.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4558,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alienantfarm"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4559,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alienantfarmofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6TZdvF1kFzwnQLgHQynzsO",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/b/csm_alien_ant_farm_26_f4695d8f52.jpg",uid:1647},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Spanien",shortNameDe:"Spanien",shortNameEn:"Spain",uid:65}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1753731000",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753750800",start:"1753682400",title:"Monday",uid:29},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753729200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2279},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1754163000",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754182800",start:"1754114400",title:"Saturday",uid:27},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1754161200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2338},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1753817400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753837200",start:"1753768800",title:"Tuesday",uid:28},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753815600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2353},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1753903800",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753902000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2373},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1753990200",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753988400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2444},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1754076600",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754096400",start:"1754028000",title:"Friday",uid:26},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1754074800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2505},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1753967700",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1753965000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2555},{artists:[{title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229}],end:"1785327300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785324600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2635}],pathSegment:"alien-rockin-explosion",title:"Alien Rockin Explosion",uid:229},biography:"<p>The Holy Ground is&nbsp;about&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;visited&nbsp;by&nbsp;extraterrestrials&nbsp;once&nbsp;again. Don’t&nbsp;worry&nbsp;though — these&nbsp;aliens&nbsp;arrive in peace and with a whole&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;good&nbsp;vibes. As longtime&nbsp;members&nbsp;of&nbsp;Maschine’s Late Night Show, the&nbsp;Spanish&nbsp;Rock’n’Roll invaders will take&nbsp;us on a trip&nbsp;to&nbsp;another&nbsp;galaxy.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Der Holy Ground wird wieder einmal extraterrestrisch heimgesucht. Aber keine Sorge diese Aliens kommen mit ganz viel guter Laune und definitiv in Frieden. Als mittlerweile fast schon zum Inventar gehörender Kapelle aus Maschines Late Night Show werden uns die spanischen Außerirdischen mit ihrem Rock’n’Roll in eine andere Galaxy mitnehmen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/alien-rockin-explosion/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gQihYmh-Tk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"alien_rockin_explosion_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/alien_rockin_explosion_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36363}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4560,uri:"https://alienrockinexplosion.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4561,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alienrockinexplosion/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4562,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alienrockinexplosion/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2GgqtN4rfpLZosbLI3PnpP",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/4/csm_alien_rockin_explosion_26_dba5a44bfe.jpg",uid:1648},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Allt",uid:1156}],end:"1785600000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785597300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2785}],pathSegment:"allt",title:"Allt",uid:1156},biography:"<p>For every true Wackener, it’s crystal clear – music is what connects us all. There’s hardly anything we value more. Allt from Sweden share this belief and not just because of their name. They fit perfectly into the next mosh pit.<br />A strong-willed blend of djent, metalcore, and progressive elements meets dystopian storytelling in Allt’s music, creating a unique sonic identity. This five-piece will definitely be a valuable addition to the history books of the Holy Ground – a Wacken debut you should keep an eye on.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Für jeden Wacken Fan ist die Sache vollkommen klar – Musik, das ist das, was uns alle verbindet. Kaum etwas ist uns ein höheres Gut. Allt aus Schweden teilen diese Ansicht, nicht nur aufgrund ihres Namens und passen deswegen wie die Faust aufs Auge im nächsten Moshpit. Eine charakterstarke Mischung aus Djent, Metalcore und progressiven Elementen trifft bei Allt auf dystopische Erzählungen und kreiert ein eigenes Soundgewand. Der Fünfer wird definitiv eine Bereicherung für die Geschichtsbücher des Holy Ground werden – eine Wacken-Premiere, die ihr im Auge haben solltet.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/allt/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnIeVbou8giGgw9NtjwSkGw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Allt-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Allt-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34834}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4322,uri:"https://shop.alltband.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4323,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/alltofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4324,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/alltband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6YRr0btzGqfQ5K7r23qjEM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/f/csm_Allt-WOA26_20072966da.jpg",uid:1578},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Anaal Nathrakh",uid:1138}],end:"1785444300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785440700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2678}],pathSegment:"anaal-nathrakh",title:"Anaal Nathrakh",uid:1138},biography:`<p>Anaal&nbsp;nathrakh, urthvas&nbsp;bethad, dokhjel&nbsp;djenve.</p>\r
<p>Speak&nbsp;this&nbsp;incantation on a dark&nbsp;night, precisely at 3 a.m., the&nbsp;witching&nbsp;hour, and perhaps a band from Birmingham will appear in your&nbsp;room.</p>\r
<p>The invocation&nbsp;borrowed&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;movie Excalibur is&nbsp;the&nbsp;namesake&nbsp;of&nbsp;the British Extreme Metal&nbsp;veterans&nbsp;Anaal&nbsp;Nathrakh, who will seize&nbsp;you&nbsp;with&nbsp;their&nbsp;dark&nbsp;riffs and gripping&nbsp;sounds.</p>\r
<p>Do you&nbsp;dare? Then&nbsp;join&nbsp;our ritual!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Anaal&nbsp;nathrakh, urthvas&nbsp;bethad, dokhjel&nbsp;djenve. Sprecht diesen Zauberspruch in einer dunklen Nacht um genau 3 Uhr Nachts zur Teufelsstunde und eine Band aus Birmingham wird vielleicht bei euch im Zimmer erscheinen.</p>\r
<p>Die aus dem Film Excalibur entliehene Beschwörungsformel ist Namensgeber für die britischen Extreme-Metal Veteranen Anaal&nbsp;Natrhakh, die euch mit ihren dunklen Riffs und einnehmenden Sounds ergreifen werden. Traut ihr euch? Dann erscheint zu unserem Ritual!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/anaal-nathrakh/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kzQpiJjdprQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"AnaalNathrakh1.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/AnaalNathrakh1.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35145}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4252,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Anaalnathrakhofficial/?locale=de_DE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4253,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/anaalnathrakh/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4431,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/user/anaalnathrakhtv"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7vrrJ5YlL3I8XUrh1ktGJV",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/6/csm_AnaalNathrakh1_1706ff6610.jpg",uid:1553},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Spanien",shortNameDe:"Spanien",shortNameEn:"Spain",uid:65}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Angelus Apatrida",uid:120}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:4},{artists:[{title:"Angelus Apatrida",uid:120}],end:"1785595500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785592800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2770}],pathSegment:"angelus-apatrida",title:"Angelus Apatrida",uid:120},biography:`<p>The homeless angels return to the warm embrace of the Holy Ground!</p>\r
<p>After six long years away, Spain’s demolition crew is back at Wacken – toolbox packed with everything that makes the place shake.</p>\r
<p>With over 25 years of experience, the four Thrashers from Albacete know exactly how to brick you in with razor-sharp riffs – just so you can mosh your way back out moments later.</p>\r
<p>Even the Wacken Chamber of Industry and Commerce gives the thumbs up!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Die heimatlosen Engel kehren zurück in den warmen Schoß des Holy Ground. Nach sechs langen Jahren der Abwesenheit kehrt das spanische Abrissunternehmen zurück nach Wacken – die Werkzeugkiste gut bestückt mit allem, was ordentlich knallt. Mit einem Vierteljahrhundert Banderfahrung wissen die vier Thrasher aus Albacete genau, wann sie euch mit ihren atemraubenden Riffs schön ein mörteln müssen. Nur damit ihr euch selbst wenige Augenblicke später wieder rausmosht. Die Wackener Industrie und Handelskammer hebt den Daumen!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/angelus-apatrida/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xb50ooBETEc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"angelus_apatrida_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/angelus_apatrida_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35131}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4391,uri:"https://angelusapatrida.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4392,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/angelusapatrida"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4393,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/angelusapatrida"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4394,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/angelusapatrida"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3bnPBquC93vbHmamojAf59",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/0/csm_angelus_apatrida_26_0bf97316dd.jpg",uid:1599},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Animals as Leaders",uid:1199}],end:"1785519900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785517200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2717}],pathSegment:"animals-as-leaders",title:"Animals as Leaders",uid:1199},biography:"<p>When Animals As Leaders start playing, guitar class suddenly turns into a sci‑fi movie. Tosin Abasi slices rhythms apart, rebuilds them and sprinkles djent grooves on top. Eight strings, no singer, riffs flying in every direction. Your brain tries to count the beats… your neck just gives up and starts headbanging.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn Animals As Leaders loslegen, fühlt sich der Gitarrenunterricht plötzlich an wie ein Science-Fiction-Film. Tosin Abasi zerlegt Rhythmen, baut sie neu zusammen und wirft noch ein paar Djent-Grooves obendrauf. Acht Saiten, kein Sänger, dafür Riffs in allen Dimensionen. Der Kopf versucht mitzuzählen – der Nacken gibt einfach auf und bangt.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/animals-as-leaders/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJ3f_eiztR0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"animals_as_leaders26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/animals_as_leaders26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36364}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4563,uri:"https://animalsasleaders.org/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4564,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/animalsasleaders"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4565,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/animalsasleaders"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"65C6Unk7nhg2aCnVuAPMo8",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/b/csm_animals_as_leaders26_0a9b3dfbf5.jpg",uid:1649},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Any given Day",uid:1162}],end:"1785509100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785506400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2722}],pathSegment:"any-given-day",title:"Any given Day",uid:1162},biography:"<p>The Ruhr area practically offers originals on every corner.&nbsp;Gelsenkirchen alone can boast a figure like Rudi Assauer, literally papal in a stature. But musically, the city also has some serious legendary potential in its back pocket.<br />Any Given Day can rightfully call themselves a trailblazing German Metalcore band. The group, led by frontman berserker Dennis Diehl, combines the brutality of death metal with the energy and catchiness of metalcore. The fact that, in their thirteenth year, the band can finally announce their appearance on the Holy Ground just proves: legends don’t rely on luck. They simply show up at the right time in the right place.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Originale bietet der Ruhrpott praktisch an jeder Ecke. Alleine Gelsenkirchen kann mit Rudi Assauer praktisch eine Papst-gleiche Figur abstellen. Aber auch musikalisch hat die Stadt durchaus Legenden-Material auf der hohen Kante. Any Given Day dürfen sich mit Fug und Recht als wegweisende deutsche Metalcore Band bezeichnen. Die Band um Frontberserker Dennis Diehl vereint die Brutalität des Death Metal mit der Dynamik und Eingängigkeit des Metalcore. Dass die Band im dreizehnten Jahr ihres Bestehens nun endlich ankündigen kann, den Holy Ground zu beehren, beweist nur, Legenden haben einfach kein Pech. Sie sind genau zur richtigen Zeit am richtigen Ort.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/any-given-day/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i2ZMb6jXV7Y",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Any_given_Day-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Any_given_Day-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34843}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4344,uri:"https://anygivenday.eu/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4345,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/AnyxGivenxDay"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4346,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/anygivenday"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4p6RoajGbtqLSfYZpFxHyU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/f/csm_Any_given_Day-WOA26_45b0bb14e2.jpg",uid:1586},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Arch Enemy",uid:414}],end:"1659816000",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1659811500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:656},{artists:[{title:"Arch Enemy",uid:414}],end:"1785609000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785603600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2751}],pathSegment:"arch-enemy",title:"Arch Enemy",uid:414},biography:"<p>Wenn Präzision eine Religion wäre, wären Arch Enemy die Hohepriester.<br />&nbsp;<i>“Deceivers”</i> zieht Linien aus Wut, Kontrolle und süßer Gewalt.<br />&nbsp;Gitarren kreisen wie Messer, Drums arbeiten wie Maschinen im Blutrausch.<br />&nbsp;Zwischen Perfektion und Chaos finden sie ihren Frieden.<br />&nbsp;Und wer Arch Enemy live erlebt, weiß: Erlösung flüstert nie – sie schreit.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>If precision were a religion, Arch Enemy would be its high clergy. <i>“Deceivers”</i> carves veins of rage, control, and exquisite violence. Guitars whirl like blades, drums grind like machines gone feral. Somewhere between order and collapse, they find peace. And once you witness Arch Enemy live you’ll find out: Redemption never whispers – it screams.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/arch-enemy/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CA6YSS_3EI0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"arch_enemy_26c.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/arch_enemy_26c.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36289}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4360,uri:"https://archenemy.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4361,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/archenemyofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4362,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/archenemyofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4363,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@archenemyofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0DCw6lHkzh9t7f8Hb4Z0Sx",subtitle:"10th time at Wacken Open Air",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/c/csm_arch_enemy_26c_e1e9c04c76.jpg",uid:1590},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Arroganz",uid:1123}],end:"1785523500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785519900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2740}],pathSegment:"arroganz",title:"Arroganz",uid:1123},biography:"<p>Across a vast&nbsp;wasteland, a glowing&nbsp;river&nbsp;of&nbsp;merciless&nbsp;lava&nbsp;pours down the&nbsp;mountains&nbsp;into a bottomless vortex. What&nbsp;the&nbsp;cover&nbsp;of&nbsp;Arroganz’s&nbsp;new&nbsp;album Death Doom Punks describes&nbsp;is also the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;metaphor&nbsp;for&nbsp;their&nbsp;sound and stage&nbsp;show. The demolition&nbsp;squad&nbsp;from Cottbus, led&nbsp;by a master&nbsp;of&nbsp;black&nbsp;magic, has&nbsp;been&nbsp;enchanting&nbsp;the&nbsp;Extreme Metal&nbsp;scene&nbsp;for&nbsp;almost&nbsp;two&nbsp;decades — and now&nbsp;they’re&nbsp;ready&nbsp;to&nbsp;unleash&nbsp;their&nbsp;wicked craft on the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Über ein weites Ödland ergießt sich ein rotglühender, erbarmungsloser Strom heißer Lava. Berge hinunterlaufend tropft diese in eine bodenlose Öffnung, in einen ewig zirkulierenden Strudel. Was das Cover zum neuen Arroganz Album Death Doom Punks beschreibt, ist zeitgleich eine Analogie ihrer Musik und Bühnen-Show. Das Cottbusser Abrisskommando mit einem Magister in schwarzer Magie verzückt nicht nur bereits seit knapp zwei Dekaden die Extrem-Metal-Welt, sondern wird ihr bitterböses Werk auch auf dem Holy Ground verrichten. Herrlich!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/arroganz/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyY2qNS_Hig",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"arroganz_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/arroganz_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36414}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4566,uri:"https://www.arroganz.info"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4567,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/arroganzgermany"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4568,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/arroganz666/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7eSVSGjrGmW6f8t21v3gHl",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/f/csm_arroganz_26b_b0fc829592.jpg",uid:1538},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Frankreich",shortNameDe:"Frankreich",shortNameEn:"France",uid:72}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ashed Winter",uid:1236}],end:"1785334200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785333000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB France",uid:2614}],pathSegment:"ashed-winter",title:"Ashed Winter",uid:1236},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Ashed Winter is a tribal death groove band from France. Initially rooted in thrash and death metal, the band has evolved gradually, shaping a unique sound that draws from both metal tradition and more tribal influences.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">That evolution has given Ashed Winter a powerful, mystical musical identity. Their current style blends heavy rhythms with elements drawn from traditional music, creating ritualistic, immersive atmospheres — a quest for authenticity that lends every track a sacred, timeless dimension.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Ashed Winter ist eine Tribal-Death-Groove-Band aus Frankreich. Ursprünglich im Thrash und Death Metal verwurzelt, hat sich die Band stetig weiterentwickelt und einen eigenständigen Sound geformt, der sowohl auf der Metal-Tradition als auch auf tribalen Einflüssen aufbaut.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Diese Entwicklung hat Ashed Winter eine kraftvolle, mystische musikalische Identität verliehen. Ihr aktueller Stil verbindet wuchtige Rhythmen mit Elementen traditioneller Musik – ritualistische, immersive Atmosphären, in denen jedes Stück die Suche nach Authentizität trägt und eine sakrale, zeitlose Dimension entfaltet.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ashed-winter/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rsYXzY1Ac2Q",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ashed_winter_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ashed_winter_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36967}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4731,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ashed_winter"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4732,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ashedwinter"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5iqCBlfnYOAxiTlCBkTASc",subtitle:"Metal Battle France",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/4/csm_ashed_winter_26_9e44606ec2.jpg",uid:1712},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Asrock",uid:119}],end:"1754138700",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754182800",start:"1754114400",title:"Saturday",uid:27},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1754136000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2056},{artists:[{title:"Asrock",uid:119}],end:"1785595500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785592800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2784}],pathSegment:"asrock",title:"Asrock",uid:119},biography:`<p>More local&nbsp;heroes&nbsp;than&nbsp;this? Impossible.</p>\r
<p>Asrock&nbsp;from Itzehoe are&nbsp;entering&nbsp;their 14th year&nbsp;as a band with&nbsp;one simple motto: A life&nbsp;for&nbsp;noise. And the&nbsp;five North Germans take&nbsp;that&nbsp;mantra&nbsp;seriously. Not for&nbsp;the&nbsp;first time — and certainly not for&nbsp;the last — they’ll&nbsp;heat&nbsp;things&nbsp;up on the Holy Ground.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Mehr local&nbsp;heroes geht nicht! Asrock aus Itzehoe gehen in ihr 14. Jahr als Band. Ihr Motto: Ein Leben für Lärm. Und das ist nicht nur eine leere Phrase, die fünf Norddeutschen nehmen ihr Mantra ernst. Nicht zum ersten und sicherlich auch nicht zum letzten Mal werden uns die Asrocker auf dem Holy Ground einheizen!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/asrock/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"asrock_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/asrock_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36366}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4569,uri:"https://www.asrock.band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4570,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/p/AsrockBand-100063632795219/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/a/csm_asrock_26_85c4a23518.jpg",uid:1650},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Battlecreek",uid:1124}],end:"1785334500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785331800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2642}],pathSegment:"battlecreek",title:"Battlecreek",uid:1124},biography:"<p>Their sound reminds us of international acts such as Testament and Exodus, with whom they already shared a stage, yet they come from tranquil Bavaria. BATTLECREEK have been on the road for over 20 years and still share the same enthusiasm for playing in 2026 as they did in their early days. It's no coincidence that the band's line-up has remained so consistent and their discography is outstanding without exception. For their first W:O:A show, the Metalheads around singer Berne are preparing the next massive punch – your neck will thank you for it!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ihr Sound erinnert an &nbsp;internationalen Größen wie Testament&nbsp;oder Exodus mit denen sie bereits die Bühne teilten und doch kommen sie aus dem beschaulichen Bayern. BATTLECREEK sind seit über 20 Jahren unterwegs und teilen auch 2026 noch die gleiche Spielfreude wie zu Anfangstagen. Nicht ohne Grund ist das Line-up konstant und in ihrer Diskografie reiht sich Volltreffer an Volltreffer. Für ihre erste W:O:A-Show hat die Truppe bereits die nächsten Hammer in ihr Arsenal gepackt – eure Nacken werden es ihnen danken!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/battlecreek/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrdheXlf5jSUvu2udPAprxw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Battlecreek-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Battlecreek-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34796}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4213,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/BattlecreekThrash/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4214,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/battlecreek_thrash/?hl=de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4216,uri:"https://battlecreek.de/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2wUKcOuW5xBpCKxnWOoxnI",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/e/csm_Battlecreek-WOA26_ebdf45051d.jpg",uid:1539},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Bear McCreary",uid:1200}],end:"1785524400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785520800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2724}],pathSegment:"bear-mccreary",title:"Bear McCreary",uid:1200},biography:"<p>What connects Terminator, Metal and the Emmy Awards? They find their creative common denominator in Bear McCreary. The award-winning soundtrack composer brings his musical magic to the W:O:A stages and proves that with his album ‘The Singularity’ his heart not only beats for symphonic sounds but also for hard tones. What began last year as part of his ‘Themes &amp; Variations’ tour will be masterfully continued on the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Was verbindet Terminator, Metal und die Emmy Awards? In Bear McCreary finden sie ihren kreativen gemeinsamen Nenner. Der preisgekrönte Soundtrack-Komponist bringt seine musikalische Magie auf die Bühnen des W:O:A und stellt unter Beweis, dass er mit seinem Album „The Singularity“ nicht nur die symphonischen Töne, sondern auch die harten Töne bestens beherrscht. Was im Rahmen seiner „Themes &amp; Variations“-Tour letztes Jahr begann, wird auf dem Holy Ground meisterhaft fortgeführt. Lasst euch überraschen…</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/bear-mccreary/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cl0o_ArdldA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"bear_mccreary_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/bear_mccreary_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36409}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4571,uri:"https://bearmccreary.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4572,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/BearMcCrearyOfficial/#"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4573,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/bearmccreary/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/e/csm_bear_mccreary_26b_802dfd47bf.jpg",uid:1651},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Niederlande",shortNameDe:"Niederlande",shortNameEn:"Netherlands",uid:157}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:62},{artists:[{title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234}],end:"1659526200",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659574800",start:"1659506400",title:"Wednesday",uid:1},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659522600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:522},{artists:[{title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234}],end:"1691227500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"128",subtitle:"",title:"Krombacher Stammtisch",uid:22},start:"1691226300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1120},{artists:[{title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234}],end:"1722595500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722654000",start:"1722578400",title:"Friday",uid:21},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722592800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1572},{artists:[{title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234}],end:"1785498300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785496500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2728}],pathSegment:"blaas-of-glory",title:"Blaas of Glory",uid:234},biography:"<p>Eyes and ears open! Soon, BLAAS OF GLORY will be marching across the Holy Ground again with sexy snow leopard leggings, wild wigs and lots of good cheer. The Dutch party animals with their guitars, accordion, timpani, clarinet, tuba and percussion instruments are a perfect fit for our anniversary motto. When the drum major and his crew transform Alice Cooper into a waltz, KISS into country and Van Halen into rumba, you know what that means: Party on!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ohren gespitzt und Augen auf! Bald marschieren BLAAS OF GLORY wieder mit sexy Schneetiger-Leggins, wilden Perücken und jeder Menge guter Laune über den Holy Ground. Die Niederländischen Partylöwen mit Gitarre, Akkordeon, Pauke, Klarinette, Tuba und Percussion passen perfekt zu unserem Jubiläumsmotto. Wenn der Tambourmajor mit seiner Crew Alice Cooper in Walzer, KISS in Country und Van Halen in Rumba verwandelt, wisst ihr Bescheid: Party on!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/blaas-of-glory/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EqgoDXAyUD4&list=RDEqgoDXAyUD4",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"blaas_of_glory_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/blaas_of_glory_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36368}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4574,uri:"https://blaasofglory.nl/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4575,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/blaasofglory"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4576,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/blaasofglory"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3qjpqpwTo3qdYJ3GjQ84GR",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/5/csm_blaas_of_glory_26_f53a31927e.jpg",uid:1652},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Black Label Society",uid:1164}],end:"1785513600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785510000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2697}],pathSegment:"black-label-society",title:"Black Label Society",uid:1164},biography:"<p>Zakk Wylde wears his heart like a weapon – open, heavy, sincere.<br />Black Label Society is whiskey, sweat, and prayer tuned to drop-C.<br /><i>“Doom Crew Inc.”</i> breathes blues-soaked fury with embers of hope beneath.<br />Every note sounds like dirt, every chorus like redemption.<br />This is music for those who’ve learned to fall and still stand tall.<br />Because pain was always part of the chord.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Zakk Wylde trägt sein Herz wie eine Waffe: offen, schwer und ehrlich.<br />Black Label Society ist Whiskey, Schweiß und Gebet in Drop-C.<br /><i>“Doom Crew Inc.”</i> atmet bluesige Wut, doch unter der Asche glüht Hoffnung.<br />Jede Note klingt nach Dreck, jeder Refrain nach Himmel.<br />Es ist Musik für Menschen, die gelernt haben zu fallen – und trotzdem zu stehen.<br />Denn Schmerz war hier schon immer Teil des Akkords.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/black-label-society/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OdNhhCWPA7g",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Blacl_Label_Society_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/Blacl_Label_Society_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35112}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4364,uri:"https://blacklabelsociety.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4365,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/blacklabelsociety"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4366,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/zakkwyldebls/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4367,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg6Vz21ViEsKkQLxuOJgQzQ"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"zfT626RwO6zN3RDYeRit5",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/4/csm_Blacl_Label_Society_26_315019e5cb.jpg",uid:1591},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Belgien",shortNameDe:"Belgien",shortNameEn:"Belgium",uid:20}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Black Tish",uid:906}],end:"1722520800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722560400",start:"1722492000",title:"Thursday",uid:20},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1722517200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Quantum",uid:1678},{artists:[{title:"Black Tish",uid:906}],end:"1785418200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785416400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2688}],pathSegment:"black-tish",title:"Black Tish",uid:906},biography:"<p>They have been named the missing link between “Einstürzende Neubauten” and bands like “Nine Inch Nails” or “Ministry”. Black Tish, formed in Belgium in 1988, released their debut in 2023 and are now ready to show the world what they’re made of. In 2026 they will visit us again!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie gelten als das fehlende Bindeglied zwischen Einstürzende Neubauten und Bands wie Nine Inch Nails oder Ministry. Black Tish, 1988 in Belgien gegründet, veröffentlichten 2023 ihr Debütalbum und sind nun bereit, der Welt zu zeigen, was in ihnen steckt. Zusammen mit „Moth Quantum“ präsentieren sie im Holy Ground eine echte Weltpremiere. Sei dabei!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/black-tish/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JncZwbxIw60",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"black_tish_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/black_tish_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36369}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4679,uri:"https://blacktish.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4577,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100052147722201"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3zgdqcPEdYpDTSCsyjXePd",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/6/csm_black_tish_26_9887b0d604.jpg",uid:1653},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Luxemburg",shortNameDe:"Luxemburg",shortNameEn:"Luxembourg",uid:127}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Blanket Hill",uid:1241}],end:"1785337200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785336000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Luxembourg",uid:2615}],pathSegment:"blanket-hill",title:"Blanket Hill",uid:1241},biography:`<p class="text-justify">BLANKET HILL is a hardcore/metal band from Luxembourg, founded in 2015. Mixing modern hardcore, thrash, death metal, and old-school heavy metal, the five-piece — Sven, Rick, Ornello, Miguel, and David — quickly built a reputation for relentless live shows, earning the moniker "Luxembourg's Hardest" from the public.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">After their 2015 EP Kaizen earned strong reviews, the band toured Europe, hitting Germany, Belgium, the Netherlands, and the UK in 2016 — where the response was strong enough to land them a second UK tour the same year. They've stayed active ever since, racking up local shows and weekenders across the continent.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">BLANKET HILL ist eine Hardcore-/Metal-Band aus Luxemburg, gegründet 2015. Mit einer Mischung aus modernem Hardcore, Thrash, Death Metal und Old-School Heavy Metal hat sich das Quintett – Sven, Rick, Ornello, Miguel und David – durch kompromisslose Live-Shows einen Namen gemacht und vom Publikum den Beinamen „Luxembourg's Hardest" verliehen bekommen.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Nach starken Kritiken zur Debüt-EP Kaizen (2015) tourte die Band durch Europa und spielte 2016 erstmals in Deutschland, Belgien, den Niederlanden und Großbritannien – mit so starkem Echo, dass noch im selben Jahr eine zweite UK-Tour folgte. Seitdem sind sie durchgehend aktiv und füllen lokale Shows und Wochenendfestivals quer durch den Kontinent.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/blanket-hill/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EhgstfAN5D0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"blanket_hill_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/blanket_hill_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36972}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4741,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/blankethillhc"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4742,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/blankethillhc"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3qlsHX7ahgICE2P8CU8Xfo",subtitle:"Metal Battle Luxembourg",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/8/csm_blanket_hill_26_0a741e61f3.jpg",uid:1717},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Bleed From Within",uid:527}],end:"1659781800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1659778200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:658},{artists:[{title:"Bleed From Within",uid:527}],end:"1785600900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785597300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2791}],pathSegment:"bleed-from-within-1",title:"Bleed From Within",uid:527},biography:"<p>From Glasgow’s rain and concrete comes their metallic heartbeat.<br />Bleed From Within don’t play – they construct walls of sound.<br /><i>“Shrine”</i> was a prayer made of sweat, precision, and revolt.<br />They balance fury and form with surgical grace.<br />Every song feels engineered, bolted with fire.<br />And when the breakdown hits, the world goes with it.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Aus Glasgow, wo Regen und Beton eins sind, kommt ihr metallischer Herzschlag.<br />Bleed From Within spielen nicht – sie konstruieren Wände aus Klang.<br /><i>“Shrine”</i> war ihr Gebet aus Schweiß, Präzision und Rebellion.<br />Sie beherrschen die Balance zwischen Raserei und Struktur wie kaum jemand sonst.<br />Jeder Song wirkt gebaut, nicht geschrieben – mit Schrauben aus Feuer.<br />Und wenn der Breakdown fällt, fällt die Welt mit.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/bleed-from-within-1/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aEW7EDECQRU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"bleed_from_within_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/bleed_from_within_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35113}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4368,uri:"https://bleedfromwithin.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4369,uri:"https://facebook.com/bleedfromwithinband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4370,uri:"https://instagram.com/bleedfromwithin"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5ZvwJikDgdP1PFU4PkAPVG",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/6/csm_bleed_from_within_26_c38f26c402.jpg",uid:1592},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Blood Command",uid:1157}],end:"1785584700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785582000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2762}],pathSegment:"blood-command",title:"Blood Command",uid:1157},biography:"<p>RoboCop, Commando, Red Dawn, Blood Command. This list sounds like the return slip from your local video store, waiting for you to bring back those VHS tapes you've had for over 25 years. But one intruder has snuck in. Blood Command make no secret of their love for cheesy 80s Horror movie titles. They mix that flair with fast-paced Hardcore Punk and a whole lot of charisma.<br />It’s a recipe that’s been working for over 17 years – so why change something that already works so well? Welcome to the Holy Ground!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>RoboCop, Commando, Red Dawn, Blood Command.&nbsp;In diese Liste, die wie eine Aufzählung von Filmen klingt, die seit mehr als 25 Jahren warten, von euch in die Videothek zurückgebracht zu werden, hat sich allerdings ein Intruder eingeschlichen.<br />Blood Command machen keinen Hehl aus ihrem Faible für kitschige Namen von 80er Jahre Horrorfilmen. Diese kreuzen sie mit schnellem Hardcore-Punk und einer ganzen Menge Charisma. Ein Rezept, das bereits seit mehr als 17 Jahren schmeckt. Wieso sollte man also etwas verändern, das sowieso gut funktioniert? Willkommen auf dem Holy Ground!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/blood-command/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1Q_rCodQQH1a5YzAXHzPJw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Blood_Command-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Blood_Command-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34835}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4325,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/bloodcommand/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4326,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Bloodcommand/?locale=de_DE"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4WfUbvICLrqPW9rzuNGS1f",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/8/csm_Blood_Command-WOA26_f82b942e22.jpg",uid:1579},{artist:{country:[],events:[{artists:[{title:"Blood Fire Death",uid:1158}],end:"1785528000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785523500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"A Tribute To Bathory",uid:2710}],pathSegment:"blood-fire-death",title:"Blood Fire Death",uid:1158},biography:"<p>Honor to whom honor is due! 22 years after the death of the legend, another dazzling figure from the Scandinavian Black Metal scene takes up the torch of blazing hellfire that Quorthon once ignited – and makes the flames rise anew.<br />With <i>Blood Fire Death</i>, Watain high priest Erik Danielsson pays tribute to the creator of the eerie and the dark, giving Bathory the monument they’ve always deserved. Between Viking and Black Metal, Bathory has carved itself deeply into the history books of heavy metal. An absolute must for every Metal fan! They are riding to Wacken for one exclusive German Show – we cannot contain our excitement!&nbsp;</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ehre, wem Ehre gebührt! 22 Jahre nach dem Tod der Legende ergreift eine weitere schillernde Persönlichkeit der skandinavischen Black Metal Szene den Staffelstab des glühenden Höllenfeuers, dass Quorthon einst entfachte und lässt das Feuer von Neuem lodern.<br />Mit Blood Fire Death zollt Watain Hohepriester Erik Danielsson dem Erfinder des Schaurigen und Dunklen Respekt und setzt Bathory das Denkmal, das ihnen sowieso schon gebührt.<br />Zwischen Viking- und Black Metal hat sich Bathory tief in die Geschichtsbücher des Heavy Metal gebrannt. Ein absolutes Muss für jeden Metal-Fan! Für eine exklusive Deutschland Show begeben sie sich auf den Weg nach Wacken – was für eine Ehre, wir können es kaum abwarten!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/blood-fire-death/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://music.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_l3YWRhSGENiAMsTSaHhHg9goBR1KMciyE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Blood_Fire_Death-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Blood_Fire_Death-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34854}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4329,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/bloodfiredeathtribute?igsh=MWc2Zng3aGJiZXZsbg=="}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2QVt9UZEloRJgYqE70ACPs",subtitle:"A tribute to Bathory / Germany exclusive",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/d/csm_Blood_Fire_Death-WOA26_c420b03929.jpg",uid:1580},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Blood Red Throne",uid:1125}],end:"1785435300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785431700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Altered Genesis Set",uid:2677}],pathSegment:"blood-red-throne",title:"Blood Red Throne",uid:1125},biography:"<p>Be there&nbsp;when&nbsp;the&nbsp;gates&nbsp;of hell open once&nbsp;again and Blood Red Throne claim&nbsp;their&nbsp;rightful&nbsp;place. After their&nbsp;first&nbsp;appearance on our&nbsp;holy&nbsp;ground&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;ten&nbsp;years&nbsp;ago, the&nbsp;five&nbsp;Death Metal&nbsp;heavyweights&nbsp;return&nbsp;to Wacken to&nbsp;spread&nbsp;fear and terror while they perform a special Altered Genesis set. While&nbsp;you’re still being&nbsp;sucked&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;pit, your&nbsp;face&nbsp;twisted in horror, the&nbsp;Norwegians will bombard&nbsp;you&nbsp;with&nbsp;their&nbsp;serenades&nbsp;of&nbsp;horror, murder, and mayhem. Simply&nbsp;glorious, isn’t&nbsp;it?</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Seid dabei wenn die Tore der Hölle sich wieder öffnen und Blood Red Throne ihren rechtmäßigen Platz einfordern. Nach ihrem ersten Gastspiel auf unserem Acker, das bereits mehr als zehn Jahre zurückliegt, kehren die fünf Death Metal Großkaliber zurück nach Wacken um mit ihrem Altered Genesis Set Angst und Schrecken zu verbreiten. Während ihr noch mit Schreck verzerrtem Gesicht in den Pit gesaugt werdet, hauen euch die Norweger ihre Serenaden aus Horror, Mord und Totschlag um die Ohren. Einfach herrlich oder?</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/blood-red-throne/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCib0fhW5fQS00H_gMmmN7CA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"blood_red_throne26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/blood_red_throne26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35143}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4217,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/BloodRedThroneOfficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4218,uri:"https://bloodredthrone.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4219,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/bloodredthroneofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"38shFuJO9k0kOEQSf854u4",subtitle:'"Altered Genesis" Set',thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/a/csm_blood_red_throne26_98867522b5.jpg",uid:1540},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kanada",shortNameDe:"Kanada",shortNameEn:"Canada",uid:36}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Born Broken",uid:1238}],end:"1785321300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785320100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Canada",uid:2623}],pathSegment:"born-broken",title:"Born Broken",uid:1238},biography:`<p class="text-justify">BornBroken is a groove metal band from Montreal, Canada — a cornerstone of the city's underground scene, known for an aggressive, groove-driven sound, socially conscious themes, and high-energy performances that have earned them a loyal following across Canada.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their 2024 album Am I Invisible marked a major creative milestone, drawing praise from Decibel Magazine for fusing early Machine Head, post-Roots Sepultura, Lamb of God, and Fear Factory influences with big guitars, bigger grooves, and soaring choruses. The lineup gained new depth with drummer Peter Tzaferis (formerly of Slaves On Dope), and the band's recent national victory signals a powerful new chapter — uncompromising music carrying a message as heavy as the sound.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">BornBroken ist eine Groove-Metal-Band aus Montreal, Kanada – ein Eckpfeiler der dortigen Underground-Szene, bekannt für aggressiven, groove-lastigen Sound, gesellschaftskritische Themen und energiegeladene Auftritte, die ihnen quer durch Kanada eine treue Fangemeinde verschafft haben.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr 2024er Album Am I Invisible markiert einen kreativen Meilenstein und wurde vom Decibel Magazine dafür gelobt, frühe Machine Head, post-Roots Sepultura, Lamb of God und Fear Factory mit dicken Gitarren, noch dickeren Grooves und hymnischen Refrains zu verbinden. Mit Schlagzeuger Peter Tzaferis (zuvor Slaves On Dope) gewann das Line-up zusätzliche Tiefe – und der jüngste nationale Sieg läutet ein kraftvolles neues Kapitel ein: kompromisslose Musik mit einer Botschaft, die so schwer wiegt wie der Sound selbst.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/born-broken/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j3JXTHX0svI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"born_broken_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/born_broken_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36969}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4735,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/bornbrokenofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4736,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/BornBroken"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1eK0MDcJMrahfqgCjlPEzl",subtitle:"Metal Battle Canada",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/9/csm_born_broken_26_e3d993f78e.jpg",uid:1714},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Japan",shortNameDe:"Japan",shortNameEn:"Japan",uid:107}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Broken By The Scream",uid:1137}],end:"1785321900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785319200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2603}],pathSegment:"broken-by-the-scream",title:"Broken By The Scream",uid:1137},biography:"<p>Don’t judge a book by its cover! The Japanese idol group is making the journey to Wacken and is ready to tear you apart – all while looking like total pros. Their mix of crushing metalcore and anime-style cuteness feels like a newly invented symbiosis between Hello Kitty and a bulldozer. No one is too tough for Kawaii – and Broken by the Scream are here to prove it to you.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Don’t judge a book by its cover!&nbsp;Die japanische Idol Gruppe tritt die Reise nach Wacken an um euch niederzufetzen und sehen dabei wie Vollprofis aus. Die Mischung aus knallhartem Metalcore und Anime-Cuteness wirkt wie eine neu erfundene Symbiose zwischen Hello Kitty und Bulldozer. Niemand ist too tough für Kawaii – &nbsp;Broken by the Scream beweisen das.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/broken-by-the-scream/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwlS2fIivj-8g8Tk4dg7Fgw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Broken_By_The_Scream-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Broken_By_The_Scream-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34836}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4249,uri:"https://www.brokenbythescream.jp/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4250,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/BrokenByTheScream.jp"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4251,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/brokenbythescream_koushiki/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0QJjaDqswcLyjDOgcBBf1Z",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/5/csm_Broken_By_The_Scream-WOA26_8ad83f8245.jpg",uid:1552},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Brunhilde",uid:615}],end:"1691066700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691110800",start:"1691042400",title:"Thursday",uid:14},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1691064000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:975},{artists:[{title:"Brunhilde",uid:615}],end:"1785422700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785420000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2689}],pathSegment:"brunhilde",title:"Brunhilde",uid:615},biography:"<p>The four musicians from Fürth are as powerful and determined as the eponymous heroine from the Nibelungen saga. BRUNHILDE released their fifth album ‘In Love Your's Hate’ on their own label in the middle of the year, in which they tell of love and hate and the bitter struggle for freedom. Frontwoman Caro knows exactly how to combine the best of Punk, Hard Rock and Metal with her likeable manner – we look forward to seeing them again at W:O:A.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Die vier Fürther sind so kämpferisch und zielstrebig wie die namensgebende Heldin aus der Nibelungensage. BRUNHILDE haben auf ihrem eigenen Label Mitte des Jahres das fünfte Album „In Love Your’s Hate“ veröffentlicht, worauf sie von Liebe und Hass sowie dem erbitterten Kampf für das Streben nach Freiheit erzählen. Frontfrau Caro weiß genau, wie sie das Beste aus den Welten Punk, Hard Rock und Metal mit ihrer sympathischen Art verbindet – wir freuen uns auf das Wiedersehen beim W:O:A.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/brunhilde/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7aRfbNWg0JM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"brunhilde_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/brunhilde_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35773}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4506,uri:"https://www.brunhilde.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4507,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Brunhilde-477070609096438/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4508,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/brunhilderocks/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0J0ZiqA0aDxmkQye4wohwb",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/4/csm_brunhilde_26_489882e4fb.jpg",uid:1631},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Castle Rat",uid:1165}],end:"1785609900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785606300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2787}],pathSegment:"castle-rat",title:"Castle Rat",uid:1165},biography:"<p>Excuse me — latest hot shit? Found it! Somewhere between nightmare and opera lies the realm of Castle Rat.<br />Their doom rituals smell of incense, sweat, and legend. On stage they slay the colossal Rat Lord – over and over, louder each time.<br />Guitars swing like swords, vocals drip with curses. Fantasy meets darkness, every gig a boss battle. See them once, and you’re joyfully doomed forever.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Bin ich hier richtig beim neuesten heißen Scheiß, oder nur beim Probelauf für Legendenstatus?&nbsp;Irgendwo zwischen Albtraum und Oper liegt das Königreich von Castle Rat.&nbsp;Ihre Doom-Rituale riechen nach Weihrauch, Schweiß und Nebel überm Gruselmoor.<br />Auf der Bühne metzeln sie den überdimensionalen Rattenlord – immer wieder, immer lauter. Ihre Gitarren schleppen Schwerter, ihre Vocals tragen Flüche. Fantasy trifft Finsternis, und jede Show fühlt sich an wie ein Bossfight. Wer sie einmal sieht, bleibt ewig verflucht – im besten Sinn.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/castle-rat/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xp-8USQQc1Q",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"castle_Rat_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/castle_Rat_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35114}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4371,uri:"https://castlerat.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4372,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/castle.rat"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4373,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/castleratband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4374,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@castlerat"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2g5gjeZJLGcWPAF0o9KdJj",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/3/csm_castle_Rat_26_29b54db683.jpg",uid:1593},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Cevret",uid:1249}],end:"1785169800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785200400",start:"1785132000",title:"Monday",uid:32},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785167100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2800}],pathSegment:"cevret",title:"Cevret",uid:1249},biography:`<p>Who says brainpower and headbanging don't mix? Cevret started in 2019 as an ambitious solo project by the Swiss multi-instrumentalist of the same name, who casually recruited the crème de la crème of modern metal (like Andy Cizek of Monuments) for guest vocals in the studio. But because sitting alone in a basement doesn't start a mosh pit, the project mutated into a fully staffed, unstoppable live machine in 2024. With their powerhouse EP “Sensus” <i>- </i>mastered by none other than Swedish production legend Jens Bogren for that perfect, crystal-clear mix - the Swiss band dissects the moral decay of humanity. Sounds a bit highbrow? Don’t worry! The music press calls the result an absolute "energy bomb," pairing complex progressive riffs with an aggression that is guaranteed to rewire your synapses right here at the Landgasthof!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Wer sagt denn, dass Gehirnschmalz und Nackenschmerzen sich ausschließen? Cevret startete 2019 als ambitioniertes Solo-Projekt des gleichnamigen Schweizer Multiinstrumentalisten, das sich im Studio mal eben die Crème de la Crème des modernen Metals (wie Andy Cizek von Monuments) ans Mikrofon holte. Doch weil alleine im Keller sitzen auf Dauer keinen Moshpit bringt, mutierte die Kiste 2024 zur vollbesetzten Live-Dampfwalze. Mit ihrem EP-Brett “Sensus” - für den perfekten, glasklaren Sound stand kein Geringerer als die schwedische Mastering-Legende Jens Bogren an den Reglern - sezieren die Schweizer den moralischen Verfall der Menschheit. Klingt verkopft? Keine Sorge! Das Resultat ist laut der Fachpresse eine absolute “Energie-Bombe”, die komplexe, progressive Riffs mit einer Aggressivität paart, die euch im Landgasthof garantiert die Synapsen neu verkabelt!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/cevret/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CLXn1Mjr5Ac",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"cevret_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/cevret_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37047}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4766,uri:"https://www.cevret.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4767,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/cevretofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4768,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/cevret_music/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4zMCIdHWgoI9MnxSFMsYxS",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/4/csm_cevret_26_18dafb1177.jpg",uid:1727},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Chaosbay",uid:1166}],end:"1785509100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785506400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2737}],pathSegment:"chaosbay",title:"Chaosbay",uid:1166},biography:`<p>From the East of Germany straight to the North – Chaosbay are ready for round two on Wacken soil!</p>\r
<p>Brace yourself for neck-breaking time shifts, brutal breakdowns, and dangerously catchy choruses.</p>\r
<p>The Leipzig quartet brings along their new record Are You Afraid? and a live show that hits harder than ever.</p>\r
<p>Even after more than a decade, their sound still feels fresh – a fountain of youth, Wacken-style.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Vom Osten der Republik in den Hohen Norden – Chaosbay sind bereit für Runde zwei auf dem Wackener Acker. Seid ihr auch bereit für eine Runde halsbrecherischer Taktwechsel, brutaler Breaks und süchtig machenden Choruses? Dann habt ihr Glück, denn die Leipziger Formation bringt nicht nur ihr aktuelles Album Are You Afraid? mit, sondern auch eine Bühnen-Show, die sich gewaschen hat. Der Mix des Vierers klingt auch nach über zehn Jahren Bestehen immer noch frisch und neu – ein Jungbrunnen der ganz besonderen Art also.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/chaosbay/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MrjMlHpTpHU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"chaos_bay_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/chaos_bay_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35827}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4538,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/chaosbay"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4539,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/chaosbayofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4540,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/chaosbay"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7GNTvmIi6DDF2XDJKYKoUk",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/8/csm_chaos_bay_26_6d40a05540.jpg",uid:1594},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Corrosion of Conformity",uid:1178}],end:"1785615300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785611700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2766}],pathSegment:"corrosion-of-conformity",title:"Corrosion of Conformity",uid:1178},biography:"<p>CORROSION OF CONFORMITY are really busy – in a positive sense. The American quartet was on tour with Judas Priest and Alice Cooper, is working on a new studio album for 2026, and Stanton Moore has recently rejoined the band as a permanent member after the band had to cope with the loss of drummer Reed Mullin. Stronger than evert they are looking ahead! Conformity? Not a chance! Pepper Keenan and his band are too versatile, ambitious and creative for that!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Bei CORROSION OF CONFORMITY brodelt es gerade mächtig – im positiven Sinne. Das US-amerikanische Quartett war mit Judas Priest und Alice Cooper auf großer Tour, arbeitet an einem neuen Studioalbum für 2026 und jüngst ist Stanton Moore wieder festes Mitglied, nachdem die Band den Verlust von Schlagzeuger Reed Mullin verarbeiten musste. Voller Kraft und unbeirrt wird nach Vorne geschaut! Konformität? Fehlanzeige! Dafür ist die Stahlschmiede um Pepper Keenan zu vielseitig, ambitioniert und kreativ!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/corrosion-of-conformity/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pEj_XtkDRFU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"corrosion_of_conformity_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/corrosion_of_conformity_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35756}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4444,uri:"https://www.corrosionofconformity.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4445,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/corrosionofconformity"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4446,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/coccabal/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4447,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOXzr2O6Nxy52AIIilwsYUw"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1BBIIH0h76KN8gYeXFcPjR",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/b/csm_corrosion_of_conformity_26_8ba7dabe09.jpg",uid:1613},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Cowgirls From Hell",uid:1232}],end:"1785459600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785448800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2679}],pathSegment:"cowgirls-from-hell",title:"Cowgirls From Hell",uid:1232},biography:`<p>Birmingham — cradle&nbsp;of&nbsp;Heavy Metal.</p>\r
<p>Around&nbsp;here, hard&nbsp;steel&nbsp;is&nbsp;absorbed&nbsp;with&nbsp;mother’s milk.</p>\r
<p>It’s&nbsp;the&nbsp;only&nbsp;explanation&nbsp;for&nbsp;legends like Ozzy, Rob Halford… and of&nbsp;course&nbsp;the Cowgirls From Hell.</p>\r
<p>Their&nbsp;mission? To kick your&nbsp;asses in the&nbsp;best possible way.</p>\r
<p>A DJ set&nbsp;by&nbsp;these&nbsp;two British women&nbsp;isn’t just a DJ set — it’s a full-throttle&nbsp;rollercoaster&nbsp;ride&nbsp;through&nbsp;everything&nbsp;that&nbsp;hits&nbsp;hard and keeps&nbsp;your neck spinning.</p>\r
<p>And once&nbsp;the Cowgirls are&nbsp;done&nbsp;with&nbsp;you, you’ll&nbsp;probably&nbsp;need a week in an oxygen tent. Guaranteed.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Birmingham, Brutkasten des Heavy Metal. Hier wird der Hartstahl bereits mit der Muttermilch aufgesogen. Nur so sind Legenden wie Ozzy, Rob Halford oder aber die Cowgirls From Hell zu erklären. Angetreten, um uns in die 5 Buchstaben zu treten ist ein DJ Set der beiden Britinnen nicht einfach nur ein DJ Set. Es ist eine wilde Achterbahnfahrt durch alles, was knallt und den Nacken zum Rotieren animiert. Wenn die Cowgirls mit euch fertig sind, braucht ihr unbedingt eine Woche im Sauerstoffzelt. Garantiert!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/cowgirls-from-hell/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"cowgirls_from_hell_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/cowgirls_from_hell_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36699}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4721,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/cowgirlsfromhell_djs/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/0/csm_cowgirls_from_hell_26_30a60185cc.jpg",uid:1705},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Craft",uid:1176}],end:"1785423600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785420900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2666}],pathSegment:"craft",title:"Craft",uid:1176},biography:`<p>Things are about to turn pitch black and ice cold – Craft are making their way from the far north of Sweden to the far north of Germany.</p>\r
<p>They’re bringing with them hymns of frozen beauty and vocals that will make your blood run cold. If Black Metal were a drink, Craft would be everything that hits hard and comes with plenty of ice!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Jetzt wird es pechschwarz und eiskalt – Craft bahnen sich ihren Weg aus dem hohen Norden Schwedens in den hohen Norden Deutschlands.</p>\r
<p>Mitbringen werden sie Hymnen voller eiskalter Schönheit und Vocals, die uns das Blut in den Adern gefrieren lassen. Wenn Black Metal ein Getränk wäre, dann wären Craft alles was knallt und mit viel Eis!&nbsp;</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/craft/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7jI_KDkWP4E",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Craft_cropped_size_-_photo_by_Soile_Siirtola.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/Craft_cropped_size_-_photo_by_Soile_Siirtola.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35148}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4432,uri:"https://craftblackmetal.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4433,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/craftblackmetal/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4434,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/craftblackmetal/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0hkIlpV0isEixFIr74VfZm",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/d/csm_Craft_cropped_size_-_photo_by_Soile_Siirtola_fabe03b40f.jpg",uid:1610},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Crematory",uid:40}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1280",subtitle:"",title:"History Stage",uid:14},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:222},{artists:[{title:"Crematory",uid:40}],end:"1691189100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1691185500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1007},{artists:[{title:"Crematory",uid:40}],end:"1785528900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785525300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"35th Anniversary Show",uid:2718}],pathSegment:"crematory",title:"Crematory",uid:40},biography:"<p>There's a lot going on for CREMATORY right now. Their latest studio album, ‘Destination,’ earned the band their highest chart entry to date in the German Top 10, after which the band went on tour in Germany and re-released their genre-defining catalogue, including albums such as “Illusions” and ‘Awake.’ A nod to the past and at the same time a clear step forward. The next stop is Wacken, where the Gothic Metal pioneers will perform their dark songs for the ninth time. What a kick off the celebrations for the band's 35th anniversary.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Im Hause CREMATORY ist derzeit mächtig was los. Ihr aktuelles Studioalbum „Destination“ bescherte der Band den bisher höchsten Charteinstieg in den Top-10 der deutschen Charts, woraufhin das Quintett auf Deutschland-Tour ging und ihren genreprägenden Katalog mit Alben wie „Illusions“ oder „Awarke“ neu veröffentlichte. Eine Verneigung vor der Vergangenheit und gleichzeitig ein klarer Schritt nach vorne. Der nächste Stopp ist in Wacken, wo die Gothic Metal-Pioniere zum neunten Mal ihre düsteren Songs zum Besten geben. So können die Feierlichkeiten anlässlich des 35. Bandjubiläums losgehen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/crematory/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMqgLBUiS-w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"crematory_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/crematory_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36370}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4578,uri:"https://www.crematory.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4579,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/crematory.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4580,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/crematory.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4581,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@CrematoryDe"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4q2uhIfBHCNlwXYvQdnzvS",subtitle:"35th Anniversary Show",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/c/csm_crematory_26_8ae2e22d82.jpg",uid:1654},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Crimson Glory",uid:1126}],end:"1785588300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785585600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2769}],pathSegment:"crimson-glory",title:"Crimson Glory",uid:1126},biography:"<p>Crimson Glory sound like dreams cast in chrome. Their <i>“Transcendence”</i> remains a masterclass in drama, pathos, and precision. Masks, myths, melodies – flirting with the divine but grounded in grit. Every note a prayer to the cosmos, every solo a crack in the sky. They are melancholy with a crown, theatre with backbone. And those who get it, hear not music – but magnitude.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Crimson Glory klingen, als hätte man Träume aus Chrom gegossen. Ihr <i>“Transcendence”</i> ist bis heute ein Lehrstück in Drama, Pathos und Präzision. Masken, Mythen, Melodien – sie spielen mit dem Überirdischen, ohne den Boden zu verlieren. Jede Note wirkt wie ein Gebet an den Kosmos, jedes Solo wie ein Riss im Himmel. Sie sind Melancholie mit Federhut, Theatralik mit Rückgrat. Und wer sie versteht, hört mehr als Musik – er hört Größe.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/crimson-glory/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvEE8_lVdKU__LIsQgdbmDg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"crimson_glory_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/crimson_glory_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35107}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4220,uri:"https://theofficialcrimsonglory.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4350,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/crimsonglory/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2B73nUiRlcSwjTyVaIAwhR",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/2/csm_crimson_glory_26_59c22b790e.jpg",uid:1541},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Irland",shortNameDe:"Irland",shortNameEn:"Ireland",uid:97}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Cruachan",uid:1201}],end:"1785513600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785510000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2731}],pathSegment:"cruachan",title:"Cruachan",uid:1201},biography:"<p>When&nbsp;the Holy Ground turns&nbsp;into a battlefield, chances&nbsp;are&nbsp;Cruachan&nbsp;are not far&nbsp;away. For&nbsp;over 30 years&nbsp;the&nbsp;Irish&nbsp;Folk Metal&nbsp;veterans&nbsp;have&nbsp;called&nbsp;Metalheads&nbsp;to&nbsp;arms — and to&nbsp;their&nbsp;mead&nbsp;horns. Because&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;earn&nbsp;your&nbsp;spurs in the&nbsp;pit, you’ve also earned&nbsp;the&nbsp;right&nbsp;to&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;the&nbsp;gentler Celtic tones&nbsp;afterwards.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn der Holy Ground bebt und zum Schlatfeld wird, dann sind die Iren Cruachan nicht weit. Die Folk Metal Veteranen rufen seit mehr als 30 Jahren uns Metalheads zu den Waffen und Metkrügen – denn wer sich im Moshpit die Sporen verdient, der hat danach auch jedes Recht bei einem Kaltgetränk den sanfteren Tönen zu lauschen, die die keltischen Inselbewohner ebenso beherrschen. Wir verneigen uns vor echten Legenden und können es kaum erwarten, unsere Bärte gemeinsam im Wind wehen zu lassen!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/cruachan/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mibB2SnmqhE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"cruachan_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/cruachan_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36371}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4582,uri:"https://www.cruachanireland.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4583,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/cruachanclan/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4584,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/cruachan_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6QpbkfyEQJ3JiQw2AbTRUH",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/0/csm_cruachan_26_fe9f62c6a3.jpg",uid:1655},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Crypt Sermon",uid:1127}],end:"1785350700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785348000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2645}],pathSegment:"crypt-sermon",title:"Crypt Sermon",uid:1127},biography:"<p>A mighty cross, spider webs and a skull adorn the backdrop of CRYPT SERMON. No wonder, because the US band led by singer Brooks Wilson plays Epic Doom Metal and preaches dark stories and enchanted legends in sometimes overly long songs. On Wasted Wednesday, they bring the dark atmosphere to the Holy Ground. Tune your airguitars down a tone and give the slow, raw sound its space – Stage clear for CRYPT SERMON.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ein mächtiges Kreuz, Spinnweben und ein Totenkopf zieren das Backdrop von CRYPT SERMON. Kein Wunder, denn die US-Amerikaner um Sänger Brooks Wilson spielen epischen Doom Metal und predigen in ihren meist epischen Songs von dunklen Geschichten und verwunschenen Legenden. Am Wasted Wednesday bringen sie diese düstere Atmosphäre auf den Holy Ground. Stimmt eure Luftgitarren einen Ton tiefer und gebt den schleppenden, rauen Klängen ihren Raum – Bühne frei für CRYPT SERMON.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/crypt-sermon/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y3XyvoVLdhk&list=RDY3XyvoVLdhk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"crypt_sermon_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/crypt_sermon_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36338}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4221,uri:"https://www.cryptsermon.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4222,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/CryptSermon/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4223,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/cryptsermon/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4542,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBVO24lk-F3oGZQFV_ZWAQw"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"363ih5wuNGWBFcjeKFG8cc",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/4/csm_crypt_sermon_26_25a80f0eed.jpg",uid:1542},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Cursed Abyss",uid:1202}],end:"1785504600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785502800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2736}],pathSegment:"cursed-abyss",title:"Cursed Abyss",uid:1202},biography:"<p>Metal&nbsp;brings&nbsp;people&nbsp;together — and sometimes&nbsp;even&nbsp;brings&nbsp;them&nbsp;straight&nbsp;to Wacken. Cursed Abyss are&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;example: the brutal Hamburg five-piece actually&nbsp;formed at the Wacken Music Camp in 2022. Now&nbsp;they&nbsp;return&nbsp;to&nbsp;that&nbsp;very same field&nbsp;to&nbsp;unleash&nbsp;their&nbsp;latest&nbsp;album Rot In Existence. If&nbsp;anyone&nbsp;ever&nbsp;asks&nbsp;you&nbsp;what Wacken sounds like — this&nbsp;is it.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Metal bringt die Menschen zusammen und zieht sie dann nach Wacken auf den Holy Ground. Im Falle von Cursed Abyss könnten wir sogar von ganz direkter Starthilfe sprechen: Der Hamburger Fünfer, der sich ganz den brutalsten Sounds verschrieben hat, die es im extremem Bereich des Metal so gibt, gründete sich 2022 beim Wacken Music Camp. Und genau auf diesen Acker kehren die jungen Metalheads wieder zurück, um uns mit ihrem aktuellen Album Rot In Existence eine ordentliche Breitseite zu verpassen. Wenn euch jemals jemand fragen sollte wie Wacken klingt? Genau so!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/cursed-abyss/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UwL2njZirxo",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"cursed_abyss_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/cursed_abyss_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36372}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4585,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/cursed_abyss_/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"18inV5ouPlVcntsdYFWwiJ",subtitle:"Founded at Wacken Music Camp",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/d/csm_cursed_abyss_26_924d9b9653.jpg",uid:1656},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kanada",shortNameDe:"Kanada",shortNameEn:"Canada",uid:36}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Danko Jones",uid:368}],end:"1659807000",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1659802500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:667},{artists:[{title:"Danko Jones",uid:368}],end:"1785509100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785505500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2701}],pathSegment:"danko-jones",title:"Danko Jones",uid:368},biography:"<p>With their brand new album ‘Leo Rising’, Canadian rockers DANKO JONES have raised the bar once again and proven that they are still going strong almost two decades after the band was formed. It's no surprise that the trio has already been nominated for the Juno Awards (the Canadian Grammy Awards) and has gathered a loyal fan base around the world. Raise your horns: It's going to be a Punk, Metal and Blues thunderstorm on the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Mit ihrem brandneuen Album „Leo Rising“ setzen die kanadischen Rocker DANKO JONES die eigene Messlatte erneut ein Stück höher und beweisen, dass sie auch knapp 2 Jahrzehnte nach der Bandgründung noch voller Power stecken. Nicht ohne Grund ist das Trio bereits für die Juno Awards (die kanadischen Grammy Awards) nominiert worden und schart weltweit eine treue Fangemeinde um sich. Pommesgabel in die Höhe: Das wird ein punkiges, metallisches und bluesiges Donnerwetter auf dem Holy Ground.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/danko-jones/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ndigVPHyysI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"danko_jones_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/danko_jones_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35774}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4509,uri:"https://www.dankojones.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4510,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/dankojones"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4511,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/danko_jones/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7CGoviGsNXYmGOBkXk8dtW",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/e/csm_danko_jones_26_3405a63446.jpg",uid:1632},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Days of Ruin",uid:1271}],end:"1785419700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785418500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Switzerland",uid:2675}],pathSegment:"days-of-ruin",title:"Days of Ruin",uid:1271},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Days of Ruin is an old-school metalcore band from Bern, Switzerland, founded in 2017 by former members of Road To Nowhere, Omnicide, and Paranoia, with Michael Stucki (ex-Art of Phobia) joining shortly after on vocals.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Musically, they blend old-school metalcore with death metal heaviness, driving grooves, and uncompromising live energy. Less about polished images or maximum complexity, more about authenticity, the joy of playing, and a direct connection with the audience — a stagecraft honed across years of Swiss shows. Following the 2020 LP Extinction and three 2025 singles, their new EP Age of Ignorance (out September 25, 2026, recorded at SOS Basement) brings established live favorites and new tracks together into their most cohesive release to date.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Days of Ruin ist eine Old-School-Metalcore-Band aus Bern, Schweiz, 2017 von ehemaligen Mitgliedern von Road To Nowhere, Omnicide und Paranoia gegründet. Kurz darauf stieß Michael Stucki (ex-Art of Phobia) am Mikrofon dazu.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Musikalisch verbinden Days of Ruin Old-School-Metalcore mit der Härte des Death Metal, treibenden Grooves und kompromissloser Live-Energie. Weniger auf akribisch inszenierte Bilder oder maximale Komplexität ausgelegt – mehr auf Authentizität, Spielfreude und den direkten Draht zum Publikum, eine Bühnenkunst, die sie über Jahre auf Schweizer Bühnen geschliffen haben. Nach dem 2020er Album Extinction und drei Singles im Jahr 2025 markiert ihre neue EP Age of Ignorance (Veröffentlichung 25. September 2026, aufgenommen im SOS Basement) ihren nächsten Schritt: etablierte Live-Favoriten und neues Material in ihrer bisher geschlossensten Veröffentlichung.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/days-of-ruin/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uR67g6MZ_FE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"days_of_ruin_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/days_of_ruin_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37111}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4825,uri:"https://www.daysofruin.ch/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4826,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/daysofruin_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4827,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/DaysofRuinHC"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"59oMejeYq8SPQKLKuqKfO8",subtitle:"Metal Battle Switzerland",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/0/csm_days_of_ruin_26_6357e7d8fe.jpg",uid:1752},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dead by April",uid:1243}],end:"1785505500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785502800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2715}],pathSegment:"dead-by-april",title:"Dead by April",uid:1243},biography:"<p>What did your playlists look like in the early 2010s, Metalheads?<br />Ours definitely featured Dead By April. Their addictive mix of crushing metalcore, soaring hooks, and pure neck-breaking energy left its mark on us, too.<br />And since 2026 marks not only almost 20 years of Dead By April, but also 35 years of W:O:A, we figured it was about time to invite them back to the Holy Ground. We might need to check on our myspace account …<br />&nbsp;</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wie wohl eure Playlist Anfang der 2010er Jahre ausgesehen hat Metalheads? Auf unseren Ohren landeten damals auf jeden Fall die Schweden Dead By April. Dieser süchtig machende Mix aus ultraschnellen und brutalen Metal Parts und eingängigen Hooks ging auch an uns nicht spurlos vorüber.<br />Und weil 2026 nicht nur fast 20 Jahre Dead By April bedeutet, sondern auch 35 Mal W:O:A haben wir die Nackenbrecher glatt mal wieder eingeladen, den Holy Ground und uns zu bespaßen. Jetzt müssten wir doch glatt auch nochmal unsere myspace Accounts checken…</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dead-by-april/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xFDmYl3l6w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dead_by_april_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dead_by_april_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36974}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4745,uri:"https://www.deadbyapril.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4746,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/deadbyapril/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4747,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/deadbyapril_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2otRZcOVNcmdkZ5nEoogy6",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/4/csm_dead_by_april_26_b9b9c21441.jpg",uid:1719},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Irland",shortNameDe:"Irland",shortNameEn:"Ireland",uid:97}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dead Memories",uid:1267}],end:"1785327300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785326100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Ireland",uid:2625}],pathSegment:"dead-memories",title:"Dead Memories",uid:1267},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Dead Memories is a slam/deathcore band from Dublin, Ireland. Just out of high school, this young band has quickly built a serious reputation for hard-hitting live performances and an original sound that fuses slam, deathcore, and hardcore into a high-intensity metal onslaught.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their devastating soundscape — full of crushing chugs, epic breakdowns, and menacing grooves — guarantees a frenzy of banging heads and maximum destruction in any pit. Dead Memories released their debut EP Slamscorthy in 2025.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Dead Memories ist eine Slam-/Deathcore-Band aus Dublin, Irland. Frisch von der Schule, hat sich die junge Band rasch einen ernstzunehmenden Ruf für wuchtige Live-Auftritte und einen eigenständigen Sound erspielt, der Slam, Deathcore und Hardcore zu einem hochintensiven Metal-Angriff verschmelzen lässt.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihre vernichtende Klanglandschaft – voller brutaler Chugs, epischer Breakdowns und bedrohlicher Grooves – garantiert eine Welle aus Headbanging und maximaler Zerstörung in jedem Pit. Ihre Debüt-EP Slamscorthy erschien 2025.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dead-memories/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W3NsvjpacBs",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dead_memories_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dead_memories_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37107}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4816,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/deadmemories_ie"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4817,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@DeadMemoriesMetalcore"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"28KiIoTkbJGM5aZNo6Q5DD",subtitle:"Metal Battle Ireland",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/8/csm_dead_memories_26_6a49209120.jpg",uid:1748},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Deafheaven",uid:1203}],end:"1785512700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785510000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2716}],pathSegment:"deafheaven",title:"Deafheaven",uid:1203},biography:"<p>Deafheaven sound like a black‑metal thunderstorm crashing through a wall of shoegaze haze. Blast beats, huge guitars and that strange mix of chaos and beauty. Their songs can feel like lightning and sunshine at the same time. On the Wacken stage that turns into a full‑on weather system.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Deafheaven klingen, als würde ein Black‑Metal-Sturm durch eine Wand aus Shoegaze-Nebel brechen. Blastbeats, große Gitarrenflächen und diese seltsame Mischung aus Chaos und Schönheit. Ihre Songs können gleichzeitig wie ein Gewitter und wie Sonnenlicht durch Wolken wirken. Auf Wacken dürfte das ziemlich spektakulär aussehen – irgendwo zwischen Sturmfront und Gänsehaut.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/deafheaven/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2h_WVPSoMwU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"deafheaven_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/deafheaven_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36373}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4586,uri:"https://www.deafheavenuk.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4587,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/deafheaven/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4588,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/deafheavenband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4589,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC97UMkZzchbn0uO-KFyq8ww"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4XpPveeg7RuYS3CgLo75t9",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/0/csm_deafheaven_26_4d801d532f.jpg",uid:1657},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Bulgarien",shortNameDe:"Bulgarien",shortNameEn:"Bulgaria",uid:22}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Death Row",uid:1264}],end:"1785409200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785408000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Bulgaria",uid:2662}],pathSegment:"death-row",title:"Death Row",uid:1264},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Death Row is a deathened groove metal band from Sofia, Bulgaria, formed in 2021 by a group of school friends. Their sound channels the aggression of '90s groove metal, thrash, and hardcore — drawing from Pantera, Machine Head, Gojira, Trivium, and 90s hardcore — paired with introspective, poetic lyricism.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Highlights include Hills of Rock 2024, Polinerock Festival, S'cool Rock Fest (Plovdiv), Shiny Fest (Sofia), and an opening slot for Lazarvs in Plovdiv. They've also taken two national prizes: the 2023 Music Accelerator (which launched their debut single Patria in February 2024) and first place at Wolf Path Rock Fest in Chelopech. Their 2025 debut album was followed by their first nationwide tour — Sofia, Plovdiv, Burgas, Yambol, Varna — with new material currently in the works.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Death Row ist eine Deathened-Groove-Metal-Band aus Sofia, Bulgarien, 2021 von einer Gruppe Schulfreunde gegründet. Ihr Sound kanalisiert die Aggression des Groove Metal, Thrash und Hardcore der 90er – inspiriert von Pantera, Machine Head, Gojira, Trivium und der 90er-Hardcore-Szene – gepaart mit nachdenklicher, poetischer Lyrik.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Zu ihren Stationen zählen Hills of Rock 2024, das Polinerock Festival, S'cool Rock Fest (Plovdiv), Shiny Fest (Sofia) und ein Support-Auftritt für Lazarvs in Plovdiv. Dazu kommen zwei nationale Preise: der Music Accelerator 2023 (der ihre Debütsingle Patria im Februar 2024 ermöglichte) und der erste Platz beim Wolf Path Rock Fest in Chelopech. Auf ihr 2025er Debütalbum folgte ihre erste landesweite Tournee – Sofia, Plovdiv, Burgas, Yambol, Varna – während aktuell neues Material entsteht.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/death-row/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ci1jv9q67s",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"death_row_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/death_row_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37104}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4811,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gbtf_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4812,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/deathrowyambol"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3w90LwQOLSItebP6ivK0iz",subtitle:"Metal Battle Bulgaria",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/6/csm_death_row_26_1520597d2a.jpg",uid:1745},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Def Leppard",uid:1128}],end:"1785448800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785442500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2653}],pathSegment:"def-leppard",title:"Def Leppard",uid:1128},biography:`<p>Who’s got the hairspray? You’ll definitely need more of it for W:O:A 2026 if you want to match the style of these legends: Def Leppard are gracing the Holy Ground! Formed in 1977 in Sheffield, England, they rose from the New Wave of British Heavy Metal in the ‘80s to become a global Rock phenomenon – and to this day, they’re considered icons of Melodic Hardrock. With albums like <i>Pyromania</i> (1983) and the diamond-certified <i>Hysteria</i> (1987), they perfected the blend of hard riffs and Pop charm. They’ve shown resilience – even in the face of setbacks – and remain veterans of an era many still long for.</p>\r
<p>When Def Leppard take the stage, it feels like we’re back in the ’80s – hair high, leggings tight, and sugar on the go.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Braucht noch jemand Haarspray? Für das W:O:A braucht ihr definitiv mehr davon, wenn ihr den Style dieser Legenden wollt: Def Leppard beehren den Holy Ground! Gegründet 1977 in Sheffield, England werden sie in den 80ern zu einem globalen Rockphänomen – bis heute gelten sie als Ikonen des melodischen Hard Rock! Mit Alben wie Pyromania (1983) und dem Diamanten Hysteria (1987) perfektionieren sie den Mix aus harten Riffs gepaart mit Pop Charme. Sie zeigen trotz Rückschlägen Beständigkeit – und sind Veteranen einer Zeit, der viele hinterhertrauern. Wenn Def Leppard die Bühne betritt, fühlt es sich an, als wären wir wieder in den 80ern, die Haare hoch, die Leggings eng und der Zucker griffbereit.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/def-leppard/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZjBqZjGsmI5OAVsLSroaWQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Def_Leppard-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Def_Leppard-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34799}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4224,uri:"https://defleppard.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4225,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/defleppard"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4226,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/defleppard/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6H1RjVyNruCmrBEWRbD0VZ",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/4/csm_Def_Leppard-WOA26_27e5f4ed42.jpg",uid:1543},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Italien",shortNameDe:"Italien",shortNameEn:"Italy",uid:104}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Deflag",uid:1239}],end:"1785338700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785337500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Italy",uid:2628}],pathSegment:"deflag",title:"Deflag",uid:1239},biography:`<p class="text-justify">DEFLAG is a metal band from Italy — built on screaming, empathy, and adrenaline on stage. Formed in 2019, the lineup is Daniele (lead vocals), Lorenzo (guitars, backing vocals), Picci (bass, backing vocals), and Fabio (drums).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their music is direct, powerful, and reflective. Debut EP Let Us All Unite! (2021) earned strong reviews and led to an opening slot for (həd) p.e. in Milan the following year. Their second EP Of Scars And Sparrows (2025) captures the band's spirit at its core: alternating between pure headbanging and melodic intervals that hold back the rage.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">DEFLAG ist eine Metal-Band aus Italien – getragen von Geschrei, Empathie und Adrenalin auf der Bühne. Gegründet 2019, besteht das Line-up aus Daniele (Lead-Gesang), Lorenzo (Gitarre, Backing Vocals), Picci (Bass, Backing Vocals) und Fabio (Schlagzeug).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihre Musik ist direkt, kraftvoll und reflektiert. Die Debüt-EP Let Us All Unite! (2021) erntete starke Kritiken und führte ein Jahr später zu einem Support-Auftritt für (həd) p.e. in Mailand. Die zweite EP Of Scars And Sparrows (2025) bringt den Kern der Band auf den Punkt: ein Wechselspiel aus purem Headbanging und melodischen Passagen, die die Wut zurückhalten.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/deflag/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBFbFXh8ICs",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"deflag_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/deflag_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36970}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4737,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/deflag_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4738,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/deflaggers"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6p7LsQk1fiNzlm2P4Jrkic",subtitle:"Metal Battle Italy",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/b/csm_deflag_26_e9757893eb.jpg",uid:1715},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Diabolisches Werk",uid:1194}],end:"1785329100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785326400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2641}],pathSegment:"diabolisches-werk",title:"Diabolisches Werk",uid:1194},biography:"<p>The devil's work began a few years ago with a blood-stained logo, dark thoughts and a healthy dose of thundering Death Metal riffs. Today, we are seizing the opportunity to announce DIABOLISCHES WERK for Wasted Wednesday. See for yourself what this quartet from Kiel is capable of as they knock your senses out and draw you to the dark side with their sharpened scythe.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Des Teufels Werk begann vor ein paar Jahren mit einem blutverschmierten Logo, finsteren Gedanken und einer gehörigen Portion bretternder Death&nbsp;Metal-Riffs. Heute nutzen wir die Gunst der pechschwarzen Stunde und kündigen DIABOLISCHES WERK zum Wasted Wednesday an. Überzeugt euch selbst vom Können des Vierers aus Kiel, wenn sie euch um den Verstand knüppeln und mit der gewetzten Sense auf die böse Seite der Macht ziehen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/diabolisches-werk/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5ianco6vSU&list=RDl5ianco6vSU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"diabolisches_werk_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/diabolisches_werk_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36339}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4543,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/diabolisches_werk"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4544,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/DiabolischesWerk"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0mdu8tTvytKczjlIVh78oJ",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/3/csm_diabolisches_werk_26_584e2240f9.jpg",uid:1642},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:'Dieter "Maschine" Birr',uid:1204}],end:"1785592800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785589200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2777}],pathSegment:"dieter-maschine-birr",title:'Dieter "Maschine" Birr',uid:1204},biography:"<p>For&nbsp;many East German Metalheads, the&nbsp;name “Maschine” is impossible to&nbsp;avoid. As the&nbsp;frontman&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;legendary Puhdys, he was part&nbsp;of&nbsp;every&nbsp;respectable Amiga record&nbsp;collection. But Western fans&nbsp;know Dieter “Maschine” Birr as&nbsp;well. The legend has&nbsp;been&nbsp;touring solo for&nbsp;years — and Wacken wouldn’t&nbsp;be Wacken if&nbsp;this&nbsp;poet&nbsp;of&nbsp;loud and quiet&nbsp;moments&nbsp;didn’t&nbsp;step&nbsp;onto&nbsp;the Holy Ground. Legendary&nbsp;stuff — or&nbsp;as Doro would&nbsp;say: When East meets West…</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ostdeutschen Metalheads wird „Maschine“ zwangsläufig in ihrem Leben das ein oder andere Mal begegnet sein. Als Frontman der ikonischen Puhdys durfte er in keiner gut sortierten Amiga Sammlung fehlen. Aber auch Westdeutsche Connaisseurs können mit dem Namen Dieter Maschine Birr viel anfangen. Die Legende ist seit Jahren solo unterwegs und das Wacken Open Air wäre nicht das Wacken Open Air, wenn sie diesen Poeten mit den lauten und manchmal leisen Zwischentönen nicht auch auf dem Acker haben wollen würde. Das wird legendär oder um es mit Doro zu sagen:&nbsp; When East meets West…!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dieter-maschine-birr/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yg6B8tE9qbs",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dieter_maschine_birr_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dieter_maschine_birr_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36374}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4590,uri:"https://dieter-maschine-birr.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4591,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/dietermaschinebirr/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4592,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/dieter_maschine_birr/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"05K6aFMiBdDWGP1PhQtfIH",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/5/csm_dieter_maschine_birr_26b_a569706c0c.jpg",uid:1658},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Rumänien",shortNameDe:"Rumänien",shortNameEn:"Romania",uid:179}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dirty Shirt",uid:113}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:9},{artists:[{title:"Dirty Shirt",uid:113}],end:"1785352500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785348900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2639}],pathSegment:"dirty-shirt",title:"Dirty Shirt",uid:113},biography:`<p>A stain on your&nbsp;shirt? Annoying.</p>\r
<p>Dirty Shirt at W:O:A? Absolutely&nbsp;perfect.</p>\r
<p>The Romanian band has&nbsp;been&nbsp;around&nbsp;for&nbsp;nearly 30 years and remains&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hottest&nbsp;musical&nbsp;exports&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;country. Their wild mix of heavy styles&nbsp;earned&nbsp;them&nbsp;second&nbsp;place at the Wacken Metal Battle 2014. Time to&nbsp;return&nbsp;to&nbsp;the Holy Ground.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Flecken auf dem Shirt? Ärgerlich. Dirty Shirt auf dem W:O:A? Einfach nur herrlich. Die Rumänen haben mittlerweile fast 30 Lenzen auf dem Buckel und sind trotzdem immer noch einer der heißesten musikalischen Exportschlager aus dem europäischen Staat mit der sechstgrößten Bevölkerung. Ihr eigenwilliger Mix aus verschiedensten Elementen aus dem Hard und Heavy Bereich bescherte der Band den zweiten Platz bei den Wacken Metal Battles 2014. Zeit also endlich auf den Holy Ground zurückzukehren. Da können wir doch gut und gerne über ein paar Flecken auf unseren Textilien hinwegsehen oder?</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dirty-shirt/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=opWRDfHWV6Q",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dirty_Shirt_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dirty_Shirt_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36375}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4593,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/DirtyShirtRomania/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4594,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/dirtyshirtband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7lnoKzE5unKzShIzkjlTX7",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/d/csm_dirty_Shirt_26_d6b1aa60da.jpg",uid:1659},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Bosnien und Herzegowina",shortNameDe:"Bosnien und Herzegowina",shortNameEn:"Bosnia and Herzegovina",uid:17}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Divlje Jagode",uid:1170}],end:"1785528900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785525300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2741}],pathSegment:"divlje-jagode",title:"Divlje Jagode",uid:1170},biography:`<p>If any band deserves the title living witnesses of (Rock) history, it’s Divlje Jagode.</p>\r
<p>Led by almost-Whitesnake-guitarist Zele Lipovača, these Bosnian Hard Rock veterans have been celebrating the spirit of Rock ’N’ Roll for over 40 years – no matter how wild the world around them spun.</p>\r
<p>Tito, the fall of Yugoslavia, the Balkan War – none of it could stop Divlje Jagode.</p>\r
<p>And in 2026, they’ll stand on the Wacken stage for the very first time – just one year before their 50th (!) anniversary.</p>\r
<p>Welcome to Wacken, legends!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Divlje Jagode sind wohl das, was Chronisten als Zeitzeugen bezeichnen würden. Die bosnische Band um Beinahe Whitesnake Gitarristen Zele Lipovaca zelebriert seit über 40 Jahren klassischen Hardrock – auch wenn sich um sie herum oftmals die Welt rasant gedreht hat. Tito, der Zusammenbruch Jugoslawiens und der Balkankrieg, all das konnte Divlje Jagode nie etwas anhaben. Und so stehen sie 2026 zum ersten Mal auf der Bühne in Wacken. Ein weiterer Meilenstein in einer bewegten Bandgeschichte – kurz bevor ein Jahr später das 50. (!) Bandjubiläum ansteht. Willkommen in Wacken!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/divlje-jagode/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lOjHcWcogTE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"divlje_jagode_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/divlje_jagode_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35132}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4395,uri:"https://divlje-jagode.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4396,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/divljejagodeofficialpage"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4397,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/divlje_jagode_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4398,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/c/DivljeJagode"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6mMlq8oWkHZwC2rd2RZbYF",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/0/csm_divlje_jagode_26_e0a2c64203.jpg",uid:1600},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dritte Wahl",uid:1167}],end:"1785610800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785607200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2772}],pathSegment:"dritte-wahl",title:"Dritte Wahl",uid:1167},biography:"<p>Dritte Wahl aren’t nostalgia – they’re the kick in the present tense.<br />Their Punk has aged, but never tamed.<br />Lyrics that bleed without whining, choruses that know more than they shout.<br />Proof that conviction outshouts distortion.<br />Every stage becomes a street corner, every crowd a movement.<br />Punk with spine – because silence is always the worse choice.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Dritte Wahl sind keine Nostalgie – sie sind der Tritt in die Jetztzeit.<br />Ihr Punk ist gewachsen, aber nie gezähmt.&nbsp;Texte, die bluten, aber nicht jammern, Refrains, die mehr wissen als sie schreien. Diese Band ist der Beweis, dass Haltung lauter ist als jede Verzerrung.&nbsp;Jede Bühne wird zur Straßenecke, jede Crowd zur Bewegung.<br />Punk mit Rückgrat – weil Schweigen immer die schlechtere Wahl ist.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dritte-wahl/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QxEHtKlVAo",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Dritte_Wahl_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/Dritte_Wahl_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35115}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4375,uri:"https://drittewahl.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4376,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/drittewahl"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4377,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/dritte.wahl/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4378,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMbzG12xP5bXU4HctnorTcA"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7zhSE4Ry047wUsemXtAzq9",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/8/csm_Dritte_Wahl_26_89eac3e241.jpg",uid:1595},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dry And Shattered",uid:1250}],end:"1785176100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785200400",start:"1785132000",title:"Monday",uid:32},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785173400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2801}],pathSegment:"dry-and-shattered",title:"Dry And Shattered",uid:1250},biography:"<p>A wrecking ball is rumbling through the peaceful streets of Lausanne: since 2022, Yann, Romain, Léo, and Gabriel have been tearing through the underground under the banner of Dry and Shattered, fusing classic Death Metal with the uncompromising brutality of Hardcore. If you’re looking for cheesy melodies, you’ve come to the wrong place. This band dives straight into the darkest depths of the human psyche, wrapped in a merciless, completely self-produced sonic assault. It’s a whipping, raw bastard of blast beats and guaranteed mosh pits that will put the very foundations of the Landgasthof to the ultimate test!<br />&nbsp;</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Durch das beschauliche Lausanne rumpelt die Abrissbirne: Seit 2022 fegen Yann, Romain, Léo und Gabriel unter dem Banner Dry and Shattered durch den Underground und kreuzen klassischen Death Metal mit der kompromisslosen Brutalität des Hardcores. Wer bei den Schweizern nach kitschigen Melodien sucht, kann lange warten: Hier geht tief in die menschlichen Abgründe, verpackt in ein unbarmherziges Soundgewand, das komplett in Eigenregie geschmiedet wurde. Ein peitschender, ungeschönter Bastard aus Blastbeats und Mosh-Garantie, der ohne Umwege direkt das Fundament des Landgasthofs testen wird.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dry-and-shattered/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RZKZ0wQIK4",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dry_and_shattered_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dry_and_shattered_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37048}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4769,uri:"https://dryandshattered.bandcamp.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4770,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/dryandshattered/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4771,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/dry_and_shattered/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4hdpm4V8iCL4ticCVHFYRn",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/3/csm_dry_and_shattered_26_22042622b9.jpg",uid:1728},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Bosnien und Herzegowina",shortNameDe:"Bosnien und Herzegowina",shortNameEn:"Bosnia and Herzegovina",uid:17}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Dubioza Kolektiv",uid:1179}],end:"1785526200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785522600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2733}],pathSegment:"dubioza-kolektiv",title:"Dubioza Kolektiv",uid:1179},biography:"<p>Life is fun – and we want to celebrate that with you at W:O:A! Reason enough to welcome the Dub band DUBIOZA KOLEKTIV from Bosnia and Herzegovina as the mood makers. Percussion, accordion, guitar and lots of good vibes will get you dancing. Even more than 20 years after the release of their self-titled debut album, their mix of Punk, Ska, Rock and many other styles is still full of energy and shows that the Balkans are a perfect fit for Wacken.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Das Leben macht Spaß – und das wollen wir mit euch auf dem W:O:A feiern! Grund genug die Dub-Band DUBIOZA KOLEKTIV aus Bosnien und Herzegowina als Stimmungsmacher willkommen zu heißen. Percussion, Akkordeon, Gitarre und jede Menge gute Laune bringen euch zum Tanzen. Auch über 20 Jahre nach der Veröffentlichung des selbstbetitelten Debütalbums ist die Mischung aus Punk, Ska, Rock und vielen weiteren Stilen noch voller Energie und zeigt, dass der Balkan bestens zu Wacken passt.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/dubioza-kolektiv/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FZZJeMKJV3M",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"dubioza_kollektiv26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/dubioza_kollektiv26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35757}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4448,uri:"https://dubioza.org"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4449,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/dubioza"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4450,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/dubiozagram"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4451,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSlEdyj6I4TX8mcGwL8rVlw"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"02IFYoziC7CpQRK8fbehUY",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/8/csm_dubioza_kollektiv26_190126a762.jpg",uid:1614},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kroatien",shortNameDe:"Kroatien",shortNameEn:"Croatia",uid:93}],events:[{artists:[{title:"E.N.D.",uid:1226}],end:"1785403200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785402000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Balkan Regions",uid:2660}],pathSegment:"end",title:"E.N.D.",uid:1226},biography:`<p class="text-justify">E.N.D. (Evil Never Dies) is a tech-groove metal/hardcore band from Zadar, Croatia. Formed in 1996, they're one of the longest-running and most steadfast names in the Croatian metal underground — celebrating 30 years of activity at Wacken Open Air 2026.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Built around brothers Alen and Davor Babin, the band has played hundreds of shows and supported the likes of Testament, Decapitated, The Ocean, Municipal Waste, God Dethroned, Negură Bunget, and Xentrix. Veterans of Brutal Assault, Metalcamp, Euroblast, and Monte Paradiso, E.N.D. arrive at Wacken with a surprise: a four-piece "two-bass attack" lineup that secured their slot. If you're into Meshuggah, Bury Your Dead, The Haunted, or After The Burial — don't miss this.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">E.N.D. (Evil Never Dies) ist eine Tech-Groove-Metal/Hardcore-Band aus Zadar, Kroatien. Gegründet 1996, zählt sie zu den dienstältesten und unbeirrbarsten Namen des kroatischen Metal-Undergrounds – und feiert 2026 beim Wacken Open Air ihr 30-jähriges Bestehen.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Im Zentrum der Band stehen die Brüder Alen und Davor Babin. Hunderte Shows später haben sie unter anderem Testament, Decapitated, The Ocean, Municipal Waste, God Dethroned, Negură Bunget und Xentrix supportet. Veteranen von Brutal Assault, Metalcamp, Euroblast und Monte Paradiso, kommen E.N.D. mit einer Überraschung nach Wacken: einem vierköpfigen Line-up mit zwei Bässen, das ihnen den Sieg sicherte. Fans von Meshuggah, Bury Your Dead, The Haunted oder After The Burial sollten sich das nicht entgehen lassen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/end/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NAKCAswHjXE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"end_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/end_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36691}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4697,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/endbandmetal"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4698,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/endbandmetal"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4699,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/ENDband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7cJcHV7KcFh4BT9OCUjC44",subtitle:"Metal Battle Balkan Regions",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/a/csm_end_26_cc8178d602.jpg",uid:1697},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Einherjer",uid:352}],end:"1659727800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659724200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:642},{artists:[{title:"Einherjer",uid:352}],end:"1722626100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722654000",start:"1722578400",title:"Friday",uid:21},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722622500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"(30th Anniversary Show)",uid:1577},{artists:[{title:"Einherjer",uid:352}],end:"1785618900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785615300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2781}],pathSegment:"einherjer",title:"Einherjer",uid:352},biography:`<p>What Valhalla is to Vikings, the Holy Ground is to us metalheads. And for some, the two even go hand in hand. Einherjer are something like the patron saints of all those who both honor the Holy Ground and long for entry into Valhalla. Musically somewhere between Folk, Metal, and a certain vocal extravagance, the band has been on a grand journey since 2004.</p>\r
<p>And who knows – maybe the Holy Ground is what they’ve been searching for all along: Valhalla!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Was für Vikinger Walhalla ist, ist für uns Metalheads der Holy Ground. Für manche geht sogar beides irgendwie zusammen.<br />Einherjer sind so etwas wie die Schutzpatronen all jener, die sowohl den Holy Ground (ver-) ehren, als auch einen Eintritt nach Walhalla ersehnen.<br />Musikalisch irgendwo zwischen Folk, Metal und einer gewissen gesanglichen Extravaganz, ist die Band bereits seit 2004 auf großer Suche.</p>\r
<p>Und wer weiß: Vielleicht ist ja der Holy Ground das, was sie schon so lange sucht – Walhalla!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/einherjer/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/einherjerofficial",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Einherjer-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Einherjer-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34841}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4341,uri:"https://einherjer.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4342,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/einherjerofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4343,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/einherjerofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0iGkBvuI18nxqJR8Ipg1cu",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/2/csm_Einherjer-WOA26_9393fba15b.jpg",uid:1585},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Finnland",shortNameDe:"Finnland",shortNameEn:"Finland",uid:67}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Eläkeläiset",uid:1129}],end:"1785519900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785516300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2732}],pathSegment:"elaekelaeiset",title:"Eläkeläiset",uid:1129},biography:"<p>Wenn ihr Eläkeläiset fünf Mal schnell hintereinander sagen könnt, erscheint euch heute Nacht der Humppa Gott und nimmt euch mit auf eine Reise in die Tiefen des Offbeats und der Akkordeons. Oder ihr habt einfach Tickets für das W:O:A 2026 und könnt den finnischen Großmeistern höchstselbst bei der Arbeit zusehen. Wer diesen Titel ernsthaft in Frage stellen möchte, möge uns bitte vorlegen, welche Band sonst einen ähnlichen Kultstatus in Hacker-Kreisen genießt und es seit Mitte der 1990er Jahre geschafft hat kontinuierlich den heiligen Acker zu besuchen. Wir warten dann mal.</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Try saying Eläkeläiset five times fast and the Humppa god himself might appear to drag you into the realm of offbeat madness and accordion mayhem.</p>\r
<p>Or, better yet, just grab your ticket for W:O:A 2026 and witness Finland’s Humppa overlords doing what they do best.</p>\r
<p>Honestly – if anyone dares to question their cult status among hackers, drinkers, and Metalheads alike, we’d love to hear which other band has ruled the Holy Ground since the mid-90s with such chaotic brilliance.</p>\r
<p>We’ll wait…&nbsp;</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/elaekelaeiset/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbHpRt9ZXNIAY8C4lwjrshA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Elaekelaeiset-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Elaekelaeiset-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34800}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4227,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/elakelaiset/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4228,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Elakelaiset"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4229,uri:"https://www.humppa.com/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3HKoyHD86fikvLBdecyl5j",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/d/csm_Elaekelaeiset-WOA26_0517340ca3.jpg",uid:1544},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Mexiko",shortNameDe:"Mexiko",shortNameEn:"Mexico",uid:148}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Elchivo",uid:1225}],end:"1785343200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785342000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Mexico",uid:2617}],pathSegment:"elchivo",title:"Elchivo",uid:1225},biography:`<p class="text-justify">ELCHIVO is a Stoner Rock and Doom Metal band from Monterrey, Mexico, formed in 2018. Founded by Marco Gil (originally of Maligno), the lineup is rounded out by Stefan Berdem (drums), Viin Angelini (vocals), and Roi Zerda (guitars).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their 2020 self-titled debut LP earned national recognition, including nominations for Stoner Rock Album of the Year and New Band of the Year. The band now returns with their new album Under the Black Sun — nine tracks exploring new sounds and textures while keeping the essence that defines them. The first single, "The Unforeseen", is out now, with festival dates in Mexico and beyond on the horizon.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">ELCHIVO ist eine Stoner-Rock- und Doom-Metal-Band aus Monterrey, Mexiko, gegründet 2018. Gestartet von Marco Gil (ehemals Maligno), wird das Line-up komplettiert durch Stefan Berdem (Schlagzeug), Viin Angelini (Gesang) und Roi Zerda (Gitarre).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr selbstbetiteltes Debütalbum (2020) brachte landesweite Anerkennung, darunter Nominierungen als „Stoner-Rock-Album des Jahres" und „Neue Band des Jahres". Mit ihrem neuen Album Under the Black Sun melden sie sich nun zurück – neun Tracks, die neue Klänge und Texturen ausloten, ohne die eigene Essenz zu verlieren. Die erste Single „The Unforeseen" ist bereits draußen, Festivalauftritte in Mexiko und international stehen vor der Tür.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/elchivo/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Al1XpQI_Ktc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"elchivo_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/elchivo_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36690}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4694,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/elchivotemple"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4695,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/elchivotemple"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4696,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@ELCHIVOtemple"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4irE4oDcl1EOiQxc4T9kNc",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/f/csm_elchivo_26_576ae82fc4.jpg",uid:1696},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Electric Bassboy",uid:1193}],end:"1785351600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785348000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2601}],pathSegment:"electric-bassboy",title:"Electric Bassboy",uid:1193},biography:`<p><strong>Electric Bassboy</strong>&nbsp;is the electronic troublemaker born from Electric Callboy —<br />&nbsp;the project where they ditch the guitars, twist the knobs, and crank the bass so hard even seasoned metalheads start wondering whether to headbang or simply hold on.</p>\r
<p>Hardstyle, rave, full-throttle chaos — delivered at a pace that makes the circle pit question its life choices.<br />&nbsp;Electric Bassboy doesn’t show up to play a polite DJ set;<br />&nbsp;he shows up to prove what&nbsp;<strong>pure, unfiltered mayhem</strong>&nbsp;sounds like without a single guitar involved.</p>\r
<p><strong>Loud. Ridiculous. Absolutely legendary.</strong></p>`,biographyDe:`<p><strong>Electric Bassboy</strong>&nbsp;ist die elektronische Problemseite von Electric Callboy – das Projekt, bei dem sie die Gitarren gegen Knöpfe tauschen und den Bass so aufdrehen, dass selbst gestandene Metaller kurz überlegen, ob man dazu headbangt oder einfach nur überlebt.</p>\r
<p>Hardstyle, Rave, Abriss – alles in einer Geschwindigkeit, bei der sogar der Circle Pit nervös wird.<br />&nbsp;Electric Bassboy kommt nicht, um höflich aufzulegen, sondern um Wacken zu zeigen, wie sich&nbsp;<strong>Eskalation ohne Verzerrer</strong>&nbsp;anhört.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/electric-bassboy/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ST007Aa7IgE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"electric_bassboy26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/electric_bassboy26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35818}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4530,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/electricbassboy"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4531,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61576887755965"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5OhB4WP6o9odTeJS6rEC9g",subtitle:"Sideproject Electric Callboy",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/3/csm_electric_bassboy26_c1af9b52ad.jpg",uid:1639},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Emperor",uid:1130}],end:"1785535200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785530700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:'"Best of" + Emperor EP w. original Lineup',uid:2711}],pathSegment:"emperor",title:"Emperor",uid:1130},biography:`<p>Bow down, mortals – <strong>Emperor</strong> will rise again to unleash a monumental Black Metal ritual at Wacken!</p>\r
<p>For one night only, they will summon the darkness - beyond and array of their full works specially concentration on their self-titled debut EP.</p>\r
<p>This will not be just a show. It’s a black mass, a tribute to the record that changed the face of Extreme Metal forever.</p>\r
<p>And it gets darker… The legendary original lineup is reforged.</p>\r
<p>Wacken will never be the same.</p>\r
<p>Come witness history, darkness, and triumph –</p>\r
<p>The night belongs to the trve.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Bow down, Mortals! &nbsp;– <strong>EMPEROR</strong> erheben sich erneut, um ein monumentales Black Metal-Ritual über Wacken zu entfesseln!</p>\r
<p>Nur für eine einzige Nacht beschwören sie die Dunkelheit – ein finsteres Best-of aus ihrem Schaffen, mit besonderem Fokus auf ihrer legendären erste EP “Emperor”</p>\r
<p>Doch das hier wird kein normales Konzert.</p>\r
<p>Das ist eine schwarze Messe.</p>\r
<p>Ein Tribut an das Werk, das das Gesicht des Extreme Metal für immer verändert hat.</p>\r
<p>Und es wird noch dunkler… denn die legendäre Originalbesetzung ist zurück:</p>\r
<p>Wacken wird danach nicht mehr sein, wie es war.</p>\r
<p>Seid dabei, wenn Geschichte, Dunkelheit und Triumph aufeinandertreffen –</p>\r
<p>This night belongs to the trve.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/emperor/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTIEXqlu73zjJIgNd8tercg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Emperor-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Emperor-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34801}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4230,uri:"https://www.emperorhorde.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4231,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/emperorofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4232,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/emperorbandofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6jPWrSmxOd9mj7Xaj4EP2Y",subtitle:"Best-of + Emperor EP Set",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/2/csm_Emperor-WOA26_d4f869c941.jpg",uid:1545},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Employed To Serve",uid:557}],end:"1691149500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1691146800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:995},{artists:[{title:"Employed To Serve",uid:557}],end:"1785498300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785495600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2714}],pathSegment:"employed-to-serve",title:"Employed To Serve",uid:557},biography:"<p>When they rocked the Holy Ground in 2023, one thing was certain: We'll see each other again soon. EMPLOYED TO SERVE are coming to the anniversary edition of W:O:A with their new album ‘Fallen Star’ in tow. Fans of Metalcore, Post-Hardcore and Mathcore will get their money's worth! If you want to prepare yourself, you can listen to the current single ‘Atonement’, which was recorded together with Lorna Shore singer Will Ramos.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Als sie 2023 den Holy Ground zum Beben brachten, stand fest: Wir sehen uns wieder. EMPLOYED TO SERVE kommen mit ihrem neuen Album „Fallen Star“ im Gepäck zum Jubiläumsfestival nach Wacken. Fans von Metalcore, Post-Hardcore und Mathcore kommen voll auf ihre Kosten! Wer sich optimal auf diesen Abriss vorbereiten möchte, kann in die aktuelle Single „Atonement“ reinhören, welche gemeinsam mit Lorna Shore-Sänger Will Ramos aufgenommen wurde.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/employed-to-serve/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rWI586git0s",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"employed_to_serve26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/employed_to_serve26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35819}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4512,uri:"https://www.employedtoserve.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4513,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/employedtoserve"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4514,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/employedtoserve/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"58d50jBQXhOetEGuSBgu64",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/a/csm_employed_to_serve26_631874c4dd.jpg",uid:1633},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Europe",uid:1131}],end:"1785435300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785430800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2652}],pathSegment:"europe",title:"Europe",uid:1131},biography:"<p>It took only one song to catapult the next band into the hall of fame: “The Final Countdown.” Founded in 1979 in Sweden, Europe has far more to offer than just that one synth riff. Joey Tempest’s voice remains unchanged to this day, as if preserved in a time capsule. Europe delivers stadium-worthy performances that you’ll remember – and want – for a long time to come! Now the giants are landing at Wacken, and we can’t wait to roar along with them to all their famous songs!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Es brauchte nur einen einzigen Song, um die nächste Band in den Olymp zu katapultieren: „The Final Countdown“. Gegründet 1979 in Schweden, hat Europe dennoch weit mehr zu bieten als nur dieses eine Synth-Riff. Joey Tempests Stimme ist bis heute unverändert als hätte er sie in einer Zeitkapsel konserviert, gibt Europe Stadiontaugliche Performances, an die man sich noch lange danach erinnern kann, und vor allem will! Nun landen die Giganten auf Wacken und wir können es gar nicht erwarten mit ihnen zusammen zu all-bekannten Songs mitzusingen!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/europe/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/user/europethebandtv",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Europe-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Europe-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34802}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4233,uri:"https://www.europetheband.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4234,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/europetheband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4235,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/officialeuropetheband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7Js6Lde8thlIHXggv2SCBz",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/3/csm_Europe-WOA26_9d76063492.jpg",uid:1546},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Evil Jared & Krogi",uid:1205}],end:"1785442500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785438900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2693}],pathSegment:"evil-jared-krogi",title:"Evil Jared & Krogi",uid:1205},biography:"<p>When Evil Jared &amp; Krogi show up, expect everything except a normal concert. Punk spirit, rock groove and pure WTF-chaos collide. Crowd antics, random madness, things getting weird in the best possible way. Basically the kind of beautiful mayhem a festival like Wacken was built for.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn Evil Jared und Krogi auftauchen, sollte man sich auf alles vorbereiten – außer auf ein normales Konzert. Zwischen Punk-Spirit, Rock-Groove und völliger WTF_Eskalation wird aus der Bühne schnell eine Partyzone. Hier kann alles passieren: spontane Aktionen, absurde Momente, Publikum mitten im Chaos. Kurz gesagt: genau der Wahnsinn, den ein Festival wie Wacken manchmal braucht.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/evil-jared-krogi/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YOKQIWZ27aY",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"evil_jared_krogi26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/evil_jared_krogi26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36376}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4595,uri:"https://eviljaredxkrogi.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4596,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/EVILJAREDXKROGI"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4597,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/eviljared_x_krogi/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"766CPWJo4muxhGzhTmI8dv",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/5/csm_evil_jared_krogi26_9d4bb77d9d.jpg",uid:1660},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Expellow",uid:1111}],end:"1753874700",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1753873500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Switzerland",uid:2378},{artists:[{title:"Expellow",uid:1111}],end:"1785332700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785329100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2626}],pathSegment:"expellow",title:"Expellow",uid:1111},biography:"<p>Sometimes&nbsp;they&nbsp;come back — and in the&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;Expellow, they do so quickly. The winners&nbsp;of last year’s Wacken Metal Battle will storm&nbsp;the Holy Ground again&nbsp;in 2026. The Swiss Metalcore machine&nbsp;around&nbsp;frontwoman Mik Dean knows&nbsp;the&nbsp;field&nbsp;inside and out — and will once&nbsp;again&nbsp;put&nbsp;their well-oiled&nbsp;brutality&nbsp;engine at the&nbsp;disposal&nbsp;of&nbsp;every&nbsp;pit&nbsp;enthusiast. Oh, and they’re&nbsp;celebrating&nbsp;their 20th anniversary. Sounds like a proper party, right?</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Manchmal kommen sie wieder. Im Falle von Expellow sogar ziemlich zügig. Die letztjährigen Gewinner des Wacken Metal Battles werden 2026 den Holy Ground erneut stürmen. Die Schweizer Metalcore-Walze um Frontfrau Mik Dean, die den Holy Ground aus dem Vorjahr noch in und auswendig kennen dürfte, wird ihre gut geölte Brutalo Maschine wieder großzügigerweise allen Moshpit afficionados zur Verfügung stellen. Außerdem feiert der sympathische Fünfer 20-jähriges Bandjubiläum. Es ist also alles für ein rauschendes Fest angerichtet.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/expellow/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQltMCDb75k",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"expellow_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/expellow_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36413}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4598,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/expellow/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4599,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/expellow_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7n7ZqJDzdKrZul0UjAWUhC",subtitle:"Metal Battle Winner 2025",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/b/csm_expellow_26b_f274263240.jpg",uid:1661},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Faun",uid:567}],end:"1691097300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691110800",start:"1691042400",title:"Thursday",uid:14},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1691093700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:974},{artists:[{title:"Faun",uid:567}],end:"1785532500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785528900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2734}],pathSegment:"faun",title:"Faun",uid:567},biography:"<p>Once again, The Holy Land opens its gates for passionate storytellers, glorious jesters, and fantastic epics of all kinds. No surprise that <strong>Faun</strong> feel right at home here. The Munich-based pagan rock group stands for captivating and elegant storytelling and has been the go-to source for atmospheric journeys into realms and eras beyond our imagination for 26 years. Welcome back to the Holy Ground!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Das Holy Land öffnet wieder einmal seine Pforten für passionierte Geschichtenerzähler, glorreiche Gaukler und fantastische Epen aller Art. Keine Überraschung, dass sich Faun hier direkt angesprochen fühlen. Die Münchner Pagan Rock Gruppe steht für eingängiges und elegantes Geschichtenerzählen und ist seit 26 Jahren der Hauptansprechpartner für stimmungsvolle Ausflüge in Reiche und Zeiten außerhalb unserer Vorstellungskraft. Willkommen zurück auf dem Holy Ground!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/faun/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxWwz-uZkTNwEM_duLUrWkQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Faun2-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Faun2-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34855}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4316,uri:"https://faune.de/de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4317,uri:"https://de-de.facebook.com/FaunOfficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4318,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/faunofficial/?hl=de"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2wPOgnQ6eW3X73uIJZ4YFE",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/4/csm_Faun2-WOA26_dec165b202.jpg",uid:1576},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Finsterforst",uid:1206}],end:"1785611700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785608100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2780}],pathSegment:"finsterforst",title:"Finsterforst",uid:1206},biography:"<p>They sing about mystical creatures, nature and its destruction by humans. Their music is dark, with Folk elements mixed in and it's no surprise that FINSTERFORST hail from the gloomy Black Forest. Their unique blend of Pagan, Post and Black Metal with epic orchestral parts and powerful choirs has made the band a fixture on the scene, and we can't wait to welcome the Black Forest metallers to the Holy Ground for the second time.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie singen von mystischen Geschöpfen, der Natur und ihrer Zerstörung durch den Menschen. Ihre Musik ist dunkel, folkige Elemente mischen sich unter und es verwundert nicht, dass FINSTERFORST aus dem düsteren Schwarzwald kommen. Ihre ureigene Mischung aus Pagan, Post und Black Metal mit epischen Orchesterparts und mächtigen Chören macht die Band zu einer festen Größe in der Szene und wir können es kaum erwarten die Black Forest-Metaller zum zweiten Mal auf dem Holy Ground zu begrüßen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/finsterforst/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8jGNLxrIfWKdMXwyzhQgEQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"finsterforst_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/finsterforst_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36378}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4600,uri:"https://www.finsterforst.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4601,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/FinsterforstOfficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4602,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/finsterforst_official"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1Gh3UMZ0WVesXifHfziSx9",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/8/csm_finsterforst_26_1eb394d15b.jpg",uid:1662},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Firespawn",uid:1132}],end:"1785427200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785424500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2676}],pathSegment:"firespawn",title:"Firespawn",uid:1132},biography:"<p>Firespawn are back! Formed in 2015 as a Swedish Death Metal supergroup, the five-piece had to face a heavy loss six years later with the passing of founding member and national Death Metal legend L.G. Petrov. Now they return with a new vocalist, ready to blast us with their old-school-soaked riffs. The flames are burning fiercer than ever – just in time to celebrate our anniversary together!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Firespawn sind zurück! Als schwedische Death Metal Supergroup 2015 gegründet musste der Fünfer sechs Jahre nach seiner Gründung den Tod von Gründungsmitglied und nationaler Death Metal Legende L.G. Petrov verkraften. Jetzt sind sie mit neuem Sänger zurück und bereit uns ihre Old-School getränkten Riffs, um die Ohren zu hauen. Das Feuer dürfte heftiger lodern als jemans zuvor – genau richtig, um mit uns Jubiläum zu feiern!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/firespawn/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClEXJQi6NgcjfPHftGfoxlg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Firespawn-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Firespawn-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34803}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4236,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/firespawnofficial/?locale=de_DE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4237,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/firespawn_official/?hl=de"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6iuACyGPyhtixKHUiJ8mNu",subtitle:"In Memory Of LG Petrov",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/3/csm_Firespawn-WOA26_b9d52bcc7e.jpg",uid:1547},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Fit For An Autopsy",uid:1207}],end:"1785624300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785620700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2767}],pathSegment:"fit-for-an-autopsy",title:"Fit For An Autopsy",uid:1207},biography:`<p>“Metal&nbsp;isn’t&nbsp;dangerous&nbsp;anymore.”</p>\r
<p>Ever catch yourself&nbsp;thinking&nbsp;that? Then&nbsp;you&nbsp;might&nbsp;simply&nbsp;be&nbsp;listening&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;wrong bands. Fit For An Autopsy&nbsp;from New Jersey bring everything&nbsp;needed&nbsp;to&nbsp;shock&nbsp;your well-behaved&nbsp;friends: brutal sounds, progressive elements and the&nbsp;nastiest&nbsp;Deathcore&nbsp;steamroller&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;imagine. Six guys&nbsp;who&nbsp;have&nbsp;been&nbsp;rearranging&nbsp;jaws&nbsp;for&nbsp;almost&nbsp;two&nbsp;decades. Now jump into&nbsp;the&nbsp;pit and prove&nbsp;this&nbsp;first&nbsp;sentence&nbsp;wrong.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>„Metal ist mittlerweile so angepasst und gar nicht mehr gefährlich. Wen soll man denn damit noch schocken?“. Ertappt ihr euch auch gelegentlich bei Gedanken wie diesen? Dann haben wir genau das richtige für euch, denn wahrscheinlich hört ihr einfach noch die falschen Bands! Die New Jersey Brutalos Fit For An Autopsy haben alles, was eure angepassten Spießer Freunde schockt! Ein bedrohlich klingender Name, noch bedrohlichere Sounds, die progressive Elemente mit dem Schlimmsten (also dem Besten) aus Deathcore und Metal mischen und wie eine Dampfwalze über alles hinwegbrettern, das Kommerz schreit. Fit For An Autopsy, das sind einfach nur sechs Jungs, die seit knapp 20 Jahren Kauleisten neu justieren. Streicht also am besten die ersten zwei Sätze dieses Textes ganz schnell aus eurem Wortschatz und springt genüsslich zu uns in den Pit.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/fit-for-an-autopsy/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jg84uvEin30",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"fit_for_an_autopsy_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/fit_for_an_autopsy_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36379}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4603,uri:"https://fitforanautopsy.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4604,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/FitForAnAutopsyOfficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4605,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/fitforanautopsy/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0qJpY7K8p7g6sacvaGNt6i",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/7/csm_fit_for_an_autopsy_26_1695f9334e.jpg",uid:1663},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Focus.",uid:622}],end:"1691145900",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1691143200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1008},{artists:[{title:"Focus.",uid:622}],end:"1785581100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785578400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2768}],pathSegment:"focus",title:"Focus.",uid:622},biography:`<p>Not to be confused with the Dutch Hard Rockers of the ’70s – Focus. from Germany are kicking in the door with both feet and childlike joy on the gas pedal.</p>\r
<p>Or as they put it themselves: “Armed with words and cigarette smoke against the darkness of simple beats and empty lyrics.”</p>\r
<p>The crew from Riesa are hitting Wacken Open Air with a brand-new album and a full-speed stop on their Sternhagelvoll 2026 tour. Buckle up – this ride’s about to get wild.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Nicht zu verwechseln mit den niederländischen Hard-Rockern der 70er steigen die deutschen Focus. mit beiden Beinen voran und fast schon kindlicher Freude aufs Gaspedal. Oder wie sie es selbst äußerst treffend formulieren: „Mit Wortgewalt und Zigarettenrauch gegen das Dunkel der einfachen Beats und simplen Texte.“</p>\r
<p>Die Riesaer kommen mit einem Album im Schlepptau auf das Wacken Open Air und nehmen uns auf ihrer Sternhagelvoll 2026 Tournee ins Visier. Und Abfahrt!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/focus/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wrOcjdUYYxw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"focus_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/focus_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35133}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4399,uri:"https://focus-band.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4400,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/focuspunkt/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4401,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/focuspunkt"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4402,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfy3ZO95T57cOPumygAc05w"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5TbE0PiXvN5JKGA6W6JybO",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/9/csm_focus_26_a98ab7e760.jpg",uid:1601},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Chile",shortNameDe:"Chile",shortNameEn:"Chile",uid:44}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Force",uid:1228}],end:"1785410700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785409500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Chile",uid:2672}],pathSegment:"force",title:"Force",uid:1228},biography:`<p class="text-justify">FORCE is a glam hard rock band from Melipilla and Santiago, Chile, founded by Laureano Starboy and Camila Sulwacker, together with bassist Hans Beyer. Their sound fuses 80s hard rock, heavy riffs, retrowave synths, and raw, classic-style vocals.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">In 2025, they released their debut single "Shine Like Me, B#tch!" followed by "SPEED" — both building toward their first LP, slated for 2026. Despite being active for only six months, FORCE won over jury and crowd alike at their national heat. In 2026, the band will also serve as the official opening act for HALESTORM in Chile.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">FORCE ist eine Glam-Hard-Rock-Band aus Melipilla und Santiago, Chile, gegründet von Laureano Starboy und Camila Sulwacker zusammen mit Bassist Hans Beyer. Ihr Sound vereint 80er-Hard-Rock, wuchtige Riffs, Retrowave-Synthesizer und rohen, klassischen Gesang.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">2025 erschien ihre Debütsingle „Shine Like Me, B#tch!", gefolgt von „SPEED" – beides Vorboten ihres ersten Albums, das für 2026 geplant ist. Obwohl erst seit sechs Monaten aktiv, überzeugten FORCE bei ihrem nationalen Vorentscheid sowohl Jury als auch Publikum. 2026 wird die Band außerdem als offizieller Opening-Act für HALESTORM in Chile auf der Bühne stehen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/force/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0qfZf2PnGvE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"force_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/force_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36693}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4703,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/forceband.cl"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4704,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Novelization"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4705,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@forceglam"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"527C8v9EOKmi9W2tApAIag",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/c/csm_force_26_9eb5006911.jpg",uid:1699},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Future Palace",uid:767}],end:"1722599100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722654000",start:"1722578400",title:"Friday",uid:21},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1722596400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1559},{artists:[{title:"Future Palace",uid:767}],end:"1785501900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785498300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2706}],pathSegment:"future-palace",title:"Future Palace",uid:767},biography:"<p>Only a few bands today are as widely praised for their innovation in metal as <strong>Future Palace</strong>. With their 2024 album <i>Distortion</i>, the Berlin-based trio has firmly secured their place among the top tier of modern metal bands. After their explosive Wacken show in 2024, the band now returns to the Holy Ground with renewed energy and even more confidence — ready to turn Wacken completely upside down this time. Their modern approach and effortless shifts through the various styles of metal have long since made them more than just an insider tip.</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Kaum eine Band wird aktuell wegen ihrer Innovation rund um den Metal so geschätzt wie Future Palace. Mit ihrem 2024 erschienenen Album Distortion haben sich die drei Berliner endgültig in die erste Riege moderner Metal Bands gespielt. Nach ihrer furiosen Wacken Show 2024 kehrt die Formation nun mit neuer Power und noch mehr Selbstbewusstsein auf den Holy Ground zurück, um Wacken dieses Mal komplett auf links zu drehen.</p>\r
<p>Ihr moderner Ansatz und ihr müheloses Wechseln durch die verschiedenen Spielarten des Metal machen sie schon längst zu keinem Geheimtipp mehr.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/future-palace/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJ47ISNx0lE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Future_Palace-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Future_Palace-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34831}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4313,uri:"https://future-palace.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4314,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/futurepalace"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4315,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/futurepalaceofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4QnuZOyl4C9d1keyOZXJ21",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/6/csm_Future_Palace-WOA26_03d8bb4d08.jpg",uid:1575},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Slowakei",shortNameDe:"Slowakei",shortNameEn:"Slovakia",uid:191}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Gagor",uid:1242}],end:"1785407700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785406500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Czech Republic",uid:2671}],pathSegment:"gagor",title:"Gagor",uid:1242},biography:`<p class="text-justify">GÁGOR is a "hard violence" band from Banská Bystrica, Slovakia. The five-piece have been performing live since 2021 — an energetic crew whose shows pull you out of your seat, and once your blood pressure spikes, you won't even mind a woman screaming at you.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their sound is a blend of heavy music genres with a strong, authentic underground vibe. Lyrics are written in Slovak and tackle themes that resonate with many people in today's world. The band self-released their self-titled debut album in 2023.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">GÁGOR ist eine „Hard Violence"-Band aus Banská Bystrica, Slowakei. Das Quintett steht seit 2021 auf der Bühne – eine energiegeladene Truppe, deren Shows einen aus dem Sitz reißen, und sobald der Blutdruck steigt, macht es einem auch nichts mehr aus, von einer Frau angeschrien zu werden.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr Sound vereint verschiedene härtere Spielarten mit einem starken, authentischen Underground-Vibe. Die Texte sind auf Slowakisch verfasst und greifen Themen auf, mit denen sich viele in der heutigen Welt identifizieren können. Ihr selbstbetiteltes Debütalbum erschien 2023 in Eigenregie.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/gagor/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rknOj_VyaP4",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"gagor_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/gagor_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36973}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4743,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gagor.band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4744,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/GAGORband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0QvKSLyY7ihGllIIAlbEju",subtitle:"Metal Battle Slovakia",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/d/csm_gagor_26_868f71af24.jpg",uid:1718},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Gannondorf",uid:1263}],end:"1785318300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785317100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB USA",uid:2622}],pathSegment:"gannondorf",title:"Gannondorf",uid:1263},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Gannondorf is an avant-garde extreme metal band from California, USA, fusing melodic black metal, atmospheric death metal, and progressive influences into a sound that's both aggressive and cinematic. Punishing riffs and visceral vocals meet layered arrangements, memorable melodies, and dynamic shifts that challenge genre conventions while staying rooted in extreme metal.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Lyrically, the band explores vengeance, power, sacrifice, and the collapse of once-great civilizations — evoking war-torn landscapes, forgotten rulers, and the struggle between ambition and destruction. Rather than leaning solely on speed and brutality, Gannondorf emphasizes storytelling and atmosphere, building songs that unfold as dark journeys.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Gannondorf ist eine Avantgarde-Extreme-Metal-Band aus Kalifornien, USA. Ihre Mischung aus melodischem Black Metal, atmosphärischem Death Metal und progressiven Einflüssen klingt ebenso aggressiv wie filmisch: wuchtige Riffs und schneidender Gesang treffen auf vielschichtige Arrangements, einprägsame Melodien und dynamische Wendungen, die Genre-Konventionen herausfordern, ohne ihre extreme Metal-Wurzeln zu verlieren.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Textlich kreist die Band um Rache, Macht, Opfer und den Untergang einst großer Zivilisationen – Bilder von kriegszerrissenen Landschaften, vergessenen Herrschern und dem ewigen Ringen zwischen Ehrgeiz und Zerstörung. Statt sich allein auf Geschwindigkeit und Brutalität zu verlassen, setzt Gannondorf auf Erzählung und Atmosphäre und formt Songs, die sich wie düstere Reisen entfalten.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/gannondorf/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auJEWowgnyY",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ganondorf_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ganondorf_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37103}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4810,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gannondorfmetalofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6HOB8sNatqHsDGAwMQei5N",subtitle:"Metal Battle USA",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/7/csm_ganondorf_26_282329a2d3.jpg",uid:1744},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"El Salvador",shortNameDe:"El Salvador",shortNameEn:"El Salvador",uid:198}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Gidora",uid:1233}],end:"1785416700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785415500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB El Salvador",uid:2674}],pathSegment:"gidora",title:"Gidora",uid:1233},biography:`<p class="text-justify">GIDORA is a groove/death metal band from El Salvador, formed in 2025 by four young musicians who blend the rhythmic power of groove metal with the aggression of death metal.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">The band stands out for a powerful yet accessible sound, energetic live performances, and well-balanced compositions — qualities that have driven their quick rise in popularity. Despite their short career, they've already shared stages with notable acts from Central and Latin America, establishing themselves as a solid and growing force within the Central American metal scene.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">GIDORA ist eine Groove-/Death-Metal-Band aus El Salvador, gegründet 2025 von vier jungen Musikern, die die rhythmische Wucht des Groove Metal mit der Aggression des Death Metal verbinden.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Die Band zeichnet sich durch einen kraftvollen, dennoch zugänglichen Sound, energiegeladene Live-Auftritte und ausgewogene Kompositionen aus – Eigenschaften, die ihren raschen Aufstieg vorangetrieben haben. Trotz ihrer noch kurzen Karriere haben sie bereits die Bühne mit namhaften Acts aus Mittel- und Lateinamerika geteilt und sich als feste, wachsende Größe in der zentralamerikanischen Metal-Szene etabliert.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/gidora/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mpys6_rpdjI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"gidora_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/gidora_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36964}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4725,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gidoraoficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4726,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Schonenbergv"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4cJUKhSNedofM9UgiAMl3L",subtitle:"Metal Battle El Salvador",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/c/csm_gidora_26_ed631fb6b6.jpg",uid:1709},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Japan",shortNameDe:"Japan",shortNameEn:"Japan",uid:107}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Given By The Flames",uid:1230}],end:"1785415200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785414000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Japan",uid:2664}],pathSegment:"given-by-the-flames",title:"Given By The Flames",uid:1230},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Given By The Flames is a gothic metalcore band from Tokyo, Japan. Over the years, they've shared stages with global acts and earned a reputation for emotionally intense performances that hit just as hard as they hurt.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their sound channels raw anger, sorrow, and beauty in equal measure — soaring clean vocals colliding with crushing breakdowns — driven by a creative mission to give voice to hidden emotions, both their own and the audience's. Recent releases like the singles "NIHIL" and "UNTIL WE MEET IN HELL AGAIN", alongside their full-length album A Book of Agony (now streaming), showcase their growth while staying true to their gothic metalcore roots.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Given By The Flames ist eine Gothic-Metalcore-Band aus Tokio, Japan. Über die Jahre hat sie Bühnen mit internationalen Acts geteilt und sich einen Namen für emotional aufgeladene Auftritte gemacht, die ebenso hart treffen wie sie schmerzen.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr Sound transportiert rohe Wut, Trauer und Schönheit zu gleichen Teilen – schwebende Cleangesänge prallen auf zermalmende Breakdowns –, getragen von dem kreativen Anspruch, verborgenen Emotionen eine Stimme zu geben, den eigenen wie denen des Publikums. Aktuelle Releases wie die Singles „NIHIL" und „UNTIL WE MEET IN HELL AGAIN" sowie ihr Album A Book of Agony (jetzt im Streaming) zeigen ihre Weiterentwicklung – ohne dabei ihre Gothic-Metalcore-Wurzeln zu verlieren.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/given-by-the-flames/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=caKmjqeyFrs",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"given_by_the_flames_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/given_by_the_flames_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36695}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4709,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gbtf_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4710,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/gbtfofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4711,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@gbtf_official"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3zig081GzEy52hB4SLF41Z",subtitle:"Metal Battle Japan",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/7/csm_given_by_the_flames_26_a72a8cc764.jpg",uid:1701},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Grand Magus",uid:1133}],end:"1785501900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785499200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2721}],pathSegment:"grand-magus",title:"Grand Magus",uid:1133},biography:`<p>Have you ever wondered what’s on the playlist of the Norse gods? We’ve got the answer: Grand Magus!&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>The Stockholm-based band began their journey as a doom outfit but quickly evolved into one of the most epic heavy metal groups in Europe. Their music sweeps across the field like hymns, feeling like the soundtrack to the gods’ most legendary battles. The sound is reminiscent of a mix between Manowar, Rainbow, and Black Sabbath – yet they bring their own unmistakable style. Especially thanks to frontman JB’s voice, which sinks into your brain like a siren’s song and demands to be followed. Grand Magus is a must at Wacken – especially for those ready to march into battle.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Habt ihr euch schon einmal gefragt, was man auf der Playlist von nordischen Göttern findet? Wir haben die Antwort: Grand Magus!&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Die Stockholmer Formation begann ihren Weg als Doom-Band, entwickelten sich aber schnell zu einer der epischsten Heavy-Metal Gruppen im europäischen Raum. Ihre Musik fegt wie Hymnen über den Platz und fühlen sich an, als wären sie der Soundtrack zu den epischsten Schlachten der Götter. Der Sound erinnert an eine Mischung aus Manowar, Rainbow und Black Sabbath und dennoch bringen sie ihren ganz eigenen Stil mit. Insbesondere durch Frontmann JB’s Stimme, die wie Sirenengesang sich in die Hirnhaut frisst und der man auf Schritt und Tritt folgen mag. Grand Magus ist auf Wacken Pflicht, vor allem für alle die bereit sind in die Schlacht zu ziehen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/grand-magus/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMMvpH0VOi0q8JrLT4PSCng",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Grand_Magus-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Grand_Magus-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34804}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4238,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/grandmagusofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4239,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/grandmagusband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4240,uri:"https://www.grandmagus.com/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7GTkjp7qsfmx8iJzBUQLmN",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/a/csm_Grand_Magus-WOA26_00bbab917e.jpg",uid:1548},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Grell",uid:1254}],end:"1785270600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785286800",start:"1785218400",title:"Tuesday",uid:33},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785267000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2807}],pathSegment:"grell",title:"Grell",uid:1254},biography:"<p>Dull and gray is a thing of the past - from now on, things are getting seriously loud and vibrant at the Landgasthof! Since 2022, the five-piece Crossover band GRELL from Neumünster has been sweeping across the country like a coastal storm, not giving a damn about genre boundaries. Fabian, David, Maxi, Yannik, and Arne fuse complex Rock breakdowns with melodic Rap verses and almost poetic lyrics that dig right where it hurts. The reason these guys strike a chord with anthems like Wimpernschlag or their heavy hitter Flutlicht comes down to their ultimate live philosophy: “Nothing but love!”. If you spend too much time overthinking and not enough time feeling with your heart, this North German five-piece provides the perfect release valve to drown your everyday worries in the mosh pit.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Grau und matt war gestern - ab jetzt wird es verdammt GRELL im Landgasthof! Die fünfköpfige Crossover-Band aus Neumünster fegt seit 2022 wie ein musikalischer Küstensturm durch die Republik und schert sich einen feuchten Kehricht um Genregrenzen. Fabian, David, Maxi, Yannik und Arne kreuzen anspruchsvolle Rock-Breakdowns mit melodischen Rap-Einlagen und fast schon poetischen Texten, die genau dort bohren, wo es wehtut. Dass die Jungs mit Hymnen wie Wimpernschlag oder ihrem Brett Flutlicht genau den Nerv der Zeit treffen, liegt vor allem an ihrer ultimativen Live-Philosophie: „Nichts als Liebe!”. Wer viel mit dem Kopf denkt und zu wenig mit dem Herzen fühlt, kriegt von diesem norddeutschen Fünfer das perfekte Ventil verpasst, um Alltagssorgen im Moshpit zu ertränken.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/grell/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-j7WQrfbko",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"grell_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/grell_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37052}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4779,uri:"https://grellmusik.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4780,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/grellmusik/?hl=de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4781,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/grellmusik/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1NTQB6cr4Anwiy4XftGcFM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/9/csm_grell_26_1900424ebd.jpg",uid:1733},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Guilt Trip",uid:1171}],end:"1785615300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785611700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2788}],pathSegment:"guilt-trip",title:"Guilt Trip",uid:1171},biography:`<p>Manchester isn’t just about football – it’s also a breeding ground for violent dancing and Hardcore devastation.</p>\r
<p>Guilt Trip prove it loud and clear.</p>\r
<p>In just ten short years, these five Mancunians have laid waste to stages across the globe with their crushing mix of Hardcore and Beatdown.</p>\r
<p>Armed with their new single Burn and a fresh deal with Roadrunner Records, another sonic assault is surely on the way.</p>\r
<p>Get ready for impact.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Dass Manchester neben Fußball auch im Bereich der harten Gitarrenmusik und der Welt der Violent Dancing Afficionados eine große Rolle spielt beweisen die Mancunians Guilt Trip. Gerade einmal zehn Jahre treiben die fünf Briten nun ihr Unwesen und legen die Bühnen dieser Welt mit ihrem brutalen Mix aus Hardcore und Beatdown in Schutt und Asche. Mit ihrer neuen Singe „Burn“ und dem Wechsel zu Roadrunner Records steht uns wohlmöglich bald die nächste Attacke der Band ins Haus. Ein echter Volltreffer.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/guilt-trip/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d5EUJXQKD1k",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"guilt_trip_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/guilt_trip_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35134}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4403,uri:"https://www.guilttripmhc.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4404,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/guilttripmhc/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4405,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/guilttripmhc/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4406,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLwfdu_6lmicZXx1RJj1mPg"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"07mhRucOGu6NJvRNVzqoxU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/b/csm_guilt_trip_26_524191a47e.jpg",uid:1602},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Tschechische Republik",shortNameDe:"Tschechische Republik",shortNameEn:"Czech Republic",uid:53}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Gutalax",uid:1134}],end:"1785497400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785493800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2695}],pathSegment:"gutalax",title:"Gutalax",uid:1134},biography:"<p>The next band is a total toilet disaster — literally! And we mean that in the most positive way possible. We’re talking about Gutalax! The Czech band is gracing W:O:A and bringing a whole lot of fun with them. Since their formation in 2009, Gutalax has become infamous for their infectious live shows — where toilet paper is never in short supply. And the music? Top-tier goregrind with guttural vocals, slapstick humor, and a guaranteed dance factor! Circle pits are old news — Gutalax are coming to the Holy Ground to kick off the <i>Toilet Pit</i>! So, grab your toilet paper and get ready!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Die nächste Band ist ein Griff ins Klo – wortwörtlich! Und wir meinen das im positivsten Sinne, in dem es möglich ist. Die Sprache ist von Gutalax! Die Tschechen beehren uns auf dem W:O:A und bringen jede Menge Spaß mit. Seit ihrer Gründung 2009 sind Gutalax berühmt-berüchtigt für ihre mitreißenden Live-Shows, bei denen mit dem Klopapier nicht gespart. Ach ja und die Musik? Feinster Goregrind mit knarzenden Vocals, Slapstick-Humor und garantiertem Tanzfaktor! Circle Pit war gestern, Gutalax kommen auf den Holy Ground, um den Toilet Pit zu starten, also packt euer 2-lagiges ein und macht euch bereit!&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/gutalax/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCstX-G8aztB8rPTgGkWMGtQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Gutalax-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Gutalax-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34805}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4241,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/gutalax.band_official/?hl=de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4242,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/gutalax.band/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5CmgfDQq0YVKMP6zpjYhPR",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/4/csm_Gutalax-WOA26_6c3c4625c6.jpg",uid:1549},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"H-Blockx",uid:1135}],end:"1785415500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785411900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2655}],pathSegment:"h-blockx",title:"H-Blockx",uid:1135},biography:"<p>They were often dubbed the German answer to Rage Against The Machine – The talk is of H-Blockx. Quality crossover, hip-hop vibes, and arena rock. Founded in 1991 in Münster, they rose to fame with songs like “Risin’ High” and “Move.” With chunky guitar riffs, unforgettable choruses, and rap vocals, H-Blockx carved out a name for themselves. They create the soundtrack for baggy pants, skateboards, and festivals where the mud still smelled like freedom. And what place could be more perfect for that than Wacken? We say: none!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Oft wurden sie als die deutsche Antwort zu Rage Against The Machine betitelt – Die Rede ist von H-Blockx. Gutes Crossover, Hip-Hop Vibes und Arenarock. Gegründet 1991 in Münster, wurden sie durch Songs wie „Risin‘ High“ und „Move“ bekannt. Die Mischung aus fülligen Gitarrenriffs mit Refrains, die einem nicht mehr aus dem Kopf gehen, und Rap-Vocals hat sich H-Blockx einen Namen gemacht. Sie schreiben die Musik für Baggy Pants, Skateboards und Festivals, bei denen der Schlamm noch nach Freiheit roch. Welcher Ort ist da perfekter als Wacken? Wir denken keiner!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/h-blockx/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/@HBlockx",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"H_Blockx-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/H_Blockx-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34806}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4243,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/HBLOCKXofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4244,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/HBLOCKXofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4245,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/hblockxofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1V3Nl0Y3EZwqP38KHws6vB",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/7/csm_H_Blockx-WOA26_c10c9dda61.jpg",uid:1550},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Hackneyed",uid:1172}],end:"1785621600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785618000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2789}],pathSegment:"hackneyed",title:"Hackneyed",uid:1172},biography:`<p>Right on time for their 20th anniversary, a legendary steamroller returns to the Holy Ground!</p>\r
<p>Hackneyed are back – a full decade after calling it quits – to blast away your skulls with roaring Death Metal once more.</p>\r
<p>We’ve been waiting for this, and we’re damn ready to have our brains rattled by these icons of the German scene.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Pünktlich zum 20-jährigen Bandjubiläum kehrt eine Dampfwalze mit Legendenstatus auf den Acker zurück. Hackneyed raffen sich auf, um zehn Jahre nach ihrer Auflösung unseren Durst nach röhrendem Death Metal zu stillen und wir sind auf jeden Fall bereit uns den Kopf ordentlich durchpusten zu lassen.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/hackneyed/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oa-4qjt8eW0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"hacknayed_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/hacknayed_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35135}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4407,uri:"https://hackneyed.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4408,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/hackneyed/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4409,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/hackneyedofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4410,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/HackneyedOfficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6Vp7LKfnmi4ONEUww3IjCj",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/f/csm_hacknayed_26_2bf550c457.jpg",uid:1603},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Malta",shortNameDe:"Malta",shortNameEn:"Malta",uid:144}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Haine",uid:1237}],end:"1785406200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785405000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Malta",uid:2661}],pathSegment:"haine",title:"Haine",uid:1237},biography:`<p class="text-justify">HAINE is a deathcore band from Malta, blending crushing breakdowns, melodic intensity, and deeply layered songwriting. Since forming in 2017, they've steadily built an international presence through powerful releases, cinematic visuals, and relentless evolution.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their latest album Fertile Void explores themes of human emotion, self-discovery, and transformation, pushing their sound into darker, more atmospheric territory. With a renewed lineup and a sharpened vision, HAINE enter 2026 heavier, more focused, and ready for the next chapter.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">HAINE ist eine Deathcore-Band aus Malta, die zermalmende Breakdowns, melodische Intensität und vielschichtiges Songwriting vereint. Seit ihrer Gründung 2017 hat die Band durch kraftvolle Releases, cinematische Visuals und beständige Weiterentwicklung stetig internationale Präsenz aufgebaut.</p>\r
<p>Ihr aktuelles Album Fertile Void behandelt Themen wie menschliche Emotion, Selbstfindung und Wandel und treibt ihren Sound in dunklere, atmosphärischere Gefilde. Mit erneuertem Line-up und geschärfter Vision gehen HAINE schwerer, fokussierter und bereit für das nächste Kapitel ins Jahr 2026.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/haine/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uxGSaTVtvTM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"haine_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/haine_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36968}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4733,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/haine.music"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4734,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/official.haine"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4SH9v6X1z8BEOL1E2JLgYd",subtitle:"Metal Battle Malta",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/c/csm_haine_26_0e543cf557.jpg",uid:1713},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:90},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1659626100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1659623400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Berlin Show",uid:545},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1659810600",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1659806100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:661},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1659633300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1659630600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:828},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1722729600",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722740400",start:"1722664800",title:"Saturday",uid:22},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1722724200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"VS. Finch",uid:1459},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1722716100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722740400",start:"1722664800",title:"Saturday",uid:22},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1722713400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"+ Finch",uid:1923},{artists:[{title:"Hämatom",uid:81}],end:"1785362400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785355200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2602}],pathSegment:"haematom",title:"Hämatom",uid:81},biography:`<p>Their paths lead in all directions, and next year the tour bus is heading to Wacken! In 2024, HÄMATOM celebrated a memorable show on the Holy Ground, did a concert-battle with rapper Finch, and still had to cope with the loss of their bassist and founding member West. We are excited to see what the loud and proud quartet prepares for next year. With their current album ‘Für Dich’ (2025), they pay tribute to West and have written plenty of new material for their set list. As always, the motto is: Join in, go wild, and if you have anything to complain about - ‘Erzähl es meinem Mittelfinger!’</p>\r
`,biographyDe:"<p>Ihre Wege führen in alle Himmelsrichtungen und nächstes Jahr fährt der Tourbus nach Wacken! HÄMATOM feierten 2024 eine Festivalshow der etwas anderen Art auf dem heiligen Acker, lieferten sich mit Rapper Finch ein Duell und hatten nach wie vor den Verlust ihres Bassisten und Gründungsmitglieds West zu verkraften. Wir sind gespannt, was das lautstarke Quartett für nächstes Jahr vorbereitet hat. Mit ihrem aktuellen Album „Für Dich“ (2025) zollen sie West Tribut und haben wieder ordentlich Nachschub für die Setlist geschrieben. Wie immer gilt: Mitmachen, abgehen und wer was zu meckern hat - „Erzähl es meinem Mittelfinger“!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/haematom/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ksTnXEHq3YM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"haematom_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/haematom_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35758}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4452,uri:"https://haematom.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4453,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/haematommusic"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4454,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/haematommusic"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4455,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/user/haematommusic"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/e/csm_haematom_26_a104ede3d5.jpg",uid:1615},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Hardline",uid:1173}],end:"1785599100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785596400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2764}],pathSegment:"hardline",title:"Hardline",uid:1173},biography:`<p>Hard Rock without wild backstories? Doesn’t exist.</p>\r
<p>But when your band’s formation at some time involved two members of Journey, you’re truly playing in a different league.</p>\r
<p>Hardline combine everything that makes the ’80s the decade of desire – with a line-up bursting with flair, melody, and groove.</p>\r
<p>Despite breakups and rebirths, the band’s fire never faded.</p>\r
<p>Time to party, old-school style!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Spannende, skurille oder beinahe unglaubliche Background Geschichten aus den 80ern gehören im Hard-Rock fast schon zum guten Ton. Unter den unzähligen Stories aber eine zu finden, in der zwei Journey Musiker bei der Gründung deiner Band dabei gewesen sind ist auch in diesem Kosmos exotisch.</p>\r
<p>Hardline verbinden alles, was uns die 80er zur Sehnsuchts-Dekade macht mit einem Line-Up, das vor Spielfreude und Flair nur so funkt. Und das trotz einer bewegten Bandhistorie mit mehrfacher Auflösung und Neugründung. Wir sind mehr als bereit für eine ordentlich Party!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/hardline/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rc3Ikk4As8U",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"hardline_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/hardline_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35136}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4411,uri:"https://www.hardlinerocks.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4412,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/hardlinerocks/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4413,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/hardlinerocks/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3caJ5Uy9aHZv7wVSNqwwjc",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/5/csm_hardline_26_73180980cd.jpg",uid:1604},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Hatebreed",uid:1185}],end:"1785520800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785517200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2709}],pathSegment:"hatebreed",title:"Hatebreed",uid:1185},biography:"<p>What can you say about the crew led by professional throat-shredder Jamey Jasta that hasn’t already been written in the chronicles of Hardcore and Metal? Hatebreed are pure cult — and have been for ages. The sheer brutality with which these Americans stir up their groove makes concrete look like jelly. If you’ve never lost your mind to Destroy Everything, can you really say you’ve been to a Hatebreed show? Your next chance: W:O:A 2026.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Was soll man zur Truppe um Berufsschreihals Jamey Jasta schreiben, was nicht bereits in etlichen Chroniken des Hardcores und Metal niedergeschrieben wurde? Hatebreed sind Kult und das nicht erst seit gestern. Die Brutalität, mit der die US-Amerikaner ihren Groove anmischen lässt, Zement aussehen wie Wackelpudding. Wer bei Destroy Everything nicht schon mal an einem anderen Schuh geschnuppert hat als dem eigenen kann wohl kaum von sich behaupten, wirklich auf einer Hatebreed Show gewesen zu sein. Nächste Chance W:O:A 2026.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/hatebreed/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IWU8wz6rvLc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"hatebreed_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/hatebreed_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35766}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4480,uri:"https://www.hatebreed.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4481,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/hatebreed"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4482,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/hatebreedofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4483,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@hatebreed"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"17Mb968quDHpjCkIyq30QV",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/6/csm_hatebreed_26_1a7dea75de.jpg",uid:1623},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Heartless Human Harvest",uid:1218}],end:"1785501000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785499200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2735}],pathSegment:"heartless-human-harvest",title:"Heartless Human Harvest",uid:1218},biography:`<p>Boundaries&nbsp;exist&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;tested. To&nbsp;walk&nbsp;along&nbsp;them — and to break them&nbsp;again and again. At least, if&nbsp;you&nbsp;ask&nbsp;us.</p>\r
<p>Luckily, we’ve&nbsp;found&nbsp;kindred&nbsp;spirits in Heartless Human Harvest. Somewhere&nbsp;between&nbsp;Metal and Hardcore, driven&nbsp;riffs and bone-shattering&nbsp;breakdowns, the northern German five-piece stands ready&nbsp;to turn the Holy Ground into&nbsp;their personal playground.</p>\r
<p>Be a part&nbsp;of&nbsp;the human harvest.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Grenzen sind dazu da sie neu auszuloten. Auf ihnen zu wandeln und sie immer wieder zu durchbrechen. Zumindest, wenn ihr uns nach unserer bescheidenen Meinung fragt. Wie gut, dass wir da in Heartless Human Harvest gleichgesinnte Mitstreiter gefunden haben. Zwischen Metal und Hardcore, treibenden Riffs und zerschmetternden Breakdowns thront der norddeutsche Fünfer und ist mehr als bereit, den Holy Ground zu seiner persönlichen Spielwiese zu machen.</p>\r
<p>Be a part&nbsp;of&nbsp;the human harvest.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/heartless-human-harvest/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aA1OzEfk9rI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"heartless_human_harvest_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/heartless_human_harvest_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36403}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4672,uri:"https://hxhxh.band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4673,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/HeartlessHumanHarvest/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4674,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/hxhxh.band/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6b5VGR6r36WvU3vbrl9HbG",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/9/csm_heartless_human_harvest_26_5c7a455a4e.jpg",uid:1688},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Heaven Shall Burn",uid:579}],end:"1691266500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1691261100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1031},{artists:[{title:"Heaven Shall Burn",uid:579}],end:"1691250300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1691247600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1394},{artists:[{title:"Heaven Shall Burn",uid:579}],end:"1785423600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785420000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Special Pay with your Blood Show!",uid:2819}],pathSegment:"heaven-shall-burn",title:"Heaven Shall Burn",uid:579},biography:`<p>Normally, Heaven Shall Burn shake the foundation of global main stages - this time, the Landgasthof will have to do. What remains unchanged: maximum energy, uncompromising riffs, and a mosh pit that will go down in the festival’s history books.</p>\r
<p>For years, Heaven Shall Burn have been one of Germany’s most vital Metal bands. Tearing down festival stages worldwide with their crushing blend of Metalcore and Melodic Death Metal, they have always stayed true to their values and social commitment. This is exactly why they act as patrons for Pay With Your Blood and actively supported the campaign as part of their "Heimat" tour.</p>\r
<p>This exclusive club show is their personal thank you to everyone who saves lives by donating blood and supporting the campaign. If you want to be there, you definitely shouldn't miss the Pay With Your Blood giveaway. Spots are highly limited - but anyone holding a W:O:A 2026 ticket has a shot.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;Enter the giveaway here</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Normalerweise bringen Heaven Shall Burn die Mainstages zum Beben - dieses Mal reicht ein Landgasthof. Was gleich bleibt: maximale Energie, kompromisslose Riffs und eine Moshpit, die in die Geschichtsbücher des Festivals eingehen wird.</p>\r
<p>Heaven Shall Burn gehören seit Jahren zu den wichtigsten Metal-Bands Deutschlands.&nbsp; Mit ihrer Mischung aus Metalcore und Melodic Death Metal reißen sie weltweit Festivalbühnen ab, bleiben dabei ihren Werten und ihrem sozialen Engagement immer treu. Genau deshalb sind sie auch Schirmherren von Pay With Your Blood und haben mit ihrer "Heimat"-Tour Teil die Aktion mitgetragen.</p>\r
<p>Diese exklusive Clubshow ist ihr persönliches Dankeschön an alle, die mit ihrer Blutspende Leben retten und die Kampagne unterstützen. Wer dabei sein will, sollte das Pay With Your Blood-Gewinnspiel auf keinen Fall verpassen. Denn Plätze gibt's nur wenige - die Chance darauf hat aber jeder, der ein W:O:A 2026 Ticket hat. <a href="t3://page?uid=880">Teilnehmen könnt ihr hier</a></p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/heaven-shall-burn/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R4JgY2wKIgk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"heaven_shall_burn_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/heaven_shall_burn_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37080}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4803,uri:"https://www.heavenshallburn.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4804,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/officialheavenshallburn/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4805,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/heavenshallburnofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4806,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/heavenshallburntv"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4sy5qWfwUwpGYBnCKnwfcW",subtitle:"Presented by Pay with your Blood",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/b/csm_heaven_shall_burn_26_37dd02c4d9.jpg",uid:1741},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Heavysaurus",uid:997}],end:"1754041500",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754096400",start:"1754028000",title:"Friday",uid:26},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1754038800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2125},{artists:[{title:"Heavysaurus",uid:997}],end:"1785579300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785576600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2748}],pathSegment:"heavysaurus",title:"Heavysaurus",uid:997},biography:"<p>At a first glance they are summoners of a long forgotten time. No way! Because the dinos of HEAVYSAURUS entertain the whole offspring of our loud and favourite music. Plea to all young W:O:A fans: Once the colourful primeval rockers turn on the amps, show your parents how much power you got! Pommesgabel reload!</p>",biographyDe:"<pre>Auf den ersten Blick wirken sie wie Beschwörer einer längst vergangenen Zeit. Weit gefehlt! Denn die Dinos aus HEAVYSAURUS begeistern die ganze Generation unserer lauten Lieblingsmusik. Aufruf an alle jungen W:O:A-Fans: Sobald die farbenfrohen Urzeit-Rocker die Verstärker aufdrehen, zeigt euren Eltern, was in euch steckt! Pommesgabel reload!</pre>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/heavysaurus/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4sYN2YeCtU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"heavysaurus_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/heavysaurus_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35824}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4535,uri:"https://www.heavysaurus.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4536,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/HeavysaurusDE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4537,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/heavysaurus/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6uyCfgv8FWIc2mifriVXqw",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/0/csm_heavysaurus_26_9d1aa2a6db.jpg",uid:1641},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Südafrika",shortNameDe:"Südafrika",shortNameEn:"South Africa",uid:235}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Human Nebula",uid:1265}],end:"1785324300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785323100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Sub Saharan Africa",uid:2624}],pathSegment:"human-nebula",title:"Human Nebula",uid:1265},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Human Nebula is a deathcore/death metal band from Pretoria, South Africa, emerged in 2018 with a genre-defying sound that fuses deathcore, death metal, and progressive elements.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their debut EP Pillars of Creation took Best EP at the 2019 South African Metal Music Awards, quickly cementing their reputation. Collaborations on tracks like Police Brutality have extended their reach across the African metal scene, and a steady run of city tours has earned them acclaim for cosmic riffs, technical solos, crushing breakdowns, and high-energy live shows.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Human Nebula ist eine Deathcore-/Death-Metal-Band aus Pretoria, Südafrika. 2018 trat sie mit einem genreübergreifenden Sound auf den Plan, der Deathcore, Death Metal und progressive Elemente miteinander verbindet.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihre Debüt-EP Pillars of Creation wurde bei den South African Metal Music Awards 2019 als „Best EP" ausgezeichnet und festigte rasch ihren Ruf. Kollaborationen auf Tracks wie Police Brutality erweiterten ihre Präsenz innerhalb der afrikanischen Metal-Szene, und kontinuierliche Auftritte in den großen Städten haben ihnen Anerkennung für kosmische Riffs, technische Soli, zermalmende Breakdowns und energiegeladene Live-Shows eingebracht.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/human-nebula/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/@humannebula",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"human_nebula_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/human_nebula_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37105}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4813,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/humannebula"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0D9Z57lkpvMICdm4Ho4f5W",subtitle:"Metal Battle Souht Africa",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/7/csm_human_nebula_26_595097da2b.jpg",uid:1746},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Griechenland",shortNameDe:"Griechenland",shortNameEn:"Greece",uid:85}],events:[{artists:[{title:"I See Red",uid:1222}],end:"1785322800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785321600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Greece",uid:2611}],pathSegment:"i-see-red",title:"I See Red",uid:1222},biography:`<p class="text-justify">I See Red is a melodic death metal band from Athens, Greece, formed in 2014. Their sound fuses melodic death metal with hardcore and black metal, building a dark, intense atmosphere all their own.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Following the EPs As Hope Runs Dry (2016) and A Drop of Truth (2020), the band underwent a complete lineup renewal. After an explosive support slot for the legendary The Haunted, 2026 marks I See Red's return with new material and a refreshed sound that continues to evolve their identity.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">I See Red ist eine Melodic-Death-Metal-Band aus Athen, Griechenland, gegründet 2014. Ihr Sound verbindet Melodic Death Metal mit Hardcore und Black Metal – und entfaltet eine düstere, intensive Atmosphäre ganz eigener Prägung.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Nach den EPs As Hope Runs Dry (2016) und A Drop of Truth (2020) wurde das Line-up komplett erneuert. Nach einem mitreißenden Support-Auftritt für die legendären The Haunted markiert 2026 die Rückkehr von I See Red – mit neuem Material und einem überarbeiteten Sound, der ihre Identität weiterführt.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/i-see-red/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"i_see_red_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/i_see_red_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36687}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4686,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/i.see.red"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4687,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/iseeredofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1yibziitCge1Mpgqj1mxcq",subtitle:"Metal Battle Greece",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/7/csm_i_see_red_26_740c88bbf9.jpg",uid:1693},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"In Flames",uid:1136}],end:"1785525300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785519900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2698}],pathSegment:"in-flames",title:"In Flames",uid:1136},biography:`<p>What screams "pioneers of melodic death metal" more than In Flames? With albums like <i>The Jester Race</i> and <i>Clayman</i>, they helped define the legendary “Göteburg Sound”! After their early successes, In Flames shifted stylistically toward alternative metal in the 2000s. With frontman Anders Fridén’s unmistakable voice and their signature riffs, the band has become an unshakable force in the scene — some would even say they're the leaders. They’re no strangers to the fields of Wacken either, having already delivered countless unforgettable moments on the Holy Ground. So, it should come as no surprise that they’re welcome guests at W:O:A — and we’re already looking forward to creating more memories with them.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Was schreit mehr nach Pionieren des Melodic Death Metal als In Flames? Mit Alben wie <i>The Jester Race&nbsp;</i>oder <i>Clayman&nbsp;</i>prägten sie den <i>Göteburg Sound!&nbsp;</i>Nach den erfolgreichen ersten Alben ging In Flames in den 2000ern stilistisch in die Richtung des Alternative Metal. Unverkennbar durch Frontman Anders Friden’s markanter Stimme und den typischen Riffs sind die Jungs aus der Szene nicht mehr wegzudenken, manche würden sogar meinen sie sind die Anführer. Auch auf dem Acker sind sie keine unbekannten Gesichter und sorgten auf dem Holy Ground schon für unzählige unvergessliche Momente – also dürfte es niemanden wundern, dass sie gern gesehene Gäste auf dem W:O:A sein und freuen uns schon weitere Erinnerungen mit ihnen zu schaffen.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/in-flames/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9qjDzIQoyW3USlw__qdmnQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"In-Flames-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/In-Flames-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34873}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4246,uri:"https://www.inflames.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4247,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/inflames/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4248,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/inflames"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"57ylwQTnFnIhJh4nu4rxCs",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/6/csm_In-Flames-WOA26_9e6947d658.jpg",uid:1551},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Österreich",shortNameDe:"Österreich",shortNameEn:"Austria",uid:13}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Insanity Alert",uid:445}],end:"1659793500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1659790800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:683},{artists:[{title:"Insanity Alert",uid:445}],end:"1659798900",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1659796200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:850},{artists:[{title:"Insanity Alert",uid:445}],end:"1785518100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785515400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2739}],pathSegment:"insanity-alert",title:"Insanity Alert",uid:445},biography:"<p>Wer hat diese Irren auf den Holy Ground gelassen? Bei Insanity Alert ist die Warnung im Namen sicherlich kein nettgemeinter Hinweis, sondern echte Warnung. Bei langanhaltender Moshpit Action angefeuert durch Heavy Kevy und seine Mitstreiter können langfristig entscheidende Nebenwirkungen auftreten. Bei so viel Spaß und guter Stimmung können wir leider nicht ausschließen, dass ihr euch umgehend in die Österreicher verlieben könntet. Ihr mit Hardcore angereicherter Thrash ist ebenfalls nichts für sanfte Gemüter. Doch die Jungs kommen nicht nur um zu shredden, sondern um Party zu machen! Sie feiern ihr 15. Jubiläum in Wacken und lasst uns euch eines sagen: Niemand hat die Kunst Party zu machen so perfektioniert wie Insanity Alert! Packt die Aspirin ein - wer sich dieser Gefahr trotzdem stellen will ist herzlich eingeladen!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Who let these maniacs onto the Holy Ground? With Insanity<strong>&nbsp;</strong>Alert, the warning is not just a friendly heads-up — it’s a <i>real</i> warning. Prolonged mosh pit action, fueled by Heavy Kevy and his crew, may lead to serious long-term side effects. With so much fun and good vibes, we unfortunately can’t rule out the risk of instantly falling in love with these Austrians. Their thrash, infused with hardcore, is not for the faint of heart. But these guys don’t just come to shred, they come to party! Celebrating their 15th anniversary at Wacken, let us tell you this: nobody has perfected the art of partying quite like Insanity Alert! Pack your aspirin—if you dare face this danger, you’re more than welcome to join!&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/insanity-alert/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/@insanityalert",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Insanity_Alert-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Insanity_Alert-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34810}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4254,uri:"https://www.insanityalert.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4255,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/insanityalert"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4256,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/insanityalert"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7371n3dNMRdoAuDOiweQJx",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/3/csm_Insanity_Alert-WOA26_32944b8820.jpg",uid:1554},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Invasion",uid:1268}],end:"1785344700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785343500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Norway",uid:2630}],pathSegment:"invasion",title:"Invasion",uid:1268},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Invasion is a hard rock/metal band from Norway, formed in 2022. Their sound blends classic heavy metal with modern, 80s-inspired rock, anchored by massive choruses and high-energy live shows. In a short time, they've put out two full-lengths — Invasion (2023) and Invasion II (2024) — and built a rapidly growing international fan base.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">In October 2025, Invasion released their latest single Helldiver alongside a spectacular music video that has already crossed 1.7 million YouTube views — their most ambitious visual project to date. Earlier that year, the melodic, explosive single Loaded Gun strengthened their international momentum, followed by a German summer tour including the RV Bang Festival (Balingen) and Rock For Animal Rights (Bremen). The band's next album, Invasion III, is now in the works.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Invasion ist eine Hard-Rock-/Metal-Band aus Norwegen, gegründet 2022. Ihr Sound verbindet klassischen Heavy Metal mit modernem, vom 80er-Rock inspiriertem Klang – getragen von gewaltigen Refrains und energiegeladenen Live-Shows. In kurzer Zeit hat die Band zwei Alben veröffentlicht – Invasion (2023) und Invasion II (2024) – und sich eine schnell wachsende internationale Fangemeinde aufgebaut.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Im Oktober 2025 erschien die aktuelle Single Helldiver samt spektakulärem Musikvideo, das auf YouTube bereits über 1,7 Millionen Aufrufe verzeichnet – ihr bislang ambitioniertestes visuelles Projekt. Zuvor hatte die melodische, explosive Single Loaded Gun ihren internationalen Schwung weiter befeuert, gefolgt von einer Sommertour durch Deutschland mit Auftritten beim RV Bang Festival (Balingen) und Rock For Animal Rights (Bremen). Aktuell arbeitet die Band an ihrem nächsten Album Invasion III.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/invasion/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c6KB1wWNWJo",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"invasion_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/invasion_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37108}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4818,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/invasion.norway"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4819,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/norwayinvasion"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4820,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@Invasion.norway"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0UVhdgxNalIFFYqUoLeREd",subtitle:"Metal Battle Norway",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/7/csm_invasion_26_9270af2a05.jpg",uid:1749},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Jäst",uid:1247}],end:"1785092400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785114000",start:"1785045600",title:"Sunday",uid:31},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785088800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2796}],pathSegment:"jaest",title:"Jäst",uid:1247},biography:"<p>“Bring Rock Back To Radio!” – that’s not a polite request; it’s Jäst’s ultimate mission! What started in 2023 as a spontaneous, beer-fueled WhatsApp idea between bassist Steven Wussow (Orden Ogan) and Axel Ritt (ex-Grave Digger) has evolved into a high-octane Rock powerhouse. With Tim Breideband (ex-Freedom Call) behind the kit, they’ve got a total beast on board, but the crown jewel is frontwoman Jessica Conte. The young Italian singer delivers that gritty '80s vibe with so much charm and vocal power, she’ll blow the minds of even the most hardened Metal veterans. The band name might be thrown together from the members' initials in cozy, classic ABBA fashion, but live, these guys don't mess around. Get ready for a massive arena-Rock party right in the Landgasthof, with stadium-sized anthems guaranteed to get stuck in your head!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>„Bring Rock Back To Radio!“ - das ist kein höfliches Bitte-Bitte, sondern die erklärte Mission von Jäst! Was 2023 als spontane Schnapsidee per WhatsApp zwischen Bassist Steven Wussow (Orden Ogan) und Axel Ritt (ex-Grave Digger) startete, hat sich zu einer hochexplosiven Rock-Dampfwalze entwickelt. Mit Tim Breideband (ex-Freedom Call) an den Kesseln haben die Jungs ein echtes Tier an Bord, aber das absolute Kronjuwel ist Frontfrau Jessica Conte: Die junge Italienerin rotzt den Vibe der 80er-Jahre so unfassbar charmant und stimmgewaltig von der Rampe, dass es den gestandenen Metal-Recken glatt die Falten aus dem Lederoutfit bügelt. Der Bandname mag zwar in bester, kuscheliger ABBA-Manier aus den Initialen der Bandmitglieder zusammengewürfelt sein, aber live fackeln die Herrschaften nicht lange. Das wird eine fette Arena-Rock-Party mitten im Landgasthof, bei der stadiongroße Ohrwürmer garantiert im Gehörgang nisten!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/jaest/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=32u4D3O2S3Q",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"jaest_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/jaest_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37044}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4759,uri:"https://jast-band.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4760,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61556364389245"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4761,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/jast_band_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3pejAqOcOsnG28IwNshhFk",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/d/csm_jaest_26_792493ad1a.jpg",uid:1724},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Jazz Sabbath",uid:1260}],end:"1785580200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785576600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Jazz Frühshoppen",uid:2822}],pathSegment:"jazz-sabbath",title:"Jazz Sabbath",uid:1260},biography:`<p>Whispers in the heavy underground suggest that the ominous piano genius Milton Keanes is actually none other than Adam Wakeman - the long-time touring keyboardist for Black Sabbath and Ozzy Osbourne himself. But… we would obviously never say that. Never!&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;After all, the official (and much more beautiful) truth is: Jazz Sabbath invented Heavy Jazz back in 1969, right before Ozzy and co. brazenly stole the songs while Milton was hospitalized! By the way, the idea for this brilliant revenge plot was born in 2013 at&nbsp;4:30 AM at a hotel bar in Berlin, when Wakeman casually jammed the entire Sabbath set as a jazz improvisation on the bar piano just for laughs. Since then, the trio has conquered the Billboard charts with albums like The 1968 Tapes and the brand-new Jazz Sabbath Live.</p>\r
<p>For the grand finale of the festival, bring your hangover breakfast, grab a cold beer, and enjoy the "originals" from Iron Man to Paranoid, beautifully reimagined in an exquisite jazz style.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Man munkelt&nbsp; im Heavy-Underground, dass hinter dem ominösen Piano-Genie Milton Keanes in Wahrheit kein Geringerer als Adam Wakeman steckt - also der langjährige Tour-Keyboarder von Black Sabbath und Ozzy Osbourne höchstpersönlich. Aber… wir würden so etwas natürlich niemals behaupten. Niemals! Die offizielle (und viel schönere) Wahrheit lautet schließlich: Jazz Sabbath erfanden 1969 den Heavy Jazz, bevor Ozzy und Co. die Songs kackdreist klauten, während Milton im Krankenhaus lag! Die Idee zu diesem genialen Rachefeldzug entstand übrigens 2013 morgens um halb fünf an einer Hotelbar in Berlin, als Wakeman den kompletten Sabbath-Set aus Jux als Jazz-Improvisation auf dem Bar-Piano runterzockte. Inzwischen hat das Trio mit Alben wie The 1968 Tapes und der brandneuen Jazz Sabbath Live die Billboard-Charts erobert.</p>\r
<p>Packt zum krönenden Festival-Abschluss das Katerfrühstück ein, schnappt euch ein kühles Blondes und genießt beim Jazz-Frühschoppen die “Originale“ von Iron Man bis Paranoid im exzellenten Jazz-Kleid.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/jazz-sabbath/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZLpThtpNPw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"jazz_sabbath_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/jazz_sabbath_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37079}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4799,uri:"http://www.jazzsabbath.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4800,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/jazz_sabbath/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4801,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/JazzSabbath1970"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Twitter",uid:2},uid:4802,uri:"https://x.com/Jazz_Sabbath"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"59dGdCSieplkG6HWFQbyYB",subtitle:"Special Breakfast Show / Jazz-Frühschoppen",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/0/csm_jazz_sabbath_26_8e95b2aeb5.jpg",uid:1740},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Judas Priest",uid:270}],end:"1659650400",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1659644100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:538},{artists:[{title:"Judas Priest",uid:270}],end:"1785531600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785526200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2703}],pathSegment:"judas-priest",title:"Judas Priest",uid:270},biography:"<p>It's time for a legend – because it's time for JUDAS PRIEST! Even after more than five decades in the music business, more than 50 million records sold and their latest LP ‘Invincible Shield’ (2024), Metal god Rob Halford and his bandmates are ready to rock Holy Ground with tons of riffs, a vocal range spanning over four octaves and roaring motorbikes. Raise your horns, oil your vocal cords and give it your all when „Breaking The Law“, „Painkiller”, „The Serpent And The King“ and many more familiar songs ring out.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Es ist Zeit für eine Legende – denn es ist Zeit für JUDAS PRIEST! Auch nach über fünf Jahrzehnten im Musikbusiness, mehr als 50 Millionen verkauften Alben und dem aktuellen Longplayer „Invincible Shield“ (2024) im Gepäck, sind Metal God Rob Halford und seine Mannen bereit, den Holy Ground mit tonnenweise Riffs, über vier Oktaven Stimmumfang und aufheulenden Motorrädern zum Beben zu bringen. Reckt die Pommesgabel in die Höhe, ölt die Stimmbänder und gebt alles, wenn „Breaking The Law“, „Painkiller“, „The Serpent And The King“ und viele weitere vertraute Songs ertönen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/judas-priest/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HwMZ20ZVZeE",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"judas_priest26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/judas_priest26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35755}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4440,uri:"https://judaspriest.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4441,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/OfficialJudasPriest"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4442,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/judaspriest"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4443,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/user/JudasPriest"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2tRsMl4eGxwoNabM08Dm4I",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/d/csm_judas_priest26_47424c35d1.jpg",uid:1612},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Kadavar",uid:373}],end:"1659701700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1659699000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:592},{artists:[{title:"Kadavar",uid:373}],end:"1659692700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1659690000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:831},{artists:[{title:"Kadavar",uid:373}],end:"1785357000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785352500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2632}],pathSegment:"kadavar",title:"Kadavar",uid:373},biography:"<p>Kadavar sound like someone plugged a dusty Sabbath record into a screaming tube amp and cranked it to festival mode. Fuzz guitars, psychedelic grooves and warm vintage vibes everywhere. When the Berlin Fantastic (now) Four kicks in, the Wacken field suddenly feels like a giant 1970s rock club.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Kadavar klingen, als hätte jemand eine alte Sabbath-Platte in einen viel zu heißen Röhrenamp gesteckt und dann auf „Festivalmodus“ gedreht. Fuzz-Gitarren, psychedelische Grooves und dieser warme Vintage-Sound. Wenn die Berliner loslegen, fühlt sich der Acker plötzlich wie ein staubiger 70er-Rockclub an – nur mit deutlich mehr Leuten.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/kadavar/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BnpmDxQ6zO8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"kadavar_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/kadavar_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36380}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4606,uri:"https://www.kadavar.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4607,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/KadavarOfficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4608,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/kadavargram"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0FfuujZJUa7Z2JzhhiPI2z",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/9/csm_kadavar_26b_5241b42bda.jpg",uid:1664},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Kärbholz",uid:57}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:145},{artists:[{title:"Kärbholz",uid:57}],end:"1691149500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1691145900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:989},{artists:[{title:"Kärbholz",uid:57}],end:"1691160300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1691157600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1375},{artists:[{title:"Kärbholz",uid:57}],end:"1785607200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785603600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2757}],pathSegment:"kaerbholz",title:"Kärbholz",uid:57},biography:"<p>True to their motto ‘Vollgas Rock’n‘Roll’, German Rock quartet KÄRBHOLZ are tirelessly committed to giving their fans 100% with songs about the heart and mind and the relentless game of life. They have always been rebels, with karma on their side, and have always torn down barricades with heart and soul. The rockers have not only announced a new tour for 2026, but are also working on new music for the follow-up to their 2023 albums ‘Barrikaden’ and ‘Wilde Augen’. Grab yourself a cold beer and turn up the volume! We're looking forward to a loud party in Wacken!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Getreu dem Motto „Vollgas Rock’n’Roll“ ist das deutsche Rock-Quartett KÄRBHOLZ rastlos dabei, seine Fans zu 100% mit Songs über Herz und Verstand und dem schonungslosen Spiel des Lebens zu versorgen. Kontra waren sie schon immer, das Karma auf ihrer Seite und Barrikaden haben sie stets mit Leib und Seele niedergerissen. Für 2026 haben die Rocker nicht nur eine neue Tour angekündigt, sondern arbeiten auch an neuer Musik für den Nachfolger ihrer 2023er Album „Barrikaden“ und „Wilde Augen“. Zapft euch ein kühles Bier, dreht die Boxen auf!&nbsp;Wir freuen uns auf die lautstarke Party in Wacken!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/kaerbholz/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Sv68QnjoSk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"kaerbholz_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/kaerbholz_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36381}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4609,uri:"https://www.kaerbholz.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4610,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Kaerbholzoffiziell"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4611,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/kaerbholz"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7LNFSNejKjCEEwneXJQwXL",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/4/csm_kaerbholz_26_85a563b793.jpg",uid:1665},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Katerfahrt",uid:1139}],end:"1785413700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785411000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2681}],pathSegment:"katerfahrt",title:"Katerfahrt",uid:1139},biography:"",biographyDe:"",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/katerfahrt/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7vmqa9jSCceSIvNo1vf21w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Katerfahrt-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Katerfahrt-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34811}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4257,uri:"https://katerfahrt.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4258,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/p/Katerfahrt-61550192707626/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4259,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/katerfahrtband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4WsOnJW1h3znXnbMGQ2mpP",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/0/csm_Katerfahrt-WOA26_4213c9f3a0.jpg",uid:1555},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Australien",shortNameDe:"Australien",shortNameEn:"Australia",uid:14}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Kim Dracula",uid:1186}],end:"1785583800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785580200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2743}],pathSegment:"kim-dracula",title:"Kim Dracula",uid:1186},biography:"<p>If Nosferatu had sailed to Tasmania instead of Wisborg and wreaked havoc there, we could explain the existence of Kim Dracula as the result of a vampire bite. Science demands we describe what we hear and see — and it’s this: Kim Dracula enchants our ears with an exotic mix of Trap, Hip-Hop, and Metal. A mad blend of styles made even more intense by the singer’s unhinged presence. A Wacken debut we’re seriously looking forward to!</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Wenn Nosferatu statt nach Wisborg nach Tasmanien gesegelt wäre und dann dort sein Unwesen getrieben hätte, könnten wir die Existenz von Kim Dracula durch einen Vampir-Biss erklären.</p>\r
<p>So gebieten es uns die Regeln der Wissenschaft zu beschreiben, was wir sehen und hören können und das ist Folgendes: Kim Dracula bezirzt unsere Ohren mit einer exotischen Mischung aus Trap, Hip Hop und Metal Elementen. Ein Spagat der Stile, dem das leicht wahnsinnige Auftreten des Sängers zusätzlich Atmosphäre verleiht. Ein Wacken Debüt, auf das wir uns ganz besonders freuen!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/kim-dracula/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wSkTmLe5kRQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"kim_dracula26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/kim_dracula26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35767}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4484,uri:"https://www.kimdracula.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4485,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/KimDrac/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4486,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/kimdrac/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4487,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1Zvw4vEriIZta80U_pUEaA"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"526TMJFuJibm9j2p9td9Yp",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/4/csm_kim_dracula26_6085add158.jpg",uid:1624},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Kittie",uid:1163}],end:"1785588300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785584700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2754}],pathSegment:"kittie",title:"Kittie",uid:1163},biography:"<p>Kittie are the rusted nails in Nu-Metal’s coffin — and the queens who forged it. While others sang about high school pain, they spat venom and truth. <i>“Spit”</i> was raw wound turned battle cry, opening a door for women in Metal. Two decades later, they sharpen the blade again — older, angrier, wiser. <i>“Fire”</i> sounds like a time machine crash-landing in the storm. And this time, it doesn’t burn out — it burns everything down.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Es gab sie – die rostigen Nägel im Sarg des Nu-Metal: geschmiedet haben sie Kitte, die Teenage Angst Queens, die mit <i>“Spit”</i>&nbsp;die Tür die für Frauen im Metal erst öffnete, mit einem Roundhouse Kick auftraten. Und wer schmiedet der weiß auch wie m an Schlösser wieder öffnet:&nbsp; Zwei Jahrzehnte später sind Kittie wieder da – älter, wütender, klarer. <i>“Fire”</i> klingt wie eine Zeitmaschine, die mitten im Sturm landet. Und diesmal brennt sie nicht aus – sie brennt alles nieder.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/kittie/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZDmLPBVOidQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"kittie_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/kittie_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35108}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4351,uri:"https://www.kittie.net"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4352,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/officialkittie/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4353,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/kittiepage/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4354,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@kittiechannel"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0ImEDe9tW5n4pxHOK39zIc",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/6/csm_kittie_26_31697daab6.jpg",uid:1588},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Kupfergold",uid:846}],end:"1722539700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722560400",start:"1722492000",title:"Thursday",uid:20},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722536100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1549},{artists:[{title:"Kupfergold",uid:846}],end:"1785438900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785435300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2685}],pathSegment:"kupfergold",title:"Kupfergold",uid:846},biography:"<p>Back in the days of the gold rush, every prospector needed their own claim. Here at Wacken, all you need is your spot on the Holy Ground to strike real gold — more precisely, Kupfergold. In their tricky seventh year, the medieval rock band finally made it to Wacken. Sometimes, you must dig a little deeper to uncover the true treasures — and now the reward is all the greater. Welcome to the Holy Ground!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Zu Zeiten des Goldrauschs brauchte jeder Goldsuchende seinen eigenen Claim. Bei uns braucht ihr lediglich euren Platz auf dem Holy Ground, um an echtes Gold zu kommen. Genauer gesagt Kupfergold. Im verflixten siebten Jahr hat es die Mittelalter-Rock Formation nun endlich nach Wacken geschafft. Manchmal muss man eben für Gold auch ein wenig schürfen, um schließlich reich beschenkt zu werden. Willkommen auf dem Holy Ground.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/kupfergold/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJJqHutxqsRgtY2TBrVt93A",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Kupfergold-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Kupfergold-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34812}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4260,uri:"https://formatio-kupfergold.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4261,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/formatio.kupfergold/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4262,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/kupfergold_band"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5ziUNRAHfR28SgsINMc66V",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/c/csm_Kupfergold-WOA26_1d73350ab6.jpg",uid:1556},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Italien",shortNameDe:"Italien",shortNameEn:"Italy",uid:104}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Lacuna Coil",uid:363}],end:"1659705300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1659702600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:598},{artists:[{title:"Lacuna Coil",uid:363}],end:"1659726900",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1659724200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:841},{artists:[{title:"Lacuna Coil",uid:363}],end:"1785357000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785351600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2608}],pathSegment:"lacuna-coil",title:"Lacuna Coil",uid:363},biography:"<p>LACUNA COIL have been on the road for over three decades and this year released their tenth album, ‘Sleepless Empire’. Their mix of Gothic, Alternative and Death Metal has always thrilled their loyal fan base. With current songs such as ‘Oxygen’ and ‘Hosting the Shadow’, the Italian band led by singer Cristina Scabbia shows that they are still full of energy, and who knows, maybe we'll get to hear the latter song live with guest singer Randy Blythe from Lamb of God? In any case, both bands are playing at Holy Ground. Don't miss the show!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Seit über drei Jahrzehnten sind LACUNA COIL unterwegs und haben dieses Jahr ihr zehntes Album „Sleepless Empire“ von den Ketten gelassen. Ihre Mischung aus Gothic, Alternative und Death Metal begeistert ihre treue Fangemeinde seit jeher. Mit aktuellen Songs wie „Oxygen“ und „Hosting the Shadow“ zeigen die Italiener um Sängerin Cristina Scabbia, dass sie noch voller Energie stecken und wer weiß, vielleicht bekommen wir den letztgenannten Song auch mit Gastsänger Randy Blythe von Lamb of God live zu hören? Beide Bands spielen jedenfalls auf dem Holy Ground. Lasst euch die Show nicht entgehen!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/lacuna-coil/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H86cL4NBZRg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"lacuna_coil_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/lacuna_coil_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36382}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4612,uri:"https://www.lacunacoil.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4613,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/lacunacoil"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4614,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lacunacoilofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4OAddazJM576euUnFSvXSL",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/3/csm_lacuna_coil_26_289f52868d.jpg",uid:1666},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Lagwagon",uid:1187}],end:"1785606300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785603600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2765}],pathSegment:"lagwagon",title:"Lagwagon",uid:1187},biography:"<p>Neben all den dunklen und fies dreinblickenden Gestalten braucht es manchmal auch einen Tupfer Farbe und Fröhlichkeit. Bei Lagwagon bleibt der Pit freundlich, die Mienen heiter und die Sonne draußen – kein Wunder beim ansteckenden Punk Rock der Amerikaner. Dass die Band bereits seit Beginn der 1990er Jahre mit guter Laune um sich wirft, kann hier getrost als Erfahrung verbucht werden. Und für alle, denen das jetzt zu viel good vibes war, denkt immer dran: Wo kein Licht ist, gibt es auch keinen Schatten!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Among all the dark, grim faces out there, sometimes you need a splash of color and joy. Enter Lagwagon — where the pit stays friendly, the faces are smiling, and the sun shines bright. No surprise, given the infectious Punk Rock energy of these Californians. They’ve been spreading good vibes since the early ’90s — that’s experience you can trust. And for anyone who thinks that’s too cheerful, remember: where there’s no light, there’s no shadow!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/lagwagon/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mdMr3AMEdXU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"lagwagon26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/lagwagon26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35768}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4488,uri:"https://www.lagwagon.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4489,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/lagwagon/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4490,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lagwagon1989/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"66riGCPfih1Xqk81dDvpvf",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/e/csm_lagwagon26_9b4cccaa2b.jpg",uid:1625},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Lamb of God",uid:1159}],end:"1785597300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785593700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2750}],pathSegment:"lamb-of",title:"Lamb of God",uid:1159},biography:"<p>There are bands whose very name is enough to send entire legions of metalheads into a frenzy of anticipation. Lamb of God is without question one of those bands. The U.S. powerhouse fronted by Randy Blythe has fought hard for their place in the spotlight. Tireless since the early 1990s, they’ve toured relentlessly and delivered album after album, hit after hit, to the hungry metal masses. Now, 35 years later, that spotlight is more than well-deserved. And in case anyone still hasn’t gotten the message: Lamb of God are coming to Wacken 2026!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Es gibt Bands, bei denen reicht die bloße Nennung des Namens, um ganze Heerscharen von Metalheads in erwartungsvolle Ekstase zu versetzen.<br />Lamb of God sind ohne Zweifel eine solche Band. Die US-Amerikaner um Frontman Randy Blythe haben sich ihren Platz an der Sonne hart erarbeitet. Nimmer müde hat die Band seit Beginn der 1990er Jahre getourt und Album nach Album, Hit nach Hit unters hungrige Metal-Volk gebracht.&nbsp;<br />35 Jahre später steht ihnen der Platz an der Sonne mehr als zu. Und für den Fall, dass es hier jemand immer noch nicht verstanden hat: Lamb of God kommen 2026 nach Wacken!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/lamb-of/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/user/lambofgod",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"lamb_of_god_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/lamb_of_god_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36143}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4330,uri:"https://www.lamb-of-god.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4331,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/lambofgod/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4332,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lambofgod/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3JFsVIxOn7STeilPICkkB2",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/4/csm_lamb_of_god_26b_d0cd004159.jpg",uid:1581},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Life of Agony",uid:13}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:93},{artists:[{title:"Life of Agony",uid:13}],end:"1659795300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1659791700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:654},{artists:[{title:"Life of Agony",uid:13}],end:"1785429900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785425400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2657}],pathSegment:"life-of-agony",title:"Life of Agony",uid:13},biography:"<p>All good things come in threes: after impressive W:O:A shows in 2019 and 2022, we are delighted to welcome New York based Alternative Metal band LIFE OF AGONY for the third time. Keith Caputo and his bandmates looked back on their long career during this year's UGLY tour, but also released a new song „The Crow“. Who knows, maybe we'll get to hear even more fresh music before their performance in Wacken?! However, one thing is certain: fan favorites such as ‘River Runs Red’ and ‘Weeds’ will shake the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Aller lautstarken Dinge sind drei: Nach den beeindruckenden W:O:A-Shows in 2019 und 2022 heißen wir die New Yorker Metallschmiede LIFE OF AGONY zum dritten Mal herzlich willkommen. Keith Caputo und seine Mitstreiter blickten erst dieses Jahr während der UGLY-Tour auf ihre langjährige Karriere zurück, veröffentlichten mit „The Crow“ aber auch einen neuen Song. Wer weiß, vielleicht bekommen wir bis zum Auftritt in Wacken noch mehr frischgebackene Musik zu hören?! Fest steht jedenfalls, dass Highlights wie „River Runs Red“ oder „Weeds“ den Acker beim Festivaljubiläum zum Beben bringen werden.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/life-of-agony/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UaCijH0USo8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"life_of_agony26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/life_of_agony26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35764}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4475,uri:"https://www.lifeofagony.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4476,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/lifeofagonyfamiglia"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4477,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lifeofagonyofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4gyzQpfG5YQZJt2jj0IkEl",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/4/csm_life_of_agony26_68ef27b061.jpg",uid:1621},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Japan",shortNameDe:"Japan",shortNameEn:"Japan",uid:107}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Lovebites",uid:1208}],end:"1785337200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785333600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2599}],pathSegment:"lovebites",title:"Lovebites",uid:1208},biography:`<p>Tokyo 2016 – Wacken 2026.</p>\r
<p>In between: ten&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;Power Metal&nbsp;without&nbsp;limits and a legendary Wacken show&nbsp;in 2018. Now&nbsp;Lovebites&nbsp;return&nbsp;to Northern Germany for&nbsp;their 10th anniversary, bringing&nbsp;epic&nbsp;melodies, a huge&nbsp;show and their&nbsp;new&nbsp;album Outstanding Power. Message received — we’re&nbsp;ready.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Tokio, 2016 – Wacken 2026. Dazwischen: Zehn Jahre Power Metal ohne Angst vor Grenzen und Vorurteilen und eine legendäre Wacken Open Air Show 2018. Jetzt kommen Lovebites, pünktlich zum 10-jährigen Bandjubiläum wieder nach Norddeutschland. Im Gepäck: epische Melodien, eine große Show und jede Menge Metal, irgendwo zwischen Iron Maiden und Helloween. Außerdem dabei: Ihr neues Album Outstanding Power – eine Nachricht auch an uns. Lovebites – wir sind bereit!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/lovebites/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vOwJCPGqlz0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"lovebites_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/lovebites_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36383}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4615,uri:"https://lovebites.jp/band/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4616,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/LovebitesTheBand/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4617,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lovebites_jp"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4H1S8RTYv4vN3SiM5uSZSa",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/d/csm_lovebites_26b_38ca926080.jpg",uid:1667},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Finnland",shortNameDe:"Finnland",shortNameEn:"Finland",uid:67}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Luna Kills",uid:1140}],end:"1785513600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785510900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2738}],pathSegment:"luna-kills",title:"Luna Kills",uid:1140},biography:"<p>Asking Finland to produce iconic and innovative metal bands is about as pointless as asking Michael Jordan to win basketball titles — it’s simply in their nature. This country was born to flood our beloved genre with legendary acts. And with Luna Kills, yet another one is stepping up to the plate. With surprising ease, this quartet blends nu-metal with electronic elements. Now, in their sixth year as a band, the Finns are setting out to haunt the Holy Ground — and we can’t wait!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Finnland zu bitten ikonische und innovative Metalbands hervorzubringen ist genauso Zeitverschwendung, wie Michael Jordan zu bitten, Basketball Titel zu gewinnen. Es liegt in der Natur dieses Landes unser geliebtes Genre mit ikonischen Bands zu fluten. Mit Luna Kills steht einmal mehr eine solche in den Startlöchern. In ungeahnter Leichtigkeit verbindet das Quartett Nu-Metal mit elektronischen Elementen. Im sechsten Jahr des Band-Bestehens machen sich die Finnen nun also auf, den Holy Ground heimzusuchen. Wir können es kaum erwarten.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/luna-kills/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDA4OW99nx7vi8JpSMRz1AA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Luna_Kills-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Luna_Kills-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34813}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4263,uri:"https://lunakills.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4264,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/lunakillsband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4265,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/lunakillsband/?hl=fi"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5OMIs8tNddcCXVDMN8LLyQ",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/3/csm_Luna_Kills-WOA26_9c2715ab09.jpg",uid:1557},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203}],end:"1753718400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753750800",start:"1753682400",title:"Monday",uid:29},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753714800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2278},{artists:[{title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203}],end:"1754159400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754182800",start:"1754114400",title:"Saturday",uid:27},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1754155800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2337},{artists:[{title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203}],end:"1753812000",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753837200",start:"1753768800",title:"Tuesday",uid:28},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753808400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2352},{artists:[{title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203}],end:"1753916400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1753912800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2385},{artists:[{title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203}],end:"1785366000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785363300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2633}],pathSegment:"mambo-kurt",title:"Mambo Kurt",uid:203},biography:"<p>Few&nbsp;word&nbsp;combinations&nbsp;make&nbsp;as&nbsp;much sense as Mambo and Kurt. Maybe only&nbsp;organ and god&nbsp;come&nbsp;close. With humor, technical&nbsp;brilliance and a home&nbsp;organ, the Orgelgott has&nbsp;been&nbsp;making&nbsp;the Holy Ground boil&nbsp;for&nbsp;years — whether&nbsp;playing&nbsp;classics like Van Halens Jump or his&nbsp;immortal Wacken anthem. Mambo Kurt belongs&nbsp;to Wacken like our&nbsp;beloved&nbsp;weather&nbsp;conditions.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Selten haben zwei Worte so sehr zusammengehört wie Mambo und Kurt. Uns fällt da persönlich nur ein weiteres Paar ein: Orgel und Gott. Und was für ein Zufall scheinen sie beide zu dieser Persönlichkeit zu gehören, die mit ganz viel Humor, technischer Raffinesse und einer Heimorgel regelmäßig die Meute auf dem Acker zum Kochen bringt. Egal ob Klassiker wie Van Halens Jump oder Eigenkompositionen, wie das unterbliche Wacken, der Orgelgott gehört zu Wacken, wie das wechselhafte Wetter.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mambo-kurt/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8ioTszy9D8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"mambo_kurt_25.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2025/mambo_kurt_25.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36384}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4618,uri:"https://www.mambokurt.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4619,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/orgelgott/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4620,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/orgelgott/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"29t2xhTM0SRjm8iTNVMynh",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/4/csm_mambo_kurt_25_d25410db45.jpg",uid:1668},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kroatien",shortNameDe:"Kroatien",shortNameEn:"Croatia",uid:93}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Manntra",uid:448}],end:"1659799800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659796200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:698},{artists:[{title:"Manntra",uid:448}],end:"1785446100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785442500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2686}],pathSegment:"manntra",title:"Manntra",uid:448},biography:"<p>All good things come in threes: In 2026, MANNTRA will rock the W:O:A for the third time and present their latest songs from the album ‘Titans’. The Croatian Folk Metal quintet knows exactly how to give ancient themes a modern twist and complement raw Industrial Metal with playful Folk elements. MANNTRA fits our motto ‘Party on’ 100%, and that's exactly what we want to celebrate with you: oil your vocal cords and raise your fists in the air when ‘Ori Ori’ and other highlights ring out.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Aller guten Dinge sind drei: 2026 rocken MANNTRA zum dritten Mal das W:O:A und präsentieren uns ihre neuesten Songs vom Album „Titans“. Das kroatische Folk&nbsp;Metal-Quintett weiß ganz genau wie es altertümlichen Themen einen modernen Anstrich verpasst und rohen Industrial Metal mit verspielten Folk-Elementen ergänzt. MANNTRA passen 100% zu unserem Motto „Party on“ und genau das wollen wir mit euch feiern: Ölt eure Stimmbänder und streckt die Fäuste in die Luft wenn „Ori Ori“ und weitere Highlights erklingen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/manntra/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/ManntraTV",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"manntra_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/manntra_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36385}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4621,uri:"https://manntra.hr"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4622,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ManntraOfficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4623,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/manntra_official"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5xKw7nNLyZ7UVvhaLC5kYd",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/3/csm_manntra_26_a22fae1fff.jpg",uid:1669},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mantar",uid:425}],end:"1659739500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1659735900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:629},{artists:[{title:"Mantar",uid:425}],end:"1785508200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785504600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2707}],pathSegment:"mantar",title:"Mantar",uid:425},biography:"<p>In the realm of extreme music, <strong>Mantar</strong> are neither unknown nor outliers. The band stands for the highest quality and has earned a reputation as an excellent live acting. Hailing from Bremen, these guys emerged in 2012 from the steel basins of the Hanseatic city and have shed everything that isn’t essential to their music. As uncompromising as that sounds, so does their music — no frills. Direct, brutal, and always hitting where it hurts. According to their own words, their only goal is simple: just hit hard! With that resume in hand, we warmly welcome them to W:O:A 2026.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Im Bereich des Extremen sind Mantar weder Unbekannte noch Exoten. Die Band steht für höchste Qualität und hat sich einen Ruf als exzellente Live-Band erarbeitet. Die Bremer, die 2012 aus den Stahlbecken der Hansestadt entstiegen sind,&nbsp; haben sich von allem gelöst, was nicht essenziell für ihre Musik ist. Genauso kompromisslos wie dies erscheinen mag, klingt auch ihre Musik – ohne Schnörkel. Direkt, brutal und immer dahin, wo es weh tut. Nach eigener Aussage lediglich mit dem einen Ziel: Einfach kloppen! Und mit diesem Bewerbungsschreiben im Gepäck sagen wir Moin! beim W:O:A 2026.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mantar/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClrxUayXC8nlv6TYLCK1MBQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Mantar-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Mantar-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34838}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4333,uri:"https://www.mantarband.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4334,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/mantarband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4335,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/MantarBand/photos"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6rVRU7I6r1lt6bhXGYTRQL",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/1/csm_Mantar-WOA26_41ea1e294a.jpg",uid:1582},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1753736400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753750800",start:"1753682400",title:"Monday",uid:29},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Spoken Word",uid:3},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753731060",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2280},{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1754168400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754182800",start:"1754114400",title:"Saturday",uid:27},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Party",uid:2},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1754163000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2340},{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1753822800",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753837200",start:"1753768800",title:"Tuesday",uid:28},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Spoken Word",uid:3},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753817400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2354},{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1753909200",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Spoken Word",uid:3},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753903860",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2374},{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1753995600",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Spoken Word",uid:3},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1753990260",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2445},{artists:[{title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230}],end:"1754082000",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754096400",start:"1754028000",title:"Friday",uid:26},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Spoken Word",uid:3},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1754076600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2506}],pathSegment:"maschines-late-night-show",title:"Maschine's Late Night Show",uid:230},biography:`<p>35 editions&nbsp;of Wacken Open Air.</p>\r
<p>Hard to&nbsp;believe&nbsp;there was ever a time when&nbsp;Maschine’s Late Night Show didn’t light up&nbsp;the Welcome To The Jungle Stage late at night&nbsp;with&nbsp;glamour, confetti, and a whole&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;sparkle.</p>\r
<p>Our&nbsp;talkmaster&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;legendary&nbsp;blow-dried&nbsp;hairstyle&nbsp;gets&nbsp;them&nbsp;all — because&nbsp;even&nbsp;the&nbsp;biggest&nbsp;stars&nbsp;of heavy entertainment&nbsp;eventually&nbsp;want a spot on his&nbsp;couch.</p>\r
<p>And we&nbsp;already&nbsp;know&nbsp;you&nbsp;love&nbsp;him&nbsp;anyway.</p>\r
<p>Because&nbsp;who&nbsp;loves&nbsp;you — and who do you&nbsp;love?</p>\r
<p>Maschine!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>35 Male Wacken Open Air. Kaum zu glauben, dass es einmal eine Zeit gab, in der Maschines Late Night Show nicht die Welcome To The Jungle Stage zu später Stunde mit Glanz, Konfetti und jeder Menge Glamour belebt hat. Unser Talkmaster mit der Föhnfrisur bekommt sie alle – denn auch die Stars der harten Unterhaltung wollen irgendwann mal in seiner Show und auf seinem Sofa zu Gast sein. Dass er bei euch sowieso ein Stein im Brett hat, wissen wir, denn wer liebt euch und wen liebt ihr? Maschine!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/maschines-late-night-show/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"maschine_2019.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2019/maschine_2019.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36698}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4718,uri:"https://www.mlns.beer"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4719,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/MaschinesLateNight/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4720,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/maschines_late_night_show/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/9/csm_maschine_2019_8c7405dcc6.jpg",uid:1704},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Chile",shortNameDe:"Chile",shortNameEn:"Chile",uid:44}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mawiza",uid:1252}],end:"1785249900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785286800",start:"1785218400",title:"Tuesday",uid:33},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785247200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2804}],pathSegment:"mawiza",title:"Mawiza",uid:1252},biography:"<p>“If necessary, we will die to defend our land!” – if anyone hears this statement from the Chilean Groove Metal juggernaut Mawiza and still expects some lukewarm Eco-Metal gathering, they clearly underestimated the raw ancestral power of these Mapuche warriors. Originally formed in 2014, the band completely discards Spanish and English, screaming exclusively in their indigenous native tongue, Mapuzungun. This fierce authenticity didn't just win over the world-renowned label Season of Mist, it also caught the attention of Gojira frontman Joe Duplantier, who wasted no time inviting the guys to his New York studio and laying down guest vocals on their latest concept album. Fusing Heavy Modern Metal, indigenous rhythms, and industrial-tinged grooves, Mawiza have already leveled tens of thousands of fans while supporting giants like Mastodon and Mercyful Fate, as well as crushing the stage at Knotfest. These gentlemen are sweeping straight out of the Chilean rainforests into the Landgasthof to show you the true, uncompromising meaning of resistance in Metal.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>“Wenn nötig, sterben wir, um unser Land zu verteidigen!“ -&nbsp; wer nach diesem Statement der chilenischen Groove-Metal-Walze Mawiza noch an einen lauwarmen Öko-Metaltreff glaubt, hat die Rechnung ohne die geballte Ahnen-Power der Mapuche-Krieger gemacht. Ursprünglich 2014 gegründet, pfeift die Band komplett auf Spanisch oder Englisch. Hier wird ausschließlich in ihrer indigenen Heimatsprache Mapuzungun gebrüllt. Das hat nicht nur das weltbekannte Label Season of Mist überzeugt, sondern auch Gojira-Frontmann Joe Duplantier, der die Jungs kurzerhand in sein New Yorker Studio einlud und auf ihrem aktuellen Konzeptalbum direkt selbst mitschreit. Mit einem wuchtigen Mix aus brutalem Modern Metal, indigenen Rhythmen und industrial-artigen Grooves haben Mawiza im Vorprogramm von Giganten wie Mastodon, Mercyful Fate oder auf dem Knotfest bereits zehntausende Fans rituell rasiert. Die Herrschaften kommen direkt aus den chilenischen Urwäldern in den Landgasthof gefegt, um euch zu zeigen, was echter, kompromissloser Widerstands-Metal bedeutet.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mawiza/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YKRpCSpH5k",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Mawiza-Bandpic_Promo_06_2025.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Mawiza-Bandpic_Promo_06_2025.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37050}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4774,uri:"https://mawizakvlt.bandcamp.com/album/l"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4775,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/mawizakvlt/?hl=de"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4oJP24bXA2fbdVmNGNmCtt",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/7/csm_Mawiza-Bandpic_Promo_06_2025_9fa96b063a.jpg",uid:1731},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Megalive - A Tribute to Megadeth",uid:1255}],end:"1785333600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785330000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2815}],pathSegment:"megalive-a-tribute-to-megadeth",title:"Megalive - A Tribute to Megadeth",uid:1255},biography:'<p>If you live for the uncompromising sound of Dave Mustaine, Megalive is an absolute must! As Germany’s only Megadeth tribute act, this top-tier quartet takes the breakneck guitar solos and highly complex song arrangements of their Californian idols dead seriously. Get ready for a straightforward, high-octane live experience that delivers both the timeless global hits of the "Big Four" legends and deep cuts buried in the archives for the ultimate die-hard metalhead. Rattle your goddamn head!</p>',biographyDe:"<p>Wer auf den kompromisslosen Sound von Dave Mustaine steht, kommt an Megalive nicht vorbei! Als Deutschlands einzige Megadeth-Tribute-Formation nimmt das hochkarätige Quartett die halsbrecherischen Gitarrensoli und extrem komplexen Songarrangements ihrer kalifornischen Idole verdammt Ernst. Das wird ein gradliniges, hochexplosives Live-Erlebnis, das neben den unsterblichen Welthits der “Big Four“-Legenden auch echte, tief vergrabene Album-Schätze für jeden Die-Hard-Metalhead bereithält. Rattle your goddamn head!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/megalive-a-tribute-to-megadeth/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"megalive_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/megalive_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37054}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4784,uri:"https://www.megalive-band.de/deutsch/megalive.htm"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4785,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/megalive_band/?hl=de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4786,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/themegadethtribute/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/8/csm_megalive_26_839cb2433e.jpg",uid:1735},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kroatien",shortNameDe:"Kroatien",shortNameEn:"Croatia",uid:93}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1659549600",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659574800",start:"1659506400",title:"Wednesday",uid:1},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2816",subtitle:"powered by Church of Wacken",title:"Metal Church",uid:12},start:"1659546000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:498},{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1659619800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659616200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:577},{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1691155800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2688",subtitle:"",title:"Welcome To The Jungle",uid:13},start:"1691152200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1103},{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1690999200",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691024400",start:"1690956000",title:"Wednesday",uid:13},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2816",subtitle:"powered by Church of Wacken",title:"Metal Church",uid:12},start:"1690995600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1148},{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1722428100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722474000",start:"1722405600",title:"Wednesday",uid:19},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722425400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1512},{artists:[{title:"Metaklapa",uid:489}],end:"1785502800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785500100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2729}],pathSegment:"metaklapa",title:"Metaklapa",uid:489},biography:`<p>Six guys, six&nbsp;voices, one&nbsp;passion – Metal! Croatia&nbsp;brings&nbsp;us&nbsp;their&nbsp;very own Heavy Metal Acapella band to&nbsp;the Holy Ground, again!</p>\r
<p>Between Fear of&nbsp;the&nbsp;dark, Wasted years and other Maiden classics stands a group&nbsp;of&nbsp;men, that&nbsp;present&nbsp;our&nbsp;beloved&nbsp;classics in a very&nbsp;distinctive style, that&nbsp;is&nbsp;even&nbsp;listed at the UNESCO heritage&nbsp;list. Let’s&nbsp;start&nbsp;our&nbsp;very own Wacken moshpit&nbsp;to&nbsp;welcome&nbsp;these&nbsp;trule&nbsp;one&nbsp;of a kind band to&nbsp;our&nbsp;festival&nbsp;once&nbsp;again!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Sechs Sänger, sechs Stimmen, eine Leidenschaft – Metal! Kroatien schickt uns ein weiteres Mal ihre ganz eigene Heavy Metal Acapella Band auf den Holy Ground.</p>\r
<p>Zwischen Fear of&nbsp;the&nbsp;dark, Wasted Years und anderen Maiden Klassikern steht eine Gruppe Männer, die unseren geliebten Metal in einem ganz bestimmten Stil darbieten, der sogar auf der UNESCO Weltkulturerbe Liste steht. Lasst uns dieser Band einen Wacken Moshpit zum Empfang gereichen, und sie wieder auf unserem Festival willkommen heißen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/metaklapa/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b5fTNEtpKNA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"metaklapa_2024.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2024/metaklapa_2024.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36386}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4624,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/metaklapa/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4625,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/metaklapa/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2SfUXfS3jFhF3iHkp0Hyqh",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/7/csm_metaklapa_2024_ec19d5fd80.jpg",uid:1670},{artist:{country:[],events:[{artists:[{title:"Metal Battle tba.",uid:889}],end:"1753961100",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1753959900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Caucasia & West Asia",uid:2451},{artists:[{title:"Metal Battle tba.",uid:889}],end:"1785491100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785488400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Award Ceremony",uid:2713}],pathSegment:"metal-battle-tba",title:"Metal Battle tba.",uid:889},biography:"<p>tba.</p>",biographyDe:"",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/metal-battle-tba/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[],networkuri:[],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:!1,uid:1707},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Indien",shortNameDe:"Indien",shortNameEn:"India",uid:99}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Midhaven",uid:1229}],end:"1785413700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785412500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB India",uid:2673}],pathSegment:"midhaven",title:"Midhaven",uid:1229},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Midhaven is a four-piece progressive metal band from Mumbai, India. Striving to bring a distinct 'Indic' voice to the world of heavy music, the band's strength was born from a confluence of Western heaviness blended with Indian Ragas — crafting evergreen, earth-shattering art with every release.</p>`,biographyDe:'<p class="text-justify">Midhaven ist eine vierköpfige Progressive-Metal-Band aus Mumbai, Indien. Mit dem Anspruch, eine eigenständige indische Stimme in die Welt der harten Musik zu tragen, schöpft die Band ihre Kraft aus dem Zusammenspiel westlicher Härte und indischer Ragas – und schafft mit jedem Release zeitlose, erderschütternde Kunst.</p>',detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/midhaven/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfFr2TMmn6s",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"midhaven_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/midhaven_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36694}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4706,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/midhaven.ind"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4707,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/midhaven.ind"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4708,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@midhaven2496"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3dpwja8lSqNL1hDCzk7qXv",subtitle:"Metal Battle India",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/9/csm_midhaven_26_ad2bc280fa.jpg",uid:1700},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Minotaurus",uid:1209}],end:"1785586500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785583800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2776}],pathSegment:"minotaurus",title:"Minotaurus",uid:1209},biography:`<p>Epic medieval&nbsp;stories&nbsp;wrapped in authentic&nbsp;sound?</p>\r
<p>Say no&nbsp;more: Minotaurus.</p>\r
<p>Since 1994 the&nbsp;band&nbsp;from Aschaffenburg has&nbsp;been&nbsp;honoring&nbsp;the&nbsp;spirit&nbsp;of&nbsp;Folk and Metal. With their&nbsp;latest&nbsp;album Memories In The Haze, they&nbsp;invite&nbsp;us&nbsp;once&nbsp;again&nbsp;into&nbsp;their&nbsp;fantastic&nbsp;world.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Hat hier jemand epische Mittelalter Geschichten im imposanten und authentischen Soundgewand gesagt? Wir kürzen das mal ab: Minotaurus!</p>\r
<p>Die Aschaffenburger Institution huldigt dem Folk und Metal seit 1994 und mit ihrem aktuellen Album Memories In The Haze schwingen sie sich erneut dazu auf uns in ihre fantastische Welt miteinzutauchen. Genau das richtige für alle die, die sich abends gerne mal ein schönes Feierabend-Met genehmigen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/minotaurus/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pSb58yYeMLg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"minotaurus_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/minotaurus_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36387}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4626,uri:"https://www.minotaurus-metal.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4627,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/MinotaurusBand/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4628,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/minotaurusmetal"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5xop0K2B5eW7xafmEO42rO",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/0/csm_minotaurus_26_1ab67a12ae.jpg",uid:1671},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Misery Index",uid:1141}],end:"1785439800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785436200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2668}],pathSegment:"misery-index",title:"Misery Index",uid:1141},biography:`<p>The year 2026 brings&nbsp;us a quarter&nbsp;century&nbsp;of Misery Index — twenty-five&nbsp;years&nbsp;of top-tier blasting&nbsp;fury. That&nbsp;alone&nbsp;is&nbsp;reason&nbsp;to&nbsp;celebrate, as&nbsp;the band returns&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;far&nbsp;north&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;first time in over&nbsp;two&nbsp;decades.</p>\r
<p>Their&nbsp;Death Metal&nbsp;infused&nbsp;with&nbsp;Hardcore elements&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;event&nbsp;for&nbsp;those&nbsp;who like it&nbsp;brutally&nbsp;hard and without&nbsp;unnecessary&nbsp;frills. Party On!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Das Jahr 2026 bringt uns ein Vierteljahrhundert Misery Index. Ein Vierteljahrhundert feinstes Geknüppel – für uns selbstverständlich ein Grund zum Feiern, denn die Band macht seit über zwanzig Jahren mal wieder einen Einkehrschwung im hohen Norden.</p>\r
<p>Ihr mit Hardcore-Elementen angereicherter Death Metal ist die ideale Spaßveranstaltung, die es gerne bretthart und ohne viel chichi mögen.</p>\r
<p>Party On!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/misery-index/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfk697jZnYGEfowTI3si6bw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Misery_Index-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Misery_Index-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34814}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4266,uri:"https://www.miseryindex.com/#contacts"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4267,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/MiseryIndex"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4268,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/miseryindex.official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1kTUJy3zL57iEANLB9FpIA",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/a/csm_Misery_Index-WOA26_477d278139.jpg",uid:1558},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Island",shortNameDe:"Island",shortNameEn:"Iceland",uid:103}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Misþyrming & Nergal",uid:1177}],end:"1785448800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785445200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:`perform Behemoth's "Sventevith"`,uid:2669}],pathSegment:"misthyrming-nergal",title:"Misþyrming & Nergal",uid:1177},biography:`<p>When the dark lord speaks to his followers, they listen in reverent silence — even if he isn’t dressed quite as you might expect.</p>\r
<p>We’re talking about Nergal and Misþyrming, who will once again bring the devilish hymns and blasphemous melodies of Behemoth's “Sventevith” to our stages.</p>\r
<p>Do not miss this unholy mass. Don’t miss one of the Extreme Metal highlights under the sign of the bullhead!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Wenn der dunkle Fürst zu seiner Gefolgschaft spricht, lauscht diese andächtig. Selbst wenn er sich nicht ganz so gewandet, wie man ihn kennt.</p>\r
<p>Die Rede ist von Nergal und Misþyrming, die die teuflischen Hymnen und ketzerischen Melodien von Behemoths “Sventevith” ein weiteres Mal auf unsere Bühnen bringen werden.</p>\r
<p>Verpasst diese unheilige Messe nicht. Verpasst nicht eines der Extreme Metal Highlights im Zeichen des Schädels!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/misthyrming-nergal/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o7jeux7HJ08",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Sventevith-Logo-2.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/Sventevith-Logo-2.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35147}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4435,uri:"https://www.behemoth.pl"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4436,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/behemothofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4437,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/behemoth/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4438,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/misthyrming/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4439,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Misthyrming/?locale=de_DE"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"32zyj5MW8nhKGMaGlp4njt",subtitle:`Perform Behemoth's "Sventevith" Storming Near The Baltic`,thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/c/csm_Sventevith-Logo-2_da655748b4.jpg",uid:1611},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mob Rules",uid:1246}],end:"1785085200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785114000",start:"1785045600",title:"Sunday",uid:31},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785081600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2795}],pathSegment:"mob-rules",title:"Mob Rules",uid:1246},biography:"<p>Who rules the Landgasthof? Mob Rules! For over three decades, this absolute institution of German Power Metal has been tearing up stages worldwide - and they’ve been doing it loud and proud. Not only have these guys brought the house down at Wacken three times and shared the stage with legends like Dio and the Scorpions, but they’re also known for crafting epic 24-minute riff monsters in the studio. Following a massive shake-up behind the drum kit and with their brand-new, chart-topping album “Rise Of The Ruler” in tow, the band is currently channeling the brilliant energy of their early days. This is a must-see for anyone craving majestic melodies, decades of live experience, and a true, flawlessly executed riff storm!</p>",biographyDe:'<p>Wer regiert den Landgasthof? Die Mob Rules! Seit über drei Jahrzehnten zersägt diese absolute Institution des deutschen Power Metals die Bühnen dieser Welt - und das nicht zu knapp: Die Jungs haben nicht nur dreimal Wacken zum Kochen gebracht und die Bretter mit Legenden wie Dio und den Scorpions geteilt, sondern schrauben auch im Studio gerne mal an epischen 24-Minuten-Riff-Monstern. Nach einem fulminanten Wechsel auf dem Schlagzeugthron und dem brandneuen Chartstürmer-Album "Rise of the Ruler" im Gepäck besinnt sich die Truppe aktuell wieder voll auf ihre brillanten Anfangstage. Ein Pflichttermin für jeden, der Bock auf majestätische Melodien, jahrzehntelange Live-Erfahrung und ein echtes, perfekt geöltes Riff-Gewitter hat!&nbsp;</p>',detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mob-rules/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iFqWqqA6lSw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"mob_rules_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/mob_rules_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37043}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4756,uri:"https://mobrules.bandcamp.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4757,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/mobrulesband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4758,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/mobrulesband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"13dxEWLoiRvGU1MK4nVUj4",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/f/csm_mob_rules_26_a6b1e98280.jpg",uid:1723},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Lettland",shortNameDe:"Lettland",shortNameEn:"Latvia",uid:128}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Morphide",uid:1234}],end:"1785346200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785345000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Latvia",uid:2618}],pathSegment:"morphide",title:"Morphide",uid:1234},biography:`<p class="text-justify">MORPHIDE is a modern metal band from Latvia, blending groovy riffs and aggressive screams with atmospheric soundscapes and dynamic vocals.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Formed in June 2019, the band quickly drew attention with their debut releases and a first European tour across the Baltics, Poland, and the Czech Republic. MORPHIDE has worked with producers Forrester Savell (Animals as Leaders, Karnivool) and George Lever (Sleep Token, Loathe, Thornhill), and crossed 7 million combined streams across all platforms.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">MORPHIDE ist eine moderne Metal-Band aus Lettland, die groovige Riffs und aggressives Geschrei mit atmosphärischen Klanglandschaften und dynamischem Gesang verbindet.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Im Juni 2019 gegründet, machte die Band rasch mit ihren ersten Releases und einer Europa-Tournee durch das Baltikum, Polen und Tschechien auf sich aufmerksam. MORPHIDE arbeitete mit den Produzenten Forrester Savell (Animals as Leaders, Karnivool) und George Lever (Sleep Token, Loathe, Thornhill) zusammen und hat plattformübergreifend über 7 Millionen Streams erreicht.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/morphide/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jraFfoByeG4",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"morphide_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/morphide_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36965}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4727,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/morphide"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4728,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/morphide"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5qJg8wCDfasUO8hFVQOR",subtitle:"Metal Battle Latvia",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/e/csm_morphide_26_73f176435f.jpg",uid:1710},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mother - A Tribute to Danzig",uid:1257}],end:"1785348000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785344400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2817}],pathSegment:"mother-a-tribute-to-danzig",title:"Mother - A Tribute to Danzig",uid:1257},biography:"<p>Who needs a confessional box when you can experience the ultimate purgatory right at the Landgasthof? With Mother, Germany’s only Danzig tribute band is rolling in to pay homage to the dark, erotic, and unholy work of Glenn Danzig (ex-Misfits, ex-Samhain). Active since 2015, this sinister outfit tackles the doomy Blues heaviness, gritty Rock 'n' Roll, and classic Heavy Metal with terrifying precision. From Lucifuge to How The Gods Kill, they deliver a full-frontal assault for everyone who likes their music pitch-black and heavy as a ton of bricks.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wer braucht schon den Beichtstuhl, wenn er das ultimative Fegefeuer im Landgasthof haben kann? Mit Mother rückt Deutschlands einzige Danzig-Tribute-Band an, um dem düster-erotischen und unheiligen Schaffen von Glenn Danzig (ex-Misfits, ex-Samhain) zu huldigen. Das seit 2015 aktive, finstere Gespann fässt die doomige Blues-Schwere, den rotzigen Rock'n'Roll und den klassischen Heavy Metal mit erschreckender Präzision an. Von Lucifuge bis How The Gods Kill gibt es hier die volle Breitseite für alle, die ihre Musik am liebsten pechschwarz und tonnenschwer serviert bekommen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mother-a-tribute-to-danzig/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"mother_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/mother_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37056}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4790,uri:"https://motherdanzigtribute.jimdofree.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4791,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/motherdanzigtribute/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4792,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/motherdanzigtribute/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/e/csm_mother_26_d29d5b201f.jpg",uid:1737},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Mr. Hurley und die Pulveraffen",uid:630}],end:"1691270100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691283600",start:"1691215200",title:"Saturday",uid:16},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1691266500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1066},{artists:[{title:"Mr. Hurley und die Pulveraffen",uid:630}],end:"1785495600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785492000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2705}],pathSegment:"mr-hurley-und-die-pulveraffen",title:"Mr. Hurley und die Pulveraffen",uid:630},biography:"<p>They don’t sail the charts – they sail chaos. And sometimes both!<br />Mr. Hurley &amp; die Pulveraffen turn every festival into a tavern with pyros and with that bec ame one of your very biggest fan-favourites. Between fiddles, curses, and casks they tell stories that taste of salt. They’re theatre, therapy, and binge in a single breath.<br />Sometimes silly, always sincere, never quiet. And those who doubt them wake up with an eyepatch.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie segeln nicht auf Charts, sondern auf Chaos. Und manchmal beides!&nbsp;<br />Mr. Hurley &amp; die Pulveraffen verwandeln jedes Festival in eine Hafenkneipe mit Flammenwerfer – und so schossen sie sich ganz easy auch in Eure Herzen!<br />Zwischen Fiedel, Fluch und Fassbier erzählen sie Geschichten, die nach Salz schmecken.<br />Sie sind Theater, Trinkgelage und Therapie in einem. Manchmal albern, immer echt, nie leise. Und wer sie unterschätzt, wacht mit Augenklappe auf.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/mr-hurley-und-die-pulveraffen/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CmkiVnOCm6w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"mr_hurley_und_die_pulveraffen_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/mr_hurley_und_die_pulveraffen_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35116}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4379,uri:"https://www.pulveraffen.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4380,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/pulveraffen"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4381,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/mr.hurley_und_die_pulveraffen/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4382,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCilJshCPtMxEEYtGQLXh1Ig"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7zhSE4Ry047wUsemXtAzq9",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/0/csm_mr_hurley_und_die_pulveraffen_26_39b0d12506.jpg",uid:1596},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Municipal Waste",uid:1180}],end:"1785602700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785600000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2771}],pathSegment:"municipal-waste",title:"Municipal Waste",uid:1180},biography:"<p>The American Groove machine MUNICIPAL WASTE has been active for over 25 years and is returning to Wacken after many years. Back in 2007, the musicians led by singer Tony Foresta officially proved that they are the champions of Party Thrash, and in 2026 they will once again show us their very own ‘Art of Partying’ – somewhere between Groove, beer, skateboards and a good dose of Hardcore Punk.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Seit über 25 Jahren ist die US-amerikanische Groove-Maschinerie MUNICIPAL WASTE bereits aktiv und kehrt nach langer Zeit zurück nach Wacken. Schon 2007 haben die Musiker um Sänger Tony Foresta amtlich bewiesen, dass sie die Verfechter des Party Thrash sind und 2026 zeigen sie uns erneut ihre ganz eigene „Art of Partying“ – irgendwo zwischen Groove, Bier, Skateboards und einer ordentlichen Portion Hardcore Punk.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/municipal-waste/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ixd0u8ygOT8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"municipal_waste26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/municipal_waste26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35759}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4456,uri:"https://www.municipalwaste.net"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4457,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Municipalwaste"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4458,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/municipalwaste"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4459,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/MUNICIPALWASTE"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2Ah9OuOj7B57gPD1cbwiaE",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/1/csm_municipal_waste26_b40cb13d64.jpg",uid:1616},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Nevermore",uid:1160}],end:"1785592800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785589200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2744}],pathSegment:"nevermore",title:"Nevermore",uid:1160},biography:"<p>If metal was a university, Nevermore would be the uncompromising professor who still gives you an A with extra credit. The Seattle-based band mixes Prog, Thrash, and a touch of madness into a sound cocktail that sends your brain cells on a rollercoaster ride. Singer Warrel Dane had the voice of a mysterious sorcerer, giving you goosebumps with every note — and you don’t even know exactly why. Anyone who’s seen them live knows: this isn’t just a band, it’s a deluxe brainwashing — but in the best way possible! The Holy Ground is ready!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn Metal eine Universität wäre, wäre Nevermore der Professor mit dem strengen Blick, der dir trotzdem eine Eins mit Sternchen gibt. Die aus Seattle stammende Truppe mixt Prog, Thrash und eine Prise Wahnsinn zu einem Soundcocktail, der deine Gehirnzellen auf Achterbahn schickt. Sänger Warrel Dane hatte die Stimme eines mysteriösen Zauberers, der einem mit jedem Ton Gänsehaut verpasst – und das, ohne dass du genau weißt, warum. Wer sie live erlebt hat, weiß: Das ist keine Band, das ist eine Gehirnwäsche deluxe – aber auf die beste Art! Der Holy Ground ist bereit!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/nevermore/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCeSGLWthhnICFqIpfSFfrdg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"nevermore_26b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/nevermore_26b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36290}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4336,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/nevermorefans/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4337,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/nev3rmoreofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1wUArE0NhHB8M1bU2WSplY",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/6/csm_nevermore_26b_55b9630985.jpg",uid:1583},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Finnland",shortNameDe:"Finnland",shortNameEn:"Finland",uid:67}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Noiduin",uid:1272}],end:"1785341700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785340500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Finland",uid:2629}],pathSegment:"noiduin",title:"Noiduin",uid:1272},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Noiduin (meaning "I cast a spell") is a pagan folk act from Finland, blending ancient folk traditions with shamanism and pagan mysticism. Deeply rooted in Finnish nature, the members not only perform with traditional instruments but also build them by hand.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">At the core of Noiduin's sound are the kantele and jouhikko, accompanied by warlike frame drums made from reindeer and elk hide, horn instruments, and percussion fashioned from natural materials. Their live performances form a hypnotic, atmospheric whole — the audience doesn't merely listen, but is drawn in, dancing and slipping into a trance-like state.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Noiduin (deutsch: „Ich spreche einen Zauber") ist ein Pagan-Folk-Act aus Finnland, der uralte Folk-Traditionen mit Schamanismus und heidnischer Mystik verschmelzen lässt. Tief in der finnischen Natur verwurzelt, spielen die Mitglieder nicht nur traditionelle Instrumente – sie bauen sie auch selbst.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Im Zentrum von Noiduins Klang stehen Kantele und Jouhikko, begleitet von kriegerischen Rahmentrommeln aus Rentier- und Elchhaut, Hörnern und Perkussion aus natürlichen Materialien. Ihre Live-Auftritte entfalten sich als hypnotisches, atmosphärisches Ganzes – das Publikum hört nicht nur zu, sondern wird hineingezogen, tanzt und gleitet in einen tranceartigen Zustand.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/noiduin/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AVCdhmPBeIw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"oiduim_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/oiduim_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37112}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4828,uri:"https://noiduin.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4829,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/noiduin"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4830,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/noiduin"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5slOpOZMe7pvqKYWMCSirH",subtitle:"Metal Battle Finland",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/c/csm_oiduim_26_38a376558c.jpg",uid:1753},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Niederlande",shortNameDe:"Niederlande",shortNameEn:"Netherlands",uid:157}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Novelization",uid:1227}],end:"1785404700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785403500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Netherlands",uid:2670}],pathSegment:"novelization",title:"Novelization",uid:1227},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Novelization is an atmospheric black and death metal band from the Netherlands. Formed in 2023, the lineup features Chris Garnier (guitar, vocals), Max Bloemendal (guitar), Daan Huls (drums), and Koert Janssen (bass).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">In a short time, they've carved out a name in the local scene with atmospheric shows packed with crushing riffs and relentless energy — known for delivering raw live power that hits the crowd head-on.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Novelization fuses atmospheric black metal and melodic passages with old-school death metal, drawing inspiration from bands like Death, Ulver, and Dissection. Their debut single Sacrifice captures it all: haunting, immersive soundscapes meeting riff-driven intensity.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Novelization ist eine atmosphärische Black- und Death-Metal-Band aus den Niederlanden. Gegründet 2023, besteht die Band aus Chris Garnier (Gitarre, Gesang), Max Bloemendal (Gitarre), Daan Huls (Schlagzeug) und Koert Janssen (Bass).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">In kurzer Zeit hat sich die Band in der lokalen Szene einen Namen gemacht – mit atmosphärischen Shows voller wuchtiger Riffs und kompromissloser Energie. Live entfesseln sie eine rohe Wucht, die das Publikum direkt mitreißt.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Novelization verbindet atmosphärischen Black Metal und melodische Passagen mit Old-School Death Metal, inspiriert von Bands wie Death, Ulver und Dissection. Ihre Debütsingle „Sacrifice" bringt all das auf den Punkt: eindringliche, immersive Klanglandschaften treffen auf riffgetriebene Intensität.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/novelization/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WR6DHyJce1E",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"novelization_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/novelization_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36692}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4700,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/novelization_arnhem"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4701,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Novelization"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4702,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@novelizationofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3poazkVxpS4USWiABaOBAZ",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/3/csm_novelization_26_6842acc391.jpg",uid:1698},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Orbit Culture",uid:1142}],end:"1785588300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785584700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2749}],pathSegment:"orbit-culture",title:"Orbit Culture",uid:1142},biography:"<p>When we talk about hype, we can’t do so without mentioning the Swedes from Orbit Culture. But as the saying goes: no smoke without fire. And true to that motto, all we can do is bow before the musical work of this quartet. Orbit Culture have rightly stood in the spotlight of the metal community for 12 years, especially due to their ability to bring technical death metal into catchy territory. The Holy Ground is ready to be transported to the next dimension.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn wir von Hype sprechen, können wir dies nicht tun, ohne die Schweden von Orbit Culture zu erwähnen. Allerdings: Wo Rauch ist, ist auch Feuer. Und gemäß diesem Motto bleibt uns nur übrig uns vor dem musikalischen Schaffen des Quartetts zu verneigen.<br />Orbit Culture stehen zurecht und gerade wegen ihrer Fähigkeit technischen Death Metal in eingängige Wege zu bringen, seit nun mehr 12 Jahren im Scheinwerferlicht der Metal Community. Der Holy Ground ist bereit sich in die nächste Dimension befördern zu lassen.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/orbit-culture/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/user/OrbitCultureOfficial",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Orbit_Culture-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Orbit_Culture-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34815}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4269,uri:"https://www.orbitculture.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4270,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/OrbitCulture"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4271,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/orbitculture"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7k29FbDq69ju2fe6zTskxY",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/c/csm_Orbit_Culture-WOA26_e0ccb2b84a.jpg",uid:1559},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Our Promise",uid:632}],end:"1691174700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691197200",start:"1691128800",title:"Friday",uid:15},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1691172000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1025},{artists:[{title:"Our Promise",uid:632}],end:"1785591900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785589200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2763}],pathSegment:"our-promise",title:"Our Promise",uid:632},biography:`<p>Hard work pays off – and no band proves it better than Our Promise.</p>\r
<p>The Stuttgart sextet blends melodic hooks, brutal shouts, and powerful songwriting into an explosive live experience.</p>\r
<p>Staying independent has kept their vision pure – no compromises, just raw energy.</p>\r
<p>In 2026, they’ll return to the Holy Ground for the second time, ready to crush the pit.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Harte Arbeit zahlt sich aus. Im Falle von Our Promise ist wohl kaum ein anderes Sprichwort so zutreffend. Das Stuttgarter Sextett besticht mit einer explosiven Kombination aus melodischen Hooks, brutalen Shouts und starkem Songwriting.</p>\r
<p>Dass die Band weiterhin unabhängig bleiben möchte und somit keine Kompromisse eingehen muss, hat sich bereits bezahlt gemacht. 2026 werden sie bereits zum zweiten Mal auf den Holy Ground zurückkehren, um euch im Pit einmal ordentlich in die Mangel zu nehmen. Gebraucht haben Our Promise dafür nicht mal sechs Jahre – beeindruckend.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/our-promise/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bUdloauzhNc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"our_promise_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/our_promise_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35137}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4414,uri:"https://our-promise.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4415,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ourpromise.band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4416,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ourpromise.band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4417,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/our-promise"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4ISeDymLgZtEyx5Dy4BaqD",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/0/csm_our_promise_26_661c3c384d.jpg",uid:1605},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ozzyfied - A Tribute to Ozzy Osbourne",uid:1258}],end:"1785355200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785351600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2818}],pathSegment:"ozzyfied-a-tribute-to-ozzy-osbourne",title:"Ozzyfied - A Tribute to Ozzy Osbourne",uid:1258},biography:'<p>Following the heartbreaking loss of the "Prince of Darkness", Ozzyfied celebrates the immortal legacy of Ozzy Osbourne and Black Sabbath with a sincere, loud, and deeply emotional homage. Fronted by scene veteran Henning Wanner (known for his work with Circle II Circle, among others), the band perfectly captures the inimitable aura of the original. After their highly acclaimed sets on the Full Metal Cruise and at Wacken Open Air, one thing is certain: if you want to experience milestones like "Crazy Train," "Mr. Crowley," or "War Pigs" with pure passion and maximum authenticity, you cannot miss this gold standard of a tribute show at the Landgasthof. Let the madness begin!</p>',biographyDe:"<p>Nach dem schmerzhaften Verlust des “Prince of Darkness“ feiert Ozzyfied das unsterbliche Vermächtnis von Ozzy Osbourne und Black Sabbath mit einer aufrichtigen, lauten und zutiefst emotionalen Hommage. Angeführt von Szene-Veteran Henning Wanner (u. a. Circle II Circle) fängt die Truppe aus dem Bergischen Land die unnachahmliche Aura des Originals perfekt ein. Spätestens nach ihren gefeierten Shows auf der Full Metal Cruise und dem Wacken Open Air ist klar: Wer Meilensteine wie “Crazy Train“, “Mr. Crowley“ oder “War Pigs“ mit purer Leidenschaft und maximaler Authentizität erleben will, darf diesen absoluten Ritterschlag von einer Tribute-Show im Landgasthof nicht verpassen. Let the madness begin! (Vielleicht lieber All Aboard?!)</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ozzyfied-a-tribute-to-ozzy-osbourne/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ozzified_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ozzified_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37058}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4793,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ozzyfiedoffical/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4794,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ozzyfied/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4795,uri:"https://dragon-productions.eu/artist/ozzyfied/?utm_source=ig&utm_medium=social&utm_content=link_in_bio&fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQPOTM2NjE5NzQzMzkyNDU5AAGne4eo88gWByYIourSik9qW9J3t1fRMBvOCNPHv64oaNXCYw8iyeCZrN28oIA_aem_XtUc4ST8kWzGbfNFUk_AeQ"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/2/csm_ozzified_26_a2b2c6cefa.jpg",uid:1738},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"P.O.D.",uid:1188}],end:"1785438000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785433500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2658}],pathSegment:"pod",title:"P.O.D.",uid:1188},biography:"<p>With all the justified hype around early-2000s Nu Metal, let’s not forget P.O.D.. The San Diego crew helped build the foundation right alongside Korn and other giants, earning their spot among the greats. Don’t believe us? Then let the whipping grooves, tight Hip-Hop/Metal crossover, and frontman Sonny Sandoval’s commanding stage presence convince you.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Bei allem Hype der aktuell berechtigterweise um die NuMetal Bands zu Beginn des jungen, neuen Jahrtausends herrscht darf man zwischen Korn und Co. P.O.D. nicht vergessen. Die Band aus San Diego hat den Boden ebenso bereitet wie andere Szenegrößen und sich somit ihren Platz in der Riege der ganz Großen redlich verdient. Glaubt ihr uns nicht? Dann lasst euch doch selbst vom peitschenden Groove, dem amtlichen Crossover zwischen Hip Hop und Metal oder der Bühnenpräsenz von Frotman Sonny Sandoval mitreisen.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/pod/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3B67QDqkDsS6H4SGpoYEIg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"POD_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/POD_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35769}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4491,uri:"https://payableondeath.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4492,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/POD/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4493,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/pod/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6KO6G41BBLTDNYOLefWTMU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/0/csm_POD_26_52d8ce1512.jpg",uid:1626},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Paleface Swiss",uid:1143}],end:"1785514500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785510900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2708}],pathSegment:"paleface-swiss",title:"Paleface Swiss",uid:1143},biography:"<p>You might escape the Grim Reaper, but Paleface Swiss will never lose your trail. The Zurich Deathcore heroes are like bloodhounds — always there when it counts and armed to the teeth with an arsenal of deadly riff barrages. No prisoners are taken here. With their latest album <i>Cursed</i>, the band has refined their sound even further and is now ready for their W:O:A debut. The only question is: Are you ready?</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Dem Sensenmann mag man entkommen, aber Paleface Swiss werden eure Spur nicht verlieren. Die Züricher Deathcore Helden sind wie gute Bluthunde: Immer zur Stelle, wenn es drauf ankommt und bis auf die Zähne bewaffnet mit einem Arsenal an todbringenden Riffsalven. Hier werden keine Gefangenen gemacht.&nbsp;<br />Mit ihrem aktuellen Album Cursed hat die Band noch einmal ihren Sound verfeinert und ist nun bereit für ihre Premiere auf dem W:O:A. Die Frage ist nur: Seid ihr es auch?</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/paleface-swiss/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VktMQwUmOq8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Paleface_Swiss-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Paleface_Swiss-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34816}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4272,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/palefaceswiss"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4273,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/palefaceswiss/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4274,uri:"https://palefaceswiss.com/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"467M2s2YxXdlL2ZpDUNL3A",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/2/csm_Paleface_Swiss-WOA26_9755b4556f.jpg",uid:1560},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Paradise Lost",uid:1169}],end:"1785504600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785501000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2696}],pathSegment:"paradise-lost",title:"Paradise Lost",uid:1169},biography:"<p>Paradise Lost don’t write songs – they carve epitaphs.<br />Each line a stone, each note a prayer made of soot and light.<br />With <i>“Obsidian”</i> they proved sorrow isn’t stagnation.<br />Architects of darkness, finding grace in decay.<br />Their sound smells of cold smoke and sacred wounds.<br />When the last echo fades, only silence – and truth – remains.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Paradise Lost schreiben keine Songs – sie graben Epitaphe.<br />Jede Zeile ein Stein, jede Note ein Gebet aus Ruß und Licht.<br />Mit <i>“Obsidian”</i> bewiesen sie, dass Schwermut kein Stillstand ist.<br />Sie sind Architekten der Dunkelheit, die Schönheit im Zerfall erkennen.<br />Ihr Sound riecht nach kaltem Rauch und heiligen Wunden.<br />Und wenn das letzte Echo verklingt, bleibt nur Stille – und Wahrheit.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/paradise-lost/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C1_kMRiyt5w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"oaradise_lost_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/oaradise_lost_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35130}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4387,uri:"https://paradiselost.co.uk"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4388,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/paradiselostofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4389,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/officialparadiselost/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4390,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@paradiselostofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"71vVmHeNgCVSa5SVmfvscU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/a/csm_oaradise_lost_26_339356239c.jpg",uid:1598},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Pentastone",uid:1253}],end:"1785263400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785286800",start:"1785218400",title:"Tuesday",uid:33},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785259800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2806}],pathSegment:"pentastone",title:"Pentastone",uid:1253},biography:"<p>When everything is getting on your nerves, Pentastone provides the perfect release valve. This five-piece Alternative Metal powerhouse from Darmstadt proves with sharp-edged '00s-style riffs and a massive dose of female empowerment that women are calling the shots in the heavy music scene. The heart of it all is frontwoman Lou, whose extraordinary vocals perfectly balance emotional depth with pure heaviness. Lyrically, the band completely discards blunt clichés, instead celebrating a fiercely strong, supportive community with a clear focus on mental health awareness. That this formula works is proven by a string of sold-out venues from Berlin to Munich and support slots for heavyweights like Eyes Set to Kill or Kælan Mikla. This Darmstadt energy bomb is coming to the Landgasthof to blow your mind and get your head banging all at once.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn euch alles auf den Zeiger geht, haben Pentastone das perfekte Ventil dafür. Die fünfköpfige Alternative-Metal-Walze aus Darmstadt beweist mit scharfkantigen Riffs der 00er-Jahre und einer gewaltigen Portion Female Empowerment, dass Frauen in der Heavy-Szene tonangebend sind. Herzstück des Ganzen ist Frontfrau Lou, deren außergewöhnliche Stimme perfekt zwischen emotionaler Tiefe und purer Härte balanciert. Inhaltlich pfeift die Truppe auf stumpfe Klischees: Hier wird mit dem klaren Fokus auf Mental Health Awareness eine verdammt starke, einander auffangende Community zelebriert. Dass dieses Rezept aufgeht, beweisen reihenweise ausverkaufte Hütten von Berlin bis München und Support-Gigs für Kaliber wie Eyes Set to Kill oder Kaelan Mikla. Diese Darmstädter Energiebombe kommt in den Landgasthof, um euch gleichzeitig den Kopf zu waschen und den Nacken zu massieren.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/pentastone/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8_yVpkYoVk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"pentastone_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/pentastone_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37051}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4776,uri:"https://www.pentastone.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4777,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/pentastone/?locale=de_DE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4778,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/pentastone_official/?hl=de"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2Ga7dFa3QASOZpORTAUD8l",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/c/csm_pentastone_26_fa39b86565.jpg",uid:1732},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Mexiko",shortNameDe:"Mexiko",shortNameEn:"Mexico",uid:148}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Phantom",uid:1144}],end:"1785345300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785342600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2644}],pathSegment:"phantom",title:"Phantom",uid:1144},biography:"<p>If the term ‘old school’ can still be used, then it certainly applies to PHANTOM GDL from Mexico. Although the quartet was only formed in 2021 in Guadalajara, Mexico, they stand for uncompromising old-school Thrash. Last year, scene connoisseurs were able to experience the bat disciples at small, hand-picked shows across Europe – apart from the pesky travel mishaps. Rest assured, we'll do everything we can to make sure the tour bus to Wacken doesn't break down and the Mexicans can deliver a proper Thrash Metal set.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn die Bezeichnung „old school“ noch verwendet werden darf, dann sicherlich im Zusammenhang mit PHANTOM GDL aus Mexiko. Das Quartett wurde zwar erst 2021 in Guadalajara gegründet, steht aber für kompromisslosen Thrash-Metal der alten Schule. Szene-Kenner konnten die Fledermaus Jünger bereits letztes Jahr auf handverlesenen Europa-Konzerten erleben – von den verflixten Anreise-Pannen mal abgesehen. Seid euch sicher, wir setzen alles daran, dass der Tourbus nach Wacken nicht abschmiert und die Mexikaner ein pechschwarzes Thrash Metal-Set zum Besten geben können.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/phantom/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GCKY3om0ToM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"phantom_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/phantom_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36337}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4275,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/phantom__speed/?hl=de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4276,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/phantommetalband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4277,uri:"https://phantombandgdl.bandcamp.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4541,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxqEC5vixLBlqEa1Ytz7kDg"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6f9WeAPRDSevpjBAyGfVmV",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/7/csm_phantom_26_2946b95d36.jpg",uid:1561},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Pig Destroyer",uid:1161}],end:"1785516300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785513600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Prowler In The Yard 25th Anniversary Set",uid:2723}],pathSegment:"pig-destroyer",title:"Pig Destroyer",uid:1161},biography:"<p>Ford, McDonald’s, or Coca-Cola — all iconic mainstream export hits from the USA. Part of pop culture for decades, shaping identities and setting styles for entire generations. Something similar can probably be said about the five gentlemen of Pig Destroyer. Firmly rooted in the underground extreme metal scene, the band from Richmond, Virginia stands for uncompromising brutality that is truly unparalleled. And let’s be honest, that interests us way more than any trends or pop cultures.&nbsp;Welcome back!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ford, McDonalds oder Coca-Cola – das alles sind im Mainstream verankerte Exportschlager der USA. Seit Jahrzehnten Teil der Pop-Kultur und Identitätsstifter sowie Style-Setter ganzer Generationen.<br />Gleiches kann wohl in ähnlicher Form auf die fünf Herren von Pig Destroyer gemünzt werden.<br />Fest im Underground der Extrem-Metal Szene verankert steht die Band aus Richmond, Virginia für kompromisslose Härte, die ihresgleichen sucht. Und sind wir mal ehrlich, das interessiert uns deutlich mehr als irgendwelche Trends oder Pop-Kulturen. Welcome Back!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/pig-destroyer/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCCQruCU3bU&list=RDXCCQruCU3bU&start_radio=1",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Pig_Destroyer-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Pig_Destroyer-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34840}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4338,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/TheRealPigDestroyer/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4339,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/pigdestroyerofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4340,uri:"https://www.pig-destroyer.com/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4raqfuxaWjPjrOQGb6zoa7",subtitle:"Prowler In The Yard 25th Anniversary Set",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/9/csm_Pig_Destroyer-WOA26_111d076650.jpg",uid:1584},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kolumbien",shortNameDe:"Kolumbien",shortNameEn:"Colombia",uid:47}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Poison The Preacher",uid:1195}],end:"1785339900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785337200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2643}],pathSegment:"poison-the-preacher",title:"Poison The Preacher",uid:1195},biography:"<p>POISON THE PREACHER know what the Ws in Wasted Wednesday stand for: wild and wicked, they shake the unholy grounds of our Wasteland. From Bogotá, the distant capital of Colombia, the four Metalheads travel to Wacken, the capital of Metal. They bring with them their debut album ‘Vs The World’ (2025) to convince you of their distinctive sound, somewhere between Thrash Metal, Hardcore and their deeply rooted Latin American soul.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>POISON THE PREACHER wissen wofür die Ws im Wasted Wednesday stehen: Wüst und wild bringen sie den unheiligen Boden zum Beben. Aus Bogotá, der weit entfernten Hauptstadt Kolumbiens, reisen die vier Metaller nach Wacken in die Hauptstadt des Metal. Im Gepäck haben sie das Debütalbum „Vs The World“ (2025), um euch von ihrem brachialen Sound irgendwo zwischen Thrash Metal, Hardcore und ihrer tiefverwurzelten lateinamerikanischen Seele zu überzeugen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/poison-the-preacher/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wl5vdSFOAzc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"poison_the_preacher_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/poison_the_preacher_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36340}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4545,uri:"https://poisonthepreacher.bandcamp.com/music"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4546,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/poisonthepreacher"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4547,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/poisonthepreacher"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3InxEfnjMqTJWqsWvHjjPU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/c/csm_poison_the_preacher_26_719f682a4a.jpg",uid:1643},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Powerwolf",uid:15}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:177},{artists:[{title:"Powerwolf",uid:15}],end:"1659823200",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1659817800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:663},{artists:[{title:"Powerwolf",uid:15}],end:"1785616200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785609900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2746}],pathSegment:"powerwolf",title:"Powerwolf",uid:15},biography:"<p>The bone-chilling howl of wolves echoes loudly over the flat farmlands of Schleswig-Holstein. Watch out, Wacken — the wolves are on the loose! After some time away, Germany’s hottest pack is finally paying us a visit again, bringing Power Metal of the highest caliber. Topped with a sophisticated and lavish stage show, their <i>Wake Up The Wicked</i> tour has Wacken on the map. And because we’re so excited about the Saarbrücken crew’s return, we’ll be howling along with them. Anyone who’s not into Metal might soon find their hair standing on end!</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Laut erklingt das markerschütternde Geheul der Wölfe über die flachen Ackerlandschaften Schleswig-Holsteins. Nimm dich in Acht Wacken: Die Wölfe sind los! Nach einiger Zeit der Abstinenz stattet uns Deutschlands angesagtestes Rudel endlich wieder einen Besuch ab. Mit im Gepäck: Power-Metal der Extraklasse. Mit einer ausgefeilten und opulenten Bühnenshow wird die Band ihre Wake Up The Wicked Tour auch nach Wacken bringen.</p>\r
<p>Und weil wir uns über den Besuch der Saarbrücker so sehr freuen, stimmen wir ebenfalls in deren Geheul mit ein. Jedem der es nicht mit Metal hält sollten also bald schon die Haare zu Berge stehen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/powerwolf/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhK2ev_O-pc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Powerwolf-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Powerwolf-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34819}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4280,uri:"https://www.powerwolf.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4281,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/powerwolfmetal"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4282,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/officialpowerwolf/?hl=en"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5HFkc3t0HYETL4JeEbDB1v",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/f/csm_Powerwolf-WOA26_acf32b8b68.jpg",uid:1563},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ragetrack - A Tribute to Rage against the Machine",uid:1256}],end:"1785340800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785337200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2816}],pathSegment:"ragetrack-a-tribute-to-rage-against-the-machine",title:"Ragetrack - A Tribute to Rage against the Machine",uid:1256},biography:"<p>When the Landgasthof suddenly smells of political force and explosive Crossover, it means Hannes, Sven, Bonny, and Luca have plugged in their gear. Standing as one of Europe’s most renowned Rage Against The Machine tribute bands, Ragetrack captures the raw, rebellious primal energy of the original as if the gods of rock themselves had cranked the volume to eleven. This four-piece doesn't deliver a lame, copy-paste show - they unleash a sweat-drenched manifestation of protest capable of waking the spirits of Woodstock from their deepest slumber. Every whipping riff and massive groove is a loaded weapon against stagnation, turning the entire crowd into a single bouncing sea of bodies.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wenn der Landgasthof plötzlich nach politischer Wucht und hochexplosivem Crossover riecht, haben Hannes, Sven, Bonny und Luca ihre Instrumente eingestöpselt. Als eine der bekanntesten “Rage Against The Machine“-Tribute-Bands Europas fangen Ragetrack aus Engelskirchen die rohe, rebellische Ur-Energie des Originals ein, als hätten die Götter des Rock persönlich die Regler hochgeschoben. Der Vierer liefert keine lahme, konforme Kopie ab, sondern eine schweißtreibende Manifestation des Protests, die selbst die Geister von Woodstock aus dem Tiefschlaf reißen würde. Jeder peitschende Riff und jeder fette Groove ist eine geladene Waffe gegen den Stillstand, die das Publikum in eine einzige, springende Bewegung verwandelt.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ragetrack-a-tribute-to-rage-against-the-machine/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ragetrack_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ragetrack_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37055}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4787,uri:"https://www.ragetrack.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4788,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ragetrack.de/?locale=de_DE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4789,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ragetrack/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/d/csm_ragetrack_26_4017f32523.jpg",uid:1736},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ricky Warwick",uid:1181}],end:"1785339900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785336300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2637}],pathSegment:"ricky-warwick",title:"Ricky Warwick",uid:1181},biography:"<p>RICKY WARWICK is undoubtedly a busy and tirelessly creative singer and guitarist. With The Almighty, New Model Army, Thin Lizzy, Black Star Riders and as a solo artist, he has compiled an impressive discography and released his new solo album ‘Blood Ties’ just this year. The single ‘Don't Leave Me In The Dark’ featuring Lita Ford was particularly well received by his fans, and you can look forward to hearing which hand-picked songs he will perform at W:O:A 2026.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>RICKY WARWICK ist ohne Frage ein vielbeschäftigter und unermüdlich kreativer Sänger und Gitarrist. Mit The Almighty, New Model Army, Thin Lizzy, Black Star Riders oder als Solomusiker hat er eine beeindruckende Diskografie zusammengestellt und veröffentlichte erst dieses Jahr sein neues Soloalbum „Blood Ties“. Bei seinen Fans stieß vor allem die Single „Don’t Leave Me In The Dark“ mit Lita Ford auf Begeisterung und ihr könnt gespannt sein, welche handverlesenen Songs ihr bei seiner Show auf dem Jubiläumsfestival zu hören bekommt.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ricky-warwick/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ehGbqFkZYgw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"ricky_warwick26c.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/ricky_warwick26c.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35826}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4460,uri:"https://www.rickywarwick.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4461,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/rickywarwickofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4462,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/rickywarwickofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4463,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/user/RickyWarwick"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5W7mxe09YZ9HfUimnNih8V",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/d/csm_ricky_warwick26c_9f35eea5b5.jpg",uid:1617},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Spanien",shortNameDe:"Spanien",shortNameEn:"Spain",uid:65}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Rise of Shadows",uid:1270}],end:"1785418200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785417000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Spain",uid:2665}],pathSegment:"rise-of-shadows",title:"Rise of Shadows",uid:1270},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Rise of the Shadows is a melodic death metal band from Medina del Campo, Spain, formed in 2019. Their sound blends the foundations of melodic death metal with elements of metalcore, deathcore, and other modern extreme metal influences. Drawing on existential reflection and social criticism, the lyrics explore personal and collective struggles through a dark yet emotional lens.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">After releasing three EPs (2020, 2023, and 2025), the band is currently working on their first full-length album. Combining experience and energy, Rise of the Shadows deliver intense live performances where melody and brutality meet to forge a powerful connection with the audience.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Rise of the Shadows ist eine Melodic-Death-Metal-Band aus Medina del Campo, Spanien, gegründet 2019. Ihr Sound verbindet die Grundlagen des Melodic Death Metal mit Elementen aus Metalcore, Deathcore und weiteren modernen Spielarten des Extreme Metal. Inspiriert von existenziellen Reflexionen und Gesellschaftskritik, beleuchten ihre Texte persönliche wie kollektive Kämpfe aus einer düsteren, doch emotionalen Perspektive.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Nach drei EPs (2020, 2023 und 2025) arbeitet die Band derzeit an ihrem ersten vollwertigen Album. Mit einer Mischung aus Erfahrung und Energie liefern Rise of the Shadows intensive Live-Auftritte, in denen Melodie und Brutalität aufeinandertreffen und eine kraftvolle Verbindung zum Publikum entsteht.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/rise-of-shadows/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U9wWXWJzDXQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"raise_of_the_shadows_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/raise_of_the_shadows_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37110}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4823,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/riseoftheshadowsband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4824,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Riseoftheshadowsband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2MxgkKOiWoRPTpDcNskI8A",subtitle:"Metal Battle Spain",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/e/2/csm_raise_of_the_shadows_26_5f881e5e68.jpg",uid:1751},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Australien",shortNameDe:"Australien",shortNameEn:"Australia",uid:14}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Rose Tattoo",uid:18}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:31},{artists:[{title:"Rose Tattoo",uid:18}],end:"1659633300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1659628800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:546},{artists:[{title:"Rose Tattoo",uid:18}],end:"1659620700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1659618000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:821},{artists:[{title:"Rose Tattoo",uid:18}],end:"1785362400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785357900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2620}],pathSegment:"rose-tattoo",title:"Rose Tattoo",uid:18},biography:`<p>Stuck on you – like a Rose Tattoo.</p>\r
<p>Angry Anderson and his Aussie gang are as much part of Wacken’s DNA as the Landgasthof. With former AC/DC bassist Mark Evans in the lineup, this five-piece reliably delivers pure Rock ’n’ Roll — slide guitars, tattoos, and tons of attitude. And 2026 marks their 50th anniversary — one more reason to hit the Holy Ground and blow the roof off.</p>\r
<p>Tats forever, forever tats!</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Stuck on you – like a Rose Tattoo. Angy Anderson und seine australische Gang gehören genauso zum Wacken Inventar wie der Landgasthof. Zuverlässig steht der Fünfer um den ehemaligen AC/DC Bassisten Mark Evans für Rock’n’Roll mit Slide Gitarren, Tattoos und jeder Menge Attitüde. Grund zum Feiern gibt es 2026 auch, denn Rose Tattoo werden 50. Noch ein Anreiz mehr auf den Holy Ground zurückzukehren und das Dach von der Hütte zu pusten.</p>\r
<p>Tats forever, forever tats!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/rose-tattoo/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fitciYI0jGI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"rose_tattoo26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/rose_tattoo26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35771}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4501,uri:"https://www.rosetattoo.com.au/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4502,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/RoseTattoo"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1WsfEkSfrPIhy1lK7ZLRRH",subtitle:"Farewell Tour",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/5/csm_rose_tattoo26_a5747c907d.jpg",uid:1629},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Running Wild",uid:1145}],end:"1785537900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785532500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2699}],pathSegment:"running-wild",title:"Running Wild",uid:1145},biography:"<p>Old Hands? No! The ultimate captains of the pirates<strong>!</strong> With a loud ARRR, we welcome Running Wild back to Wacken! They are regarded as the fathers of pirate metal and have inspired countless followers. With the absolute legend that is the album <i>Under Jolly Roger</i> (1987), they raised their flag high over the music world. Frontman Rolf Kasparek is not only the captain of this unstoppable ship but also the songwriter behind countless hits. Their songs tell tales of epic battles, hidden treasures, and revolutions — all backed by guitars that sound like they’re being played with a hook. Their stay in Wacken will be their last on stage – they honor us with one last show! Power Metal with depth? This way!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Urgesteine? Nein! Urpiraten! Mit einem lauten ARRR heißen wir Running Wild willkommen zurück in Wacken! Sie gelten als die Väter des Pirate Metal und sie ziehen unzählige Epigonen nach. Mit der absoluten Legende, die das Album „Under Jolly Roger (1987)“ schreibt, hissten sie ihre Flagge über die Musikwelt. Frontmann Rolf Kasparek ist nicht nur der Kapitän dieses unaufhaltbaren Schiffs, sondern auch der Songwriter hinter den unzähligen Hits. Die Songs handeln von epischen Schlachten, versteckten Schätzen und Revolutionen – alles mit Gitarren, die klingen, als würden sie mit einem Haken gespielt werden. Ihr Besuch in Wacken wird auch gleichzeitig ihr letzter sein – sie beehren uns für eine letzte finale Show! Power Metal mit Tiefgang? Hier entlang!&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/running-wild/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8mEKsJhuwbfY1jSDTxplog",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Running_Wild-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Running_Wild-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34818}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4278,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/runningwildmusic/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4279,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/runningwildmusic/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7954VFaZClkL503srfV5PE",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/f/csm_Running_Wild-WOA26_5c9b78de18.jpg",uid:1562},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sabaton",uid:2}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:74},{artists:[{title:"Sabaton",uid:2}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:78},{artists:[{title:"Sabaton",uid:2}],end:"1785624300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785618000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2753}],pathSegment:"sabaton",title:"Sabaton",uid:2},biography:`<p>These days, everyone’s talking about the headliners of tomorrow.</p>\r
<p>Who comes after Maiden? Who follows Metallica? Who takes the torch from Helloween?</p>\r
<p>And while we can still celebrate these legends, the next generation has long been ready.</p>\r
<p>Between bombast and history,</p>\r
<p>between fateful battles and epic heroes — there they stand:</p>\r
<p>the stadium-filling stormtroopers of Power Metal — Sabaton.</p>\r
<p>The Swedish flagship of the genre.</p>\r
<p>With well over a quarter of a century of band history and 11 albums as grand as they are defining, these battle-hardened bards return to the Holy Ground once more.</p>\r
<p>Ready, visors open and weapons drawn, to fight the next battle side by side with you, Metalheads.</p>\r
<p>They’re not just the headliners of tomorrow — they’re already leading the charge today.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Heutzutage wird viel über die Headliner von morgen gesprochen.&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Wer kommt nach Maiden, wer folgt auf Metallica, wer beerbt Helloween?&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Und während wir uns immer noch an diesen Helden erfreuen können, steht die nächste Generation doch schon lange bereit. Zwischen Bombast und Historie.</p>\r
<p>Schicksalsträchtigen Schlachten und epischen Helden da stehen sie, die Stadion füllenden Sturmtruppen des Power Metals – Sabaton.&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Das schwedische Aushängeschild des Genres.&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Mit nun mehr deutlich über einem Vierteljahrhundert Bandgeschichte und 11 ebenso grandiosen, wie richtungsweisenden Alben kehren die fünf kampferprobten Barden wieder auf den Holy Ground zurück.&nbsp;</p>\r
<p>Bereit mit offenem Visier und bis an die Zähne bewaffnet die nächste Schlacht, Seite an Seite mit euch auszutragen, Metalheads! Sie sind nicht nur die möglichen Headliner von morgen – sie führen unser Feld bereits jetzt an.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sabaton/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPbaLrbU6Ho",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sabaton_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sabaton_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36555}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4680,uri:"https://www.sabaton.net"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4681,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/sabaton/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4682,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sabatonofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3o2dn2O0FCVsWDFSh8qxgG",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/4/csm_sabaton_26_143decf5a4.jpg",uid:1691},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sacred Steel",uid:1146}],end:"1785362400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785358800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2647}],pathSegment:"sacred-steel",title:"Sacred Steel",uid:1146},biography:"<p>It has been a long time since SACRED STEEL first played at W:O:A in the 90s. So it is even more exciting that Gerrit Mutz and his bandmates will headline Wasted Wednesday 2026. The Metal machine from Baden-Württemberg got lots of energy with new members Toni Ieva on bass and Jörn Langenfeld on guitar, yet remain true to their powerful discography and trademarks, as we recently heard on their latest album ‘Ritual Supremacy’ (2025). Horns up and hand on heart – this is going to be legendary!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Lang ist es her, als SACRED STEEL in den 90ern das erste Mal auf dem W:O:A gespielt haben. Umso größer die Freude, dass die Metaller um Gerrit Mutz den Wasted Wednesday 2026 anführen. Die Baden-Württemberger Stahlschmiede strotzt mit neuen Mitgliedern, Toni Ieva am Bass und Jörn Langenfeld als Saitenhexer, nur so vor Energie und bleibt dennoch ihrer mächtigen Diskografie und ihren Trademarks verbunden, was wir jüngst auf dem aktuellen Longplayer „Ritual Supremacy“ (2025) hören konnten. Horns up und Hand aufs Herz – das wird legendär!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sacred-steel/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YaKCeyQA_8o",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sacred_steel_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sacred_steel_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36336}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4283,uri:"https://www.sacredsteel.de/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4284,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/sacredsteelofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4285,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sacredsteelofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0IZvYyslQEyG9Aa4Sy2orL",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/0/csm_sacred_steel_26_78f1daf932.jpg",uid:1564},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sagenbringer",uid:1210}],end:"1785426300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785422700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2683}],pathSegment:"sagenbringer",title:"Sagenbringer",uid:1210},biography:"<p>A Folk Metal&nbsp;wildfire&nbsp;is&nbsp;approaching&nbsp;our&nbsp;sacred&nbsp;field, led&nbsp;by Sagenbringer. For&nbsp;five&nbsp;years&nbsp;Azaril, Skjomi, Haldruhir and Trygve have&nbsp;been&nbsp;pulling&nbsp;Metalheads&nbsp;into&nbsp;their&nbsp;magical&nbsp;universe. And like all great&nbsp;storytellers, they&nbsp;possess a special&nbsp;gift: once&nbsp;enchanted, you&nbsp;simply&nbsp;cannot&nbsp;escape.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ein Folk Metal Flächenbrand nähert sich unserem heiligen Acker und an seiner Speerspitze stehen keiner Geringeren als Azaril, Skjomi, Haldruhir, Trygve besser bekannt als Sagenbringer. Mit viel Geschick und einer ganzen Menge Liebe zum Detail ziehen die vier seit 5 Jahren Metalheads in ihren Bann und nehmen sie mit auf eine Reise durch ihre Welt. Wie es sich für echte Erzähler gehört, wohnt auch ihnen eine ganz besondere Gabe inne: Einmal verzaubert, kann man sich ihnen nicht mehr entziehen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sagenbringer/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uI3eArehLps",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sagenbringer_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sagenbringer_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36389}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4632,uri:"https://www.sagenbringer.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4633,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/sagenbringer/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4634,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sagenbringer_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"66ezn48mPS89ukz6Fo3nqx",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/2/csm_sagenbringer_26_b57d26c84d.jpg",uid:1673},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Savatage",uid:1147}],end:"1785441600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785436200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2650}],pathSegment:"savatage",title:"Savatage",uid:1147},biography:"<p>Savatage combine power and prog metal like no other. Founded by the brother duo Jon and Criss Oliva in Florida, they quickly became one of the most influential American bands. Known for their dramatic and symphonic concept albums, they made a name for themselves with classics like <i>Hall of the Mountain King</i>, <i>Gutter Ballet</i>, and <i>Streets: A Rock Opera</i>. After the tragic death of Criss Oliva in 1993, Jon Oliva carried on his legacy. From this legacy, the globally successful <i>Trans-Siberian Orchestra</i> evolved. After a long break, Savatage reunited in 2015 — and now they are also gracing the Holy Ground. We can hardly wait to dive into their world.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Savatage vereinen Power und Prog-Metal wie kaum ein Anderer. Gegründet von dem Brüderduo Jon und Criss Oliva in Florida sind sie schnell zu einer der einflussreichsten US-Amerikanischen Bands erkoren. Bekannt für dramatisch und symphonische Konzeptalben, haben sie sich mit Klassikern wie <i>Hall of the Mountain King, Gutter Ballet&nbsp;</i>und<i> Streets: A Rock Opera</i> einen Namen gemacht. Nach dem tragischen Tod von Criss Olivia 1993 führte John Oliva sein Vermächtnis fort.&nbsp; Aus diesem entwickelt sich das weltweit erfolgreiche <i>Trans-Siberian Orchestra.&nbsp;</i>Aber nach einer langen Pause trat Savatage 2015 wieder gemeinsam auf – und nun beehren sie endlich auch den Holy Ground, wir können es kaum abwarten in ihre Welt einzutauchen.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/savatage/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxy4Z6XF2t00cVSN0Qa55Uw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Savatage-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Savatage-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34821}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4286,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/savatage/?locale=de_DE"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4287,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thisissavatage/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3N1B1g6JtIgd6ClRkzD4yT",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/9/csm_Savatage-WOA26_6be2e38515.jpg",uid:1565},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Saviourself",uid:1219}],end:"1785414600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785412800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2687}],pathSegment:"saviourself",title:"Saviourself",uid:1219},biography:"<p>There&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;something in the&nbsp;water in Kiel. Otherwise&nbsp;we&nbsp;can’t&nbsp;explain&nbsp;the&nbsp;sheer&nbsp;intensity&nbsp;with&nbsp;which&nbsp;Saviourself&nbsp;unleash&nbsp;their&nbsp;Nu metal&nbsp;infused&nbsp;with&nbsp;Hardcore on stage. Let’s&nbsp;be honest — the 1990s are&nbsp;looking&nbsp;north&nbsp;with&nbsp;envy, watching&nbsp;what&nbsp;this&nbsp;four-piece has&nbsp;been&nbsp;building&nbsp;since 2017. And that’s&nbsp;exactly&nbsp;why&nbsp;we’re&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;this&nbsp;full-force&nbsp;neckbreaker&nbsp;to&nbsp;the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Irgendetwas muss in Kiel im Wasser sein. Anders können wir uns die Intensität mit der Saviourself ihren NuMetal mit deutlichem Hardcore Einschlag auf die Bretter bringen und ihresgleichen sucht, nicht erklären. Sind wir ehrlich, die 90er schauen gerade neidisch in den hohen Norden und bewundern, was der Vierer seit 2017 auf die Beine stellt. Und genau deswegen holen wir uns eben auch die volle Prise Nackenbrecher auf den Holy Ground.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/saviourself/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kGm11oNWVNA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"saviourself_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/saviourself_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36411}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4675,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/saviourselfde/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4676,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/faceiourself/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"7CkHF3MbHm4kTdB9ZOJkV4",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/5/csm_saviourself_26_2359155f97.jpg",uid:1689},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Saxon",uid:175}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:178},{artists:[{title:"Saxon",uid:175}],end:"1785519000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785514500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2702}],pathSegment:"saxon",title:"Saxon",uid:175},biography:"<p>They’re the kind of band you meet on the highway when you think you understand metal — and they smile as they run you down.<br />&nbsp;Biff Byford grabbed death by the collar, snarled in his face, and kept the mic hot.<br />&nbsp;<i>Carpe Diem</i> dropped first, the heart surgery came after — the title wasn’t a mantra, it was prophecy.&nbsp;The riffs spin like jet engines, his voice soaked in denim, leather, and pure octane.&nbsp;Every note smells of&nbsp;dust, and defiance — the sound of survival turned sacred.&nbsp;Wacken is Saxon, Saxon is Wacken — welded together in noise and legend.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Saxon sind die Typen, die du auf dem Highway triffst, wenn du denkst, du hättest Metal verstanden – und sie überfahren dich lächelnd. Biff Byford hat den Tod am Revers gepackt, ihm die Zähne gezeigt und weitergesungen. Erst kam das Album “Carpe Diem” dann Biff’s Herz OP – der Name Programm: kein Comeback, sondern ein Kriegsruf. Die Gitarren sind Turbinen, die Stimme klingt nach Denim, Leder und Gasoline. Wacken ist Saxon und DSaxon ist Wacken. Eine Verbindung, die niemand so schnell trennen wird.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/saxon/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QOREbJ4D70",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"saxon_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/saxon_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35109}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:3595,uri:"https://saxon747.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:3596,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/saxon/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4355,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/saxon.official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4356,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@PlanetSaxon"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"71vVmHeNgCVSa5SVmfvscU",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/6/csm_saxon_26_0097ea04d2.jpg",uid:1284},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Ungarn",shortNameDe:"Ungarn",shortNameEn:"Hungary",uid:95}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Seers of Light",uid:1266}],end:"1785316800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785315600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Hungary",uid:2609}],pathSegment:"seers-of-light",title:"Seers of Light",uid:1266},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Seers of Light is a six-piece melodic progressive metal band from Budapest, Hungary, formed in 2022. They bend atmospheric melodies into powerful metal — a sound defined by commanding female vocals, heavy guitar riffs, and dynamic instrumental passages built around expressive solos.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">In 2025, the band recorded and released a four-song live session as a preview of their upcoming eight-song album, King of Dreamers.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Seers of Light ist eine sechsköpfige Melodic-Progressive-Metal-Band aus Budapest, Ungarn, gegründet 2022. Sie verschmelzen atmosphärische Melodien mit kraftvollem Metal – ein Sound, der von markantem weiblichem Gesang, wuchtigen Gitarrenriffs und dynamischen Instrumentalpassagen mit ausdrucksstarken Soli geprägt ist.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">2025 nahm die Band eine vierteilige Live-Session auf und veröffentlichte sie als Vorbote ihres kommenden achtteiligen Albums King of Dreamers.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/seers-of-light/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrvrM8nDHD8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"seers_of_light_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/seers_of_light_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37106}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4814,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/seers_of_light_band"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4815,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/seersoflight"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"Metal Battle Hungary",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/1/csm_seers_of_light_26_d43bfa874a.jpg",uid:1747},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Philippinen",shortNameDe:"Philippinen",shortNameEn:"Philippines",uid:168}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sentient Void",uid:1269}],end:"1785412200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785411000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Philipines",uid:2663}],pathSegment:"sentient-void",title:"Sentient Void",uid:1269},biography:'<p class="text-justify">Sentient Void is a six-piece metal band from Iloilo City, Philippines, who began their musical journey together in 2022. Driven by a shared dedication to the craft, they secured their place on the international stage at their national heat — and this July they cross borders to represent the Philippines on the global stage at Wacken Open Air in Germany.</p>',biographyDe:'<p class="text-justify">Sentient Void ist eine sechsköpfige Metal-Band aus Iloilo City, Philippinen, die ihre gemeinsame musikalische Reise 2022 begann. Getragen von ihrer Hingabe zum Handwerk, sicherten sie sich beim nationalen Vorentscheid ihren Platz auf der internationalen Bühne – und im Juli überqueren sie nun Grenzen, um die Philippinen beim Wacken Open Air in Deutschland zu vertreten.</p>',detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sentient-void/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sentient_void_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sentient_void_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37109}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4821,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sentientvoid.ph"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4822,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/sentientvoid.ph"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"48QFXbgDdZi3rSjDj3BeKo",subtitle:"Metal Battle Philippines",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/4/csm_sentient_void_26_5fec72603f.jpg",uid:1750},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Brasilien",shortNameDe:"Brasilien",shortNameEn:"Brazil",uid:29}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sepultura",uid:1148}],end:"1785543300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785538800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2704}],pathSegment:"sepultura",title:"Sepultura",uid:1148},biography:"<p>What could we actually say? Sepultura are one of the greats.&nbsp; The institution began in 1984 in Belo Horizonte with brothers Max and Igor Cavalera — initially as a thrash/death band, but with <i>Chaos A.D.</i> and <i>Roots</i>, they firmly established themselves as pioneers of groove metal. Despite turmoil, Sepultura has prevailed, continuously evolving musically while remaining politically sharp-edged. Even without the original lineup, they uphold the band's spirit. At Wacken, we get to welcome them for the 5th time, and each time we’re more excited. Sepultura remains a milestone of international metal — political, innovative, and uncompromising. Now let us gather one last time to be witnesses of absolute greatness.&nbsp;</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sepultura gehören zu den ganz Großen. Gegründet 1984 in Belo Horizonte von den Brüdern Max und Igor Cavalera etablierte sich die Riff-Maschine als Thrash-/Death-Band, bevor &nbsp;<i>„Chaos A.D“&nbsp;</i>und <i>„Roots“&nbsp;</i>zeigen sie sich stark als Groove-Metal Pioniere. Trotz Turbulenzen, setzt Sepultura sich vehement durch und entwickeln sich musikalisch immer weiter und bleiben politisch scharfkantig. Auch ohne Originalbesetzung halten sie den Spirit der Band hoch. Auf Wacken dürfen wir sie zum 5. Mal begrüßen und freuen uns jedes Mal mehr. Sepultura bleibt ein Meilenstein des internationalen Metal – politisch, innovativ und kompromisslos. Nun kommt ein letztes Mal rum und lasst uns Zeugen von absoluter Größe werden!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sepultura/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4Prl7UQx5i5PgRUh-O5XBg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Sepultura-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Sepultura-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34822}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4288,uri:"https://www.sepultura.com.br/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4289,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sepultura"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4290,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/search/top?q=sepultura"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6JW8wliOEwaDZ231ZY7cf4",subtitle:"Last German Festival Show",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/1/csm_Sepultura-WOA26_f6b8328d6d.jpg",uid:1566},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Litauen",shortNameDe:"Litauen",shortNameEn:"Lithuania",uid:126}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Sinamort",uid:1224}],end:"1785335700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785334500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Lithuania",uid:2627}],pathSegment:"sinamort",title:"Sinamort",uid:1224},biography:`<p class="text-justify">SINAMORT is a progressive doom metal quartet from Lithuania, fronted by songwriter, guitarist and vocalist Juozas Grigas, with Rimantas Galvonas (guitar), Paulius Musteikis (bass), and newest member Vykintas Vainius (drums).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">The band aims to transcend the boundaries of the metal genre by fusing crushing, unorthodox riffing with complex harmony — interspersed with moments of calm melancholy and atmospheric passages. Think classic death/doom formula merged with modern progressive metal.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their debut album THE IDLE VEIL was nominated for Best Doom Metal Album of the Year by Metalstorm.net and dubbed "an adrenaline shot to the heart of death doom" by reviewers.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">SINAMORT ist ein Progressive-Doom-Metal-Quartett aus Litauen, angeführt von Songwriter, Gitarrist und Sänger Juozas Grigas, ergänzt durch Rimantas Galvonas (Gitarre), Paulius Musteikis (Bass) und den neuesten Zugang Vykintas Vainius (Schlagzeug).</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Die Band sprengt bewusst die Grenzen des Metal-Genres und verbindet wuchtiges, unorthodoxes Riffing mit komplexer Harmonik – durchzogen von Momenten ruhiger Melancholie und atmosphärischen Passagen. Klassisches Death/Doom-Schema trifft auf modernen Progressive Metal.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr Debütalbum THE IDLE VEIL wurde von Metalstorm.net als „Bestes Doom-Metal-Album des Jahres" nominiert und von den Rezensenten als „eine Adrenalinspritze ins Herz des Death Doom" gefeiert.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sinamort/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zf8cuo1HZMM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sinamort_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sinamort_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36689}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4691,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sinamortofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4692,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/sinamort"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4693,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@sinamort1282"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5MIQTIloEJunbdyIcANNwW",subtitle:"Metal Battle Lithuania",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/7/csm_sinamort_26_76b1458fee.jpg",uid:1695},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Skyline",uid:152}],end:"1753970400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1753966800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2222},{artists:[{title:"Skyline",uid:152}],end:"1753651800",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753664400",start:"1753596000",title:"Sunday",uid:30},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1753646400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2539},{artists:[{title:"Skyline",uid:152}],end:"1753978500",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754010000",start:"1753941600",title:"Thursday",uid:25},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1753975800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2596},{artists:[{title:"Skyline",uid:152}],end:"1785420000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785416400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2648},{artists:[{title:"Skyline",uid:152}],end:"1785100500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785114000",start:"1785045600",title:"Sunday",uid:31},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785096000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2797}],pathSegment:"skyline",title:"Skyline",uid:152},biography:"<p>They are undoubtedly one of the bands with a very special relationship to the festival. SKYLINE opened the first W:O:A in 1990 and they will also be rocking the Holy Ground at the anniversary festival. Andreas ‘Gösy’ Schlüter and his bandmates have plenty of material to celebrate on their two albums “Uncovered” (2019) and ‘Human Monster’ (2024), including the two Wacken anthems ‘This is W:O:A’ and ‘30 Years Ago’. In honor of Diedel we raise our horns up high!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie gehören ohne Frage zu den Bands mit einer ganz besonderen Beziehung zum Festival. SKYLINE eröffneten das erste W:O:A im Jahr 1990 und auch zum Jubiläum rocken sie den Holy Ground. Andreas „Gösy“ Schlüter und seine Mitstreiter haben auf ihren beiden Alben „Uncovered“ (2019) und „Human Monster“ (2024) jede Menge Material zum Feiern, u.a. die beiden Wacken-Hymnen „This is „W:O:A“ und „30 Years Ago“. Diedel zu Ehren recken wir die Pommesgabel extra weit in die Höhe!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/skyline/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXq0__ipINAnvZT9LXuMX3A",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"skyline_2024.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2024/skyline_2024.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36390}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4635,uri:"https://skylineofficial.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4636,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/SkylineOfficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4637,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/skyline.official"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"648WDOhkiezX4fVNIfqbD4",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/5/csm_skyline_2024_a76c70015c.jpg",uid:1674},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Australien",shortNameDe:"Australien",shortNameEn:"Australia",uid:14}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Skynd",uid:170}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:101},{artists:[{title:"Skynd",uid:170}],end:"1753910100",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1753906500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2392},{artists:[{title:"Skynd",uid:170}],end:"1785537900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785534300",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2719}],pathSegment:"skynd",title:"Skynd",uid:170},biography:"<p>Skynd are back at W:O:A! The enigmatic singer of the same name and her partner Father return to the Holy Ground once again to captivate the crowd with a fusion of electronic music, brutal outbursts, and chilling lyrics inspired by real crimes. The Australian duo, who prefer to keep their identities under wraps, will make the long journey from Down Under once more—just for you!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Skynd sind zurück beim W:O:A! Die geheimnisvolle Sängerin gleichen Namens und ihr Partner Father kehren erneut auf den Holy Ground zurück, um das Publikum mit einer Mischung aus elektronischer Musik, brutalen Ausbrüchen und erschütternden, von realen Verbrechen inspirierten Texten zu fesseln. Das australische Duo, das seine Identität lieber geheim hält, nimmt die lange Reise aus Down Under erneut auf sich – nur für euch!<br />&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/skynd/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KmpQcXTJfpk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"skynd26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/skynd26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35823}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4532,uri:"https://skynd-music.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4533,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/skynd.music"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4534,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/skynd_music/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3Ca8UhvMDcgM1zyfAZGw3M",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/3/csm_skynd26_fdaccaa45e.jpg",uid:1640},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Island",shortNameDe:"Island",shortNameEn:"Iceland",uid:103}],events:[{artists:[{title:"SÓT",uid:1235}],end:"1785347700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785346500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Iceland",uid:2631}],pathSegment:"sot",title:"SÓT",uid:1235},biography:`<p class="text-justify">SÓT is a sludge, groove, stoner, and doom metal band from Iceland. Emerging onto the underground scene in 2023, they quickly built a reputation for powerful live performances and relentless energy.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their debut album Beware (2025) has been played relentlessly across Iceland — but now it's time for new music, a new sound, and a new chapter, which they'll unleash at Wacken Open Air.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">SÓT ist eine Sludge-, Groove-, Stoner- und Doom-Metal-Band aus Island. Seit ihrem Auftauchen in der Underground-Szene 2023 haben sie sich rasch einen Ruf für kraftvolle Liveauftritte und kompromisslose Energie erspielt.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr Debütalbum Beware (2025) wurde quer durch Island unermüdlich gespielt – doch jetzt steht ein neues Kapitel an: neue Musik, ein neuer Sound, neu entfesselt beim Wacken Open Air.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/sot/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AeqR78Nvd3U",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"sot_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/sot_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36966}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4729,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thesotofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4730,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thesotofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6Nc1Qeqwnbi0odTnFc0Lua",subtitle:"Metal Battle Iceland",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/6/csm_sot_26_0252001d7e.jpg",uid:1711},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Zypern",shortNameDe:"Zypern",shortNameEn:"Cyprus",uid:52}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Speak in Whispers",uid:1221}],end:"1785319800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785318600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Cyprus",uid:2610}],pathSegment:"speak-in-whispers",title:"Speak in Whispers",uid:1221},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Speak In Whispers is a progressive groove metal band from Cyprus, founded in 2017. They've become a mainstay of the live circuit, known for high-energy shows and an intricate, groove-heavy sound.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">The band has played Bloodstock Open Air 2025 and shared stages with Freak Kitchen, Rage, Poem, Planet of Zeus, and Welicoruss, among others. Their 2020 debut EP The Dark Descent introduced their style; their full-length Crystalline Structures followed on March 28, 2025, via M&amp;O Music.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Speak In Whispers ist eine Progressive-Groove-Metal-Band aus Zypern, gegründet 2017. Längst eine feste Größe in der Live-Szene, ist die Band bekannt für energiegeladene Shows und ihren komplexen, groove-lastigen Sound.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Sie spielten beim Bloodstock Open Air 2025 und teilten die Bühne unter anderem mit Freak Kitchen, Rage, Poem, Planet of Zeus und Welicoruss. Ihre Debüt-EP The Dark Descent (2020) etablierte ihren Stil; ihr Debütalbum Crystalline Structures erschien am 28. März 2025 über M&amp;O Music.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/speak-in-whispers/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AQ7C-HvyDhY",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"speak_in_whispers_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/speak_in_whispers_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36686}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4683,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/speak.in.whispers"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4684,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/speakinwhispers"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4685,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@speakinwhispersband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"61Usxx24TwxGUlTUhE2S4u",subtitle:"Metal Battle Cyprus",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/9/csm_speak_in_whispers_26_157b14e684.jpg",uid:1692},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Kanada",shortNameDe:"Kanada",shortNameEn:"Canada",uid:36}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Spectral Wound",uid:1175}],end:"1785430800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785428100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2667}],pathSegment:"spectral-wound",title:"Spectral Wound",uid:1175},biography:`<p>From the deep forests and endless mountain ranges of Canada rises an entity devoted to spreading the never-ending darkness and claustrophobic panic of its music across the world. Spectral Wound and their traditional Black Metal have been making massive waves in the underground – and now they’re set to conquer the stages of Wacken.</p>\r
<p>But beware: once you follow this path, there’s no turning back!</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Den tiefen Wäldern und endlosen Berglandschaften Kanadas entsteigt eine Entität, die es sich auf die dunklen Fahnen geschrieben hat, die nie endende Dunkelheit und klaustrophobische Panik ihrer Musik hinaus in die Welt zu tragen. Spectral Wound und ihr traditioneller Black Metal schlagen hohe Wellen im Untergrund und werden nun die Wacken Bühnen entern. Aber Achtung: Wenn ihr auf diesen Weg folgt, gibt es kein Zurück!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/spectral-wound/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SLrLtrrZM68",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"spectral_wound26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/spectral_wound26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35144}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4429,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/spectralwoundcontramundi/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4430,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/spectral.wound/ Instagram"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3i6zP2x9GMBV3WyRzqQtM6",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/e/csm_spectral_wound26_3263ad4710.jpg",uid:1609},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Stonem",uid:1211}],end:"1785591000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785589200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2783}],pathSegment:"stonem",title:"Stonem",uid:1211},biography:`<p>Cooler&nbsp;than&nbsp;cool: Stonem.</p>\r
<p>Anyone&nbsp;who&nbsp;attended&nbsp;Full&nbsp;Metal Cruise 2025 already&nbsp;knows&nbsp;the Augsburg Modern Metal&nbsp;crew. Since 2014 they’ve&nbsp;been&nbsp;conquering&nbsp;stages&nbsp;with a groove-heavy mix of brutal&nbsp;Metal, soaring clean vocals and a shot&nbsp;of&nbsp;Rock’n’Roll attitude. Next stop: Wacken, Holy Ground.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Cool, cooler, Stonem! Wer sich die Full&nbsp;Metal Cruise 2025 gut schmecken lassen hat, kennt die Augsburger Modern Metal Truppe, die bereits seit 2014 die Bühnen dieser Welt stürmt. Alle, die bisher noch zu den Unwissenden zählen seien gewarnt: Der Groove, der bei Stonem auf beinharte Metalparts trifft, die Shouts, die sich im Wechselspiel mit cleanen Vocals ergänzen und der nötige Schuss Rock’n’Roll Attitüde machen die Band zu einer fast süchtig machenden Erfahrung. Nächster Halt: Wacken, Holy Ground</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/stonem/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxsLwcMcmMc",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"stonem_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/stonem_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36391}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4638,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/StonemMetal/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4639,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/stonem_metal/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4h4QdZPbKp8lz7PEA1FqkO",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/9/csm_stonem_26_e1ff4b71dd.jpg",uid:1675},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Storm Seeker",uid:430}],end:"1659807000",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659803400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:699},{artists:[{title:"Storm Seeker",uid:430}],end:"1785432600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785429000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2684}],pathSegment:"storm-seeker",title:"Storm Seeker",uid:430},biography:"<p>Set your sail and join us on a voyage into the legendary pirate world of STORM SEEKER! A breath of fresh air is indeed blowing through the Folk rockers, as they have released their first album with new singer Manuel Depryck, entitled ‘Set Your Sails’. But the compass hasn't strayed from the band's familiar and beloved course: Cheery sea shanties, tales of boozy nights in the harbour pub and mighty sea adventures await you. Arrrr, it's going to be hell of a party!</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Setzt die Segel und brecht mit uns auf in die sagenumwobene Piratenwelt von STORM SEEKER! Bei den Folk-Rockern weht in der Tat ein frischer Wind, da sie mit „Set Your Sails“ das erste Album mit ihrem neuen Sänger Manuel Depryck von der Leine gelassen haben. Doch der Kompass weicht nicht ab vom altbekannten und geschätzten Kurs der Band: Muntere Seemannslieder, Geschichten von durchzechten Nächten in der Hafenkneipe und mächtigen Seeabenteuern warten auf euch. Arrrr, das wird ein Fest!</p>\r
`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/storm-seeker/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UUlhSXG6dSk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"stormseeker26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/stormseeker26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35776}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4515,uri:"https://www.storm-seeker.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4516,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/stormseekerband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4517,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Stormseekerband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4zAK8a87dIdPw6xRYvsr4c",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/9/csm_stormseeker26_ffac69751b.jpg",uid:1634},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Subway to Sally",uid:93}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:179},{artists:[{title:"Subway to Sally",uid:93}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:423},{artists:[{title:"Subway to Sally",uid:93}],end:"1785542400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785537900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2712}],pathSegment:"subway-to-sally",title:"Subway to Sally",uid:93},biography:"<p>Fortunately, the rumours circulating after 30 years of outstanding band history did not come true. SUBWAY TO SALLY is still around, stronger than ever! On their current album ‘Post Mortem’ (2024), the Mittelalter&nbsp;Rock institution has proven that those declared dead live longer and that they still firmly hold the sceptre of their genre in their hands. So it feels great that Eric Fish and his comrades are finally returning to W:O:A after several years of break for&nbsp;their magical 13th show on the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Zum Glück wurde nicht wahr, was nach 30 Jahren herausragender Bandgeschichte gemunkelt wurde. SUBWAY TO SALLY gibt es noch, stärker als jemals zuvor!&nbsp;Auf ihrem aktuellen Album „Post Mortem“ (2024) hat die Mittelalter&nbsp;Rock-Institution bewiesen, dass Totgesagte länger leben und dass sie noch immer das Zepter ihres Genres fest in der Hand haben. So fühlt es sich großartig an, dass Eric Fish und co. nach mehreren Jahren Pause endlich wieder auf das W:O:A zurückkehren – für ihre verflixte und magische 13. Show auf dem Holy Ground.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/subway-to-sally/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q-pgg4lmjrM",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"subway_to_sally_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/subway_to_sally_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36392}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4640,uri:"https://subwaytosally.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4641,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/subwaytosally"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4642,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/subwaytosallyofficial"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"544X9aDcwFDSon8HevRcqg",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/3/csm_subway_to_sally_26_c89a7c04fa.jpg",uid:1676},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"T.H. and the Boneshakerz",uid:1244}],end:"1785070800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785114000",start:"1785045600",title:"Sunday",uid:31},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785067200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2793}],pathSegment:"th-and-the-boneshakerz",title:"T.H. and the Boneshakerz",uid:1244},biography:`<p>"Real, handmade Rock music with heart and balls…” – that’s how multi-instrumentalist Tim Husung loves to describe his sound. The former drummer for John Diva &amp; The Rockets Of Love, who has also laid down the beat for icons like Alice Cooper and Doro, has traded his seat behind the drums for the spotlight. After laying down the tracks for the debut album entirely on his own, he brought his best friends - officially known as the Boneshakerz - on board for the new record.<br />Together, they’re bringing a gritty, authentic fusion of Southern Rock and Retro Blues to the stage of the Landgasthof. Powered by a heavy Hammond organ in the style of Deep Purple legend Jon Lord, their sound hits you straight in the gut. Grab your sunglasses, grease up your hips, and shake your bones to the finest Blues'n'Roll!!<br />&nbsp;</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>“Echte, handgemachte Rockmusik mit Herz und Eiern…” - so beschreibt Multiinstrumentalist Tim Husung seinen Sound am liebsten selbst. Der ehemalige Schlagzeuger von John Diva &amp; The Rockets Of Love, der auch schon für Ikonen wie Alice Cooper oder Doro die Sticks fliegen ließ, hat den Platz hinter den Kesseln gegen das Rampenlicht getauscht: Nachdem er das Debütalbum noch im Alleingang einprügelte, hat er für das neue Werk seine besten Freunde - offiziell bekannt als die Boneshakerz - ins Boot geholt. Zusammen bringen sie eine dreckige, authentische Fusion aus Southern Rock und Retro-Blues auf die Bretter des Landgasthofs, die dank einer fetten Hammond-Orgel im Stile von Deep-Purple-Legende Jon Lord direkt in die Magengrube geht. Packt die Sonnenbrillen ein, ölt die Hüften und schüttelt Eure Knochen für feinsten Blues ’n’ Roll!!<br />&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/th-and-the-boneshakerz/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WtD7WM4AFwY",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"TH_boneshakerz_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/TH_boneshakerz_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37039}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4748,uri:"https://www.boneshakerz.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4749,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/th_boneshakerz"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4750,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/THTheBoneshakerz"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4751,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/timhusung"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4KgGKjQunCMZUMatnXtUZE",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/7/csm_TH_boneshakerz_26_f0b6fae8fe.jpg",uid:1720},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Temple of the Absurd",uid:1212}],end:"1785437100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785433500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2692}],pathSegment:"temple-of-the-absurd",title:"Temple of the Absurd",uid:1212},biography:"<p>Temple Of The Absurd is one of those names that make old‑school thrash fans grin instantly. Sabina Classen – the legendary voice of Holy Moses – launched the project in the 90s and dropped the album “Absurd” like a small crater in the underground scene. Now the band is back. And when a reunion like that lands on the Wacken field, you know things are about to get loud.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Temple Of The Absurd ist so ein Name, bei dem alte Thrash-Fans sofort anfangen zu grinsen. Das Projekt von Sabina Classen – vielen als Stimme von Holy Moses bekannt – tauchte in den 90ern im deutschen Underground auf und hinterließ mit „Absurd“ einen ordentlichen Krater. Jetzt kehrt die Band zurück. Und wenn so eine Reunion auf dem Wacken-Acker passiert, weiß man: Es wird laut.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/temple-of-the-absurd/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"temple_of_the_absurd_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/temple_of_the_absurd_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36410}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4643,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/sabina_holy_moses/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0nUPTibxuWvP3nGFOyDOQl",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/f/a/csm_temple_of_the_absurd_26_ad20ecb9ce.jpg",uid:1677},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Frankreich",shortNameDe:"Frankreich",shortNameEn:"France",uid:72}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Ten56.",uid:1149}],end:"1785494700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785492000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2720}],pathSegment:"ten56",title:"Ten56.",uid:1149},biography:"<p>Who said the new generation can’t be saved<u>? Ten56 is</u> the proof that metal is still in very good hands. Founded in 2021 by former Betraying The Martyrs vocalist Aaron Matts, this metalcore band combines modern deathcore elements with a dark industrial sound. With everything that comes with it: brutal breakdowns and emotional lyrics. Ten56 is part of a new generation breaking genre boundaries and setting new ideals with a heavy yet atmospheric sound. Despite their short existence, the band already has a loyal fanbase, which is why we’re happy to clear the stage for Ten56 at Wacken 2026.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wer sagt die neue Generation sei nicht zu retten? Ten56 ist der Beweis dafür, dass zumindest Metal immer noch in sehr guten Händen ist. Die im Jahr 2021 von Ex-Betraying The Martyrs Sänger Aaron Matts gegründete Metalcore Formation kombiniert moderne Deathcore Elemente mit düsteren Industrial Sound. Mit allem, was dazu gehört: Brachiale Breakdowns und emotionale Lyrics. Ten56 ist Teil einer neuen Generation die Genregrenzen sprengen und mit hartem sowie atmosphärischem Sound neue Ideale setzten. Trotz des kurzen Bestehens der Band, zieht sie schon eine treue Fanbase mit sich mit, weswegen wir Bühne frei machen für Ten56 auf dem Wacken 2026.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/ten56/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHSO-EA-qfxAbV8jQiSfH4w",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Ten56-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Ten56-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34823}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4291,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/ten56hq/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4292,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ten56hq/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"28dpy0DQotTkBXcTlniQii",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/b/csm_Ten56-WOA26_515bdac59e.jpg",uid:1567},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Butcher Sisters",uid:992}],end:"1754092800",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754096400",start:"1754028000",title:"Friday",uid:26},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1754089200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2350},{artists:[{title:"The Butcher Sisters",uid:992}],end:"1785344400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785340800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2600}],pathSegment:"the-butcher-sisters",title:"The Butcher Sisters",uid:992},biography:`<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Butcher Sisters</strong>&nbsp;return to Wacken 2026—officially invited,&nbsp;<i>unofficially monitored</i>&nbsp;ever since their&nbsp;<strong>Abriss 25 anthem</strong>accidentally triggered seismic activity, tipped over three beer stands, and sent a portable toilet on a 12-meter journey of self-discovery.</p>\r
<p>For 2026 they promise only this:<br />&nbsp;<strong>More destruction. More noise. Zero remorse.</strong><br /><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Rumor has it their new anthem already annihilated two amps, one power box, and the patience of a sound engineer during testing.</p>\r
<p>Wacken better brace itself—the&nbsp;<strong>Butcher Sisters</strong>&nbsp;are back, ready to make Abriss 25 look like a peaceful Sunday brunch.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Die&nbsp;Butcher Sisters&nbsp;kommen 2026 nach Wacken zurück – offiziell eingeladen,&nbsp;<i>inoffiziell unter Beobachtung</i>, seit sie mit der&nbsp;Abriss-25-Hymne&nbsp;damals halb Schleswig-Holstein in Schwingung versetzt haben. Drei Bierstände kippten, ein Dixiklo wanderte 12 Meter, und ein Moshpit wurde später vom Geologie-Institut als „lokaler Erdrutsch“ eingestuft.</p>\r
<p>Für 2026 versprechen sie:<br />&nbsp;Noch mehr Abriss. Noch mehr Lärm. Noch weniger Rücksicht.<br />&nbsp;Gerüchte sagen, die neue Hymne sei so heftig, dass sie bereits in der Testphase zwei Verstärker, einen Stromkasten und die Geduld eines Toningenieurs zerstört hat.</p>\r
<p>Wacken kann sich also warm anziehen – die&nbsp;Butcher Sisters&nbsp;kommen zurück, um den Abriss 25 wie ein gemütliches Kaffeekränzchen aussehen zu lassen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-butcher-sisters/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4y_YlW6ezA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"the_butcher_sisters26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/the_butcher_sisters26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35815}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4521,uri:"https://thebutchersisters.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4522,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thebutchersisters/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4523,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thebutchersisters"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6j8vGWE3wKAFEn0ngreusM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/a/csm_the_butcher_sisters26_63acf7d891.jpg",uid:1636},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Österreich",shortNameDe:"Österreich",shortNameEn:"Austria",uid:13}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Crescent's Call",uid:1240}],end:"1785328800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785327600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Austria",uid:2613}],pathSegment:"the-crescents-call",title:"The Crescent's Call",uid:1240},biography:`<p class="text-justify">The Crescent's Call is a symphonic folk metal project from Austria. The band's name was inspired by the call of an inner voice that brought founder Christina back to her musical home after a long absence from the metal scene.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Their 2022 concept album THE CALL tells the story of Cairistiona, who, after severe emotional trauma, finds her true calling to save her world. Irish folk melodies (violins, cello) paint her village and people; symphonic, mystical layers carry her dramatic journey; the typical metal lineup drives the tempo with death metal accents underlining the brutality, while the alternation between clean and scream vocals first voices her inner conflict — then her transformation into a demonic figure who restores the balance of power.</p>\r
<p>For fans of Eluveitie, Within Temptation, Amaranthe, and System of a Down</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">The Crescent's Call ist ein Symphonic-Folk-Metal-Projekt aus Österreich. Der Bandname entstand aus dem Ruf einer inneren Stimme, die Gründerin Christina nach langer Distanz zurück in ihre musikalische Heimat – die Metal-Szene – führte.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Ihr Konzeptalbum THE CALL (2022) erzählt die Geschichte von Cairistiona, die nach einem schweren emotionalen Trauma ihre wahre Bestimmung findet, ihre Welt zu retten. Irische Folk-Melodien (Violinen, Cello) zeichnen ihr Dorf und ihr Volk; symphonische, mystische Klangschichten tragen ihre dramatische Reise; das klassische Metal-Line-up gibt das Tempo vor, Death-Metal-Akzente unterstreichen die Brutalität, und der Wechsel zwischen Cleangesang und Screams gibt zunächst ihrem inneren Konflikt eine Stimme – und schließlich ihrer Verwandlung in eine dämonische Gestalt, die das Gleichgewicht der Mächte wiederherstellt.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Für Fans von Eluveitie, Within Temptation, Amaranthe und System of a Down.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-crescents-call/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k1FWi2PgPFI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"The_Crescents_Call._26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/The_Crescents_Call._26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36971}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4739,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thecrescentscall"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4740,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thecrescentscall"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3RYGzF0y3W9cUuuwO4GWjI",subtitle:"Metal Battle Austria",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/a/csm_The_Crescents_Call._26_ec89342cc5.jpg",uid:1716},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Niederlande",shortNameDe:"Niederlande",shortNameEn:"Netherlands",uid:157}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Gathering",uid:1150}],end:"1785348000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785343500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2607}],pathSegment:"the-gathering",title:"The Gathering",uid:1150},biography:"<p>Are you looking for hypnosis? Even this can be found on the Holy Ground, delivered by <strong>The Gathering</strong>. They started as a Doom and Death Metal act but eventually shifted their focus to atmospheric and progressive Rock, especially through Anneke van Giersbergen. Her heartfelt vocals left a lasting mark on the band’s style. They are considered a pioneering band in their genre and one of the first to prominently integrate female vocals into Metal. To continue celebrating the 30th anniversary of Mandylion, the original line-up of The Gathering featuring Anneke van Giersbergen will perform an exclusive show in Germany at Wacken Open Air 2026!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ihr seid auf der Suche nach einer Hypnose? Auch das geht auf dem Holy Ground und The Gathering sorgen dafür. Die Anfänge der Band lagen im Doom und Death-Metal, danach verlegte die Band ihre Heimat schließlich in den Atmospheric und Progressive Rock, vor allem durch den Einfluss von Anneke van Giersbergen. Ihr gefühlvoller Gesang prägte die Band nachhaltig. Sie gelten als stilprägende Band und waren unter den Ersten, die weiblichen Gesang prominent im Metal integrierten. Zur Feier des 30-jährigen Jubiläums von Mandylion wird die Originalbesetzung von The Gathering mit Anneke van Giersbergen eine exklusive Show in Deutschland spielen – beim Wacken Open Air 2026!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-gathering/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/user/TheGatheringband",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"The_Gathering-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/The_Gathering-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34824}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4293,uri:"https://gathering.nl/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4294,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thegatheringofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4295,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thegatheringband/?igshid%201do2dc4ht1cbl"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2kO6zjt4a1OIqxOERhliEX",subtitle:"Exclusive Show in Germany in 2026",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/2/csm_The_Gathering-WOA26_57ded7843d.jpg",uid:1568},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Ukraine",shortNameDe:"Ukraine",shortNameEn:"Ukraine",uid:217}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Hardkiss",uid:1076}],end:"1753898400",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2816",subtitle:"powered by Church of Wacken",title:"Metal Church",uid:12},start:"1753894800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2190},{artists:[{title:"The Hardkiss",uid:1076}],end:"1785340800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785337200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2606}],pathSegment:"the-hardkiss",title:"The Hardkiss",uid:1076},biography:"<p>This Ukrainian formation is like an audiovisual explosion in high definition. Since 2011, The Hardkiss have mixed anthemic rock hymns with electronic soundstorms and a stage presence that would even make Muse twitch nervously. Lead singer Julia Sanina is not only powerful in voice but also a visual work of art. They combine dark glam with stadium-ready appeal – a must for fans of Nightwish!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Diese ukrainische Formation ist wie eine audiovisuelle Explosion in High Definition. Seit 2011 mixt The Hardkiss hymnische Rock-Hymnen mit elektronischen Klanggewitter und einer Bühnenpräsenz, bei der selbst Muse nervös zucken würden. Sängerin Julia Sanina ist dabei nicht nur stimmgewaltig, sondern auch visuell ein Gesamtkunstwerk. Sie verbinden düsteren Glam mit Stadiontauglichkeit – für Fans von Nightwish ein Muss!&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-hardkiss/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/thehardkiss",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"The_Hardkiss-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/The_Hardkiss-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34857}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4310,uri:"https://www.thehardkiss.com/en"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4311,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/THEHARDKISS/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4312,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/the_hardkiss"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4IJcztNtY5L7G3qK4yu1qt",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/8/csm_The_Hardkiss-WOA26_2db7165b54.jpg",uid:1574},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Haunted",uid:1151}],end:"1785533400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785529800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2725}],pathSegment:"the-haunted",title:"The Haunted",uid:1151},biography:"<p>The Haunted are rage with structure, noise with purpose.<br />They forged their own monster from the bones of <i>At the Gates</i>.<br /><i>“Strength in Numbers”</i> is the blueprint – fast, focused, unforgiving.<br />Their songs hit like storms that demolish with method.<br />No poses, no pauses – only pressure.&nbsp;And when it’s over, you beg for more.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>The Haunted sind Wut mit Struktur, Lärm mit Absicht.<br />&nbsp;Sie haben aus dem Erbe von <i>At the Gates</i> ihr eigenes Monster gebaut.<br />&nbsp;<i>“Strength in Numbers”</i> ist die Blaupause: schnell, präzise, unerbittlich.<br />&nbsp;Ihre Songs sind wie Stürme, die Häuser mit System abtragen.<br />&nbsp;Keine Posen, keine Pausen – nur Druck.&nbsp;Und wenn es vorbei ist, willst du sofort wieder rein.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-haunted/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCu0VWKjVjtxVIUPUhJf3_3g",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"The_Haunted-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/The_Haunted-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34825}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4296,uri:"https://thehaunted.shop/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4297,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/officialthehaunted/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4298,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thehauntedrocks/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2WLmgv66Uq4vt2i36vwkAq",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/3/csm_The_Haunted-WOA26_849d3b2a7e.jpg",uid:1569},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Hebridean Sheep",uid:1259}],end:"1785513600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785511800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2820}],pathSegment:"the-hebridean-sheep",title:"The Hebridean Sheep",uid:1259},biography:"<p>Whoever claims you need six strings and a wall of Marshall amps for legitimate metal clearly underestimated The Hebridean Sheep. Armed with absolutely nothing but bass, drums, and an outrageous amount of fuzz, this German duo builds a massive, crushing wall of sound at the Landgasthof that packs a serious punch. Their unique bastard child of Groove Metal and Punk Rock is brutal, hypnotic, and catchy as hell. The duo completely discards boring gimmicks or a forced image - here, it’s all about pure, raw craftsmanship. Rumor has it their show is “highly entertaining.” The band itself says they’re actually just trying to entertain themselves. Fair enough - if the result is this much of a demolition derby, we in the audience are more than happy to watch!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Wer behauptet, man bräuchte sechs Saiten und eine Wand aus Marshall-Verstärkern für amtlichen Metal, hat die Rechnung ohne The Hebridean Sheep gemacht. Bewaffnet mit absolut nichts außer Bass, Schlagzeug und einer unverschämten Portion Fuzz, zimmert dieses deutsche Zweier-Gespann eine massive, tonnenschwere Soundwand in den Landgasthof, die sich gewaschen hat. Ihr ureigener Bastard aus Groove Metal und Punk Rock ist brutal, hypnotisch und verdammt eingängig. Auf langweilige Gimmicks oder ein mühsam konstruiertes Image pfeift das Duo komplett - hier zählt nur das pure, rohe Handwerk. Böse Zungen behaupten, die Show sei “hochgradig unterhaltsam“. Die Band selbst sagt dazu, dass sie eigentlich nur versucht, sich selbst zu unterhalten. Fair enough - wenn das Ergebnis ein derartiger Abriss ist, gucken wir im Publikum gerne dabei zu!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-hebridean-sheep/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0YMrCvL_sFk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"the_hebridean_sheep_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/the_hebridean_sheep_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37078}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4796,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/the_hebridean_sheep/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4797,uri:"https://www.thehebrideansheep.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4798,uri:"https://thehebrideansheep.bandcamp.com/album/the-hebridean-sheep"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/5/c/csm_the_hebridean_sheep_26_4fee167442.jpg",uid:1739},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Limit",uid:1213}],end:"1785628800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785625200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2774},{artists:[{title:"The Limit",uid:1213}],end:"1785524400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785520800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2821}],pathSegment:"the-limit",title:"The Limit",uid:1213},biography:`<p>What&nbsp;happens&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;throw&nbsp;Pentagram, The Testors and The Stooges into a sonic&nbsp;blender, add a splash&nbsp;of&nbsp;whiskey and shake&nbsp;well?</p>\r
<p>Exactly: The Limit.</p>\r
<p>With legends like Bobby Liebling, Sonny Vincent and Jimmy Recca, this&nbsp;supergroup&nbsp;pushes&nbsp;the legend-meter to&nbsp;the maximum. Punk meets&nbsp;Doom — and our pitch-black&nbsp;hearts&nbsp;beat&nbsp;even&nbsp;harder.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Was glaubt ihr, würde dabei rauskommen, wenn man Pentagram, die Testors und Stooges zusammen in einen akustischen Cocktail-Mixer packt, ein Schlückchen (das können wir hier nur betonen!) Whiskey dazugibt und dann gut schüttelt? Richtig: The Limit. Die superste aller Super Groups fährt mit Bobby Liebling, Sonny Vincent und Jimmy Recca den Legenden-Spiegel in schwindelerregende Höhen. Und auch musikalisch macht dem US amerikanischen Fünfer niemand etwas vor. Punk und Doom geben sich die Klinke in die Hand und lassen unsere pechschwarzen Herzen tiefer aber nicht weniger intensiv schlagen! Ob Vorfreude wohl ansteckend ist?</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-limit/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBfQXrPBxOI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"the_limit_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/the_limit_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36393}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4644,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/TheLimitRock/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/6/csm_the_limit_26_954965f6df.jpg",uid:1678},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Other",uid:304}],end:"1659806100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1659803400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:705},{artists:[{title:"The Other",uid:304}],end:"1785604500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785601800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2786}],pathSegment:"the-other",title:"The Other",uid:304},biography:"<p>Punks, rockers, goths and metalheads take note, it's horror alert! Because THE OTHER are coming to haunt the Holy Ground! Just as the band released their new studio album ‘Alienated’ on 31 October 2025 fittingly for Halloween, they are back on time for the W:O:A in summer with their macabre show. Get ready for a set full of horror stories, top-notch entertainment and the usual tongue-in-cheek humour that gives Horror Punk its humorous flavour.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Punks, Rockers, Goths und Metalheads aufgepasst, es ist Gruselalarm!&nbsp;Denn THE OTHER suchen den den Acker heim! So wie die Band am 31.10.2025 passend zu Halloween ihr neues Studioalbum „Alienated“ veröffentlicht hat, ist sie pünktlich im Sommer zum W:O:A mit ihrer makabren Show am Start.&nbsp;Macht euch gefasst auf ein Set voller Schauergeschichten, bester Unterhaltung und dem üblichen Augenzwinkern, das dem Horrorpunk die humorvolle Würze verpasst.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-other/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AOSS3e2EljI",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"the_other_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/the_other_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36394}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4645,uri:"https://theother.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4646,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/theotherhorrorpunk"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4647,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/theotherhorrorpunk"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0a3Gua6g9TZBKlDSqebL7W",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/8/csm_the_other_26_bb6a90d46d.jpg",uid:1679},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Brasilien",shortNameDe:"Brasilien",shortNameEn:"Brazil",uid:29}],events:[{artists:[{title:"The Troops Of Doom",uid:1152}],end:"1785356100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785353400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2646}],pathSegment:"the-troops-of-doom",title:"The Troops Of Doom",uid:1152},biography:"<p>THE TROOPS OF DOOM have built up a remarkable reputation in the Brazilian Metal scene, and with good reason: former Sepultura guitarist Jairo ‘Tormentor’ Guedz and his bandmates have been producing new material almost every year since 2020 and are touring tirelessly around the world. It's time to welcome the quartet to Wacken to expand Wasted Wednesday with a loud Death Metal show.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>THE TROOPS OF DOOM haben sich nicht ohne Grund einen beachtlichen Ruf in der brasilianischen Metalszene erspielt: Der ehemalige Sepultura Gitarrist Jairo „Tormentor“ Guedz und seine Mitstreiter haben seit 2020 fast jährlich neues Material produziert und touren unermüdlich durch die Welt. Zeit, das Quartett in Wacken zu begrüßen, um den Wasted Wednesday erfolgreich um eine lautstarke Death-Metal-Show zu erweitern.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/the-troops-of-doom/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c27LxrSRsSk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"troops_of_doom26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/troops_of_doom26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36335}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4299,uri:"https://www.thetroopsofdoom.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4300,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thetroopsofdoom"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4301,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thetroopsofdoom"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1GCnpVka37q3EXMVnK9bma",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/6/6/csm_troops_of_doom26_13f1c1c107.jpg",uid:1570},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Therapy?",uid:293}],end:"1659704400",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1659700800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:604},{artists:[{title:"Therapy?",uid:293}],end:"1785421800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785418200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2656}],pathSegment:"therapy",title:"Therapy?",uid:293},biography:"<p>Therapy? Yes, Therapy! The Alternative Rock trio from Northern Ireland turly belongs to the scene and has built up a loyal fan base with 16 studio albums and numerous tours. After a 30th anniversary tour for their highlight album ‘Troublegum’, the band led by singer and guitarist Andy Cairns will once again take the world's stages by storm next year and lets the Punk loose. Whether ‘Screamager’, “Diane” or ‘Nowhere’ – get ready to shake your head!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Therapy? Ja, Therapy! Das Alternative Rock-Trio aus Nordirland gehört fest zur Szene und hat sich mit 16 Studioalben und zahlreichen Tourneen eine treue Fanbase erspielt. Nach einer 30 Jahre-Jubiläumstour zum Erfolgsalbum „Troublegum“, stürmt die Band um Sänger und Gitarrist Andy Cairns nächstes Jahr erneut die Bühnen der Welt und lässt den Punk von den Leinen. Ob „Screamager“, „Diane“ oder „Nowhere“ – die Matte wird geschüttelt!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/therapy/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nhJHs5UEV2Q",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"therapy26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/therapy26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35762}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4464,uri:"https://therapyquestionmark.co.uk"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4465,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Therapyofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4466,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/therapyofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4467,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7ZeIuKJwO4ORBeSBx60NGg"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3MomZRiJwdZmYnysgtF4Ey",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/5/csm_therapy26_acbd2ac94b.jpg",uid:1618},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[],pathSegment:"thomas-nicholas-band",title:"Thomas Nicholas Band",uid:1231},biography:`<p>When&nbsp;two&nbsp;icons&nbsp;of&nbsp;the 1990s collide, things&nbsp;are&nbsp;bound&nbsp;to&nbsp;become&nbsp;legendary!</p>\r
<p>While&nbsp;Metal&nbsp;history was being&nbsp;written in Northern Germany, Thomas Nicholas rose&nbsp;to&nbsp;fame&nbsp;through&nbsp;his&nbsp;role in the&nbsp;cult&nbsp;trilogy American Pie.</p>\r
<p>Even during&nbsp;the&nbsp;difficult 1990s, he always&nbsp;carried heavy music in his&nbsp;heart. With his own band, music&nbsp;always&nbsp;stood&nbsp;proudly&nbsp;beside&nbsp;his&nbsp;acting&nbsp;career.</p>\r
<p>And that’s&nbsp;exactly&nbsp;why&nbsp;we’re&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;him&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;stages&nbsp;of&nbsp;the Holy Ground now.</p>\r
<p>Between&nbsp;childhood&nbsp;memories, teenage&nbsp;crushes, and pure Heavy&nbsp;Metal — this&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;stuff&nbsp;legends&nbsp;are&nbsp;made&nbsp;of.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Wenn zwei Ikonen der 90er Jahre aufeinandertreffen, dann wird es zwangsläufig legendär! Während in Norddeutschland Metal Geschichte geschrieben wurde, erlangte Thomas Nicholas Berühmtheit durch seine Rollen in der Kult Trilogie American Pie!</p>\r
<p>Die harten Klänge hat er, auch in den schwierigen 1990er Jahren, immer im Herzen getragen. Mit seiner eigenen Band stand diese immer auch gleichberechtigt neben der Schauspielerei. Deswegen hieven wir ihn jetzt auf unsere Bühnen auf den Holy Ground. Zwischen Kindheitserinnerungen, Jugend-Schwärmerei und Heavy Metal in Reinkultur – das ist der Stoff aus dem Legenden werden.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/thomas-nicholas-band/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zoFXmsbjKuY",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"thomas_nicholas_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/thomas_nicholas_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36697}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4715,uri:"https://www.tinicholas.com/music"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4716,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/TINband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4717,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/tinband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"553ygvIoh7oel0K4hrC1dC",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/6/csm_thomas_nicholas_26_d2983140b2.jpg",uid:1703},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Thrown",uid:1153}],end:"1785594600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785591000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2755}],pathSegment:"thrown",title:"Thrown",uid:1153},biography:"<p>Are you into brutal beatdowns, sweet melodies, and catchy riffs? Then the Stockholm band Thrown is just the right crew for you! With their mix of Nu-Metal, Hardcore, and Metalcore, the four-piece delivers an adrenaline rush that’s almost borderline legal! Having been in the game for over six years, the band knows better than most how to take the audience on a journey through a new dimension of brutal precision.&nbsp;We can’t wait.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ihr steht auf brutale Beatdowns, zuckersüße Melodien und mitreißende Riffs? Dann haben wir mit den Stockholmern Thrown genau die richtige Kapelle für euch!<br />Mit ihrer Mischung aus Nu-Metal, Hardcore und Metalcore sorgt der Vierer für Adrenalinausschüttung am Rande des Legalen!&nbsp;<br />Bereits mehr als sechs Jahre im Business versteht es die Band wie kaum eine andere das Publikum in eine neue Bandbreite der brutalen Präzision zu entführen. Wir können es kaum erwarten.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/thrown/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Thrown-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Thrown-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34827}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4302,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thrownband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4303,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thrownband"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4304,uri:"https://extendedpain.com/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5eBCPtU2iPbzuMRre9BePt",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/9/csm_Thrown-WOA26_f70cc40622.jpg",uid:1571},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Thundermother",uid:360}],end:"1659556800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659574800",start:"1659506400",title:"Wednesday",uid:1},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1659553200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Unplugged Show",uid:496},{artists:[{title:"Thundermother",uid:360}],end:"1659619800",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1659616200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:544},{artists:[{title:"Thundermother",uid:360}],end:"1659631500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1659628800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:823},{artists:[{title:"Thundermother",uid:360}],end:"1785334500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785330900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2605}],pathSegment:"thundermother",title:"Thundermother",uid:360},biography:"<p>Some bands don’t just play music that fits into a certain genre. Some bands live that spirit.<br />Thundermother from Sweden breathe, live, and create rock ’n’ roll. Honest, straightforward, and no frills. And just like in any marriage, sometimes things come to an end — Thundermother didn’t hesitate to make a clean break and start anew.<br />Now, with their new lineup for almost two years, the band once again knows how to quickly win over the audience.&nbsp;See for yourself!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Manche Bands spielen nicht nur Musik, die sich dann einem bestimmten Genre zuschreiben lässt. Manche Bands leben genau diesen Spirit.<br />Thundermother aus Schweden atmen, leben und kreieren Rock’n’Roll. Ehrlich schnörkellos direkt. Und da es in jeder Ehe auch mal zu Ende gehen kann haben auch Thundermother nicht davor zurückgeschreckt Tabularasa zu machen und neu zu beginnen.<br />Nun seit knapp 2 Jahren im neuen Lineup versteht es die Band auch wieder, die Zuschauer schnell um den Finger zu wickeln. Überzeugt euch selbst!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/thundermother/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyyyZ8cMvrLvEvfAraTnsFQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Thundermother-Band-2023.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Thundermother-Band-2023.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34845}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4347,uri:"https://www.thundermother.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4348,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thundermother/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4349,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thundermother/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"18jTFcgHRRYHdwdof1MDZw",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/a/csm_Thundermother-Band-2023_d61771d790.jpg",uid:1587},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Australien",shortNameDe:"Australien",shortNameEn:"Australia",uid:14}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Thy Art Is Murder",uid:22}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:146},{artists:[{title:"Thy Art Is Murder",uid:22}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:417},{artists:[{title:"Thy Art Is Murder",uid:22}],end:"1785613500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785609900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2758}],pathSegment:"thy-art-is-murder",title:"Thy Art Is Murder",uid:22},biography:`<p>“Extreme” gets thrown around a lot in Metal – but for Thy Art Is Murder, it’s the only fitting word.</p>\r
<p>Australia’s Deathcore flagship returns, tighter and heavier than ever.</p>\r
<p>With new frontman Tyler Miller leading the charge, their sound is a perfect storm of precision, fury, and groove.</p>\r
<p>Brace yourselves: the moshpit will not survive.</p>\r
<p>And whoever still thinks Aussies only do AC/DC – think again.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Extrem ist ein in unserem Heavy Metal Kosmos oft bemühtes Wort. Im Fall des australischen Aushängeschilds Thy Art Is Murder und deren musikalischen Schaffens trifft die Umschreibung aber den Nagel auf den Kopf. Der brutale Deathcore gepaart mit den Fähigkeiten des neuen Manns am Mikrofon, Tyler Miller, zimmern einen wohligen Unterstand im Sturm des tosenden Moshpits.</p>\r
<p>Und da soll nochmal einer sagen die Australier können nur AC/DC.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/thy-art-is-murder/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5rPbb0WCpOw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"thy_art_is_murder_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/thy_art_is_murder_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35138}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4418,uri:"https://www.thyartismurder.net"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4419,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/thyartismurder"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4420,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/thyartinstagram"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4421,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/c/thyartismurder"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3et9upNERQI5IYt5jEDTxM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/0/csm_thy_art_is_murder_26_9e88fcd95e.jpg",uid:1606},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Triptykon",uid:1154}],end:"1785621600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785617100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Exclusive Special Best Of Set With Several World Live Premiers",uid:2759}],pathSegment:"triptykon",title:"Triptykon",uid:1154},biography:"<p>Our legend meter is off the charts. Tom Warrior Fischer brings with Triptykon an absolute milestone of heavy metal to the already legendary Holy Ground.<br />And although Fischer’s fans have been waiting for new music since 2014 and the last album <i>Melana Chasmata</i>, you can be sure the Holy Ground won’t be big enough to fully capture this icon.<br />Starting out as one of the fathers of black and death metal, Fischer boasts an impressive range of sounds. This kind of legacy normally belongs in a museum! The formation is not just coming to the Holy Grand, they bring loads of surprises and specials for an unforgettable Wacken experience.&nbsp;</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Bei uns schlägt das Legenden-Barometer ohne Ende aus. Tom Warrior Fischer bringt mit Triptykon eine absolute Sternstunde des Heavy Metal auf den ohnehin schon an Legenden nicht armen Holy Ground.<br />Und obwohl Fischers Fans seit 2014 und dem letzten Album Melana Chasmate auf neuen Musik warten müssen, könnt ihr euch sicher sein, dass der Holy Ground nicht groß genug sein wird, um diese Ikone in ihrer Gänze zu erfassen.<br />Als einer der Väter von Black – und Death Metal gestartet hat Fischer eine beeindrucke Bandbreite an Sounds vorzuweisen.<br />So etwas gehört normalerweise in ein Museum! Die Formation kommt nicht auf den Holy Ground, sie haben einige Überraschung und Specials im Sack für ein unvergessliches Wacken Erlebnis.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/triptykon/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKXdXpeSwheXyt1WUINGPTg",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Triptykon-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Triptykon-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34828}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4305,uri:"https://www.triptykon.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4306,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/triptykonofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4307,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/triptykonofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"37fG1EQuwb6zBHyFYUGfj8",subtitle:"Exclusive Special Best Of Set With Several World Live Premiers",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/c/csm_Triptykon-WOA26_0599ad9698.jpg",uid:1572},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Dänemark",shortNameDe:"Dänemark",shortNameEn:"Denmark",uid:56}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Trold",uid:1214}],end:"1785507300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785504600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2730}],pathSegment:"trold",title:"Trold",uid:1214},biography:`<p>Where do trolls live?</p>\r
<p>Usually&nbsp;under&nbsp;bridges&nbsp;or in caves. But not Trold.</p>\r
<p>This summer&nbsp;the&nbsp;Danish&nbsp;tin-whistle-loving&nbsp;Metalheads&nbsp;are&nbsp;moving&nbsp;straight&nbsp;onto&nbsp;the Holy Ground. Armed&nbsp;with a sack full&nbsp;of explosive Folk, Pagan and Metal&nbsp;anthems — guaranteed&nbsp;to&nbsp;get&nbsp;your&nbsp;hair&nbsp;flying and your neck spinning.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Wisst ihr wo Trolle leben? Gemeinhin findet ihr sie unter Brücken oder in ihren Höhlen. Nicht aber unsere Freunde von Trold! Die dänischen Tin Whistle Verehrer leben diesen Sommer, zumindest übergangsweise, direkt bei uns auf dem Holy Ground. Mitbringen werden sie einen ganzen Sack voller Trold Hits und die habe es wirklich in sich. Wer bei dieser explosiven Mischung aus Pagan- Folk- und Metal-Elementen nicht irgendwann die Haare fliegen und den Nacken kreisen lässt, ist bei dieser Band dann wahrscheinlich sowieso falsch.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/trold/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eDXf4JCySfk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"trold_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/trold_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36395}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4648,uri:"https://www.troldband.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4649,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/troldband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4650,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/troldband"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/2/csm_trold_26_e2d88c204e.jpg",uid:1680},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Turbonegro",uid:1192}],end:"1785447000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785441600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2659}],pathSegment:"turbonegro",title:"Turbonegro",uid:1192},biography:`<p>Turbonegro roll back into Wacken 2026 like they own the damn place –</p>\r
<p>no flowers, no friendly waves, just a truckload of noise and denim heavy enough to bend the earth’s crust.</p>\r
<p>Last time they showed up, half the crowd left with ringing ears and the other half with an identity crisis. Nobody’s sure if it was a concert or a controlled demolition with better lighting.</p>\r
<p>This year?</p>\r
<p>They’re coming in meaner, louder, and about three showers past respectable.</p>\r
<p>Word on the street: their rehearsal volume got so out of hand the speakers tried to file complaints, and the crew considered quitting music altogether to pursue quieter careers like chainsaw testing.</p>\r
<p>Turbonegro at Wacken 2026:</p>\r
<p>No polish. No mercy. Just filthy Rock ’n’ Roll punching you right in the jaw.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>2026 marschieren Turbonegro wieder in Wacken ein – nicht, um nett zu spielen, sondern um das Gelände daran zu erinnern, wie sich echte Bühnenpräsenz anhört, wenn man sie mit einem Presslufthammer verwechselt.</p>\r
\r
<p>Ihr letzter Besuch hinterließ einen Feldbericht, der ungefähr so klang wie eine Mischung aus Katastrophenprotokoll und Liebesbrief: zu viel Lärm, zu viel Denim, zu viel Haltung – also genau richtig.</p>\r
\r
<p>Dieses Jahr haben sie angeblich beschlossen, noch ungepflegter aufzutreten, rein aus Prinzip. Die neue Live-Show soll so kompromisslos sein, dass selbst die Lautsprecher versuchten, Gewerkschaftsschutz anzumelden.</p>\r
\r
<p>Turbonegro 2026:</p>\r
<p>keine Schönfärberei, kein Kuschelkurs, nur ehrlicher Krawall – und zwar der Sorte, die man nicht vergisst, sondern noch Wochen später aus den Kleidern klopft.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/turbonegro/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzBNLvElCyk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"turbonegro26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/turbonegro26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35816}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4524,uri:"https://turbonegro.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4525,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/TurbonegroHQ/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4526,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMr0kxESaMbrpRuqB4_YwRQ"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"191rVxQbbZ05wcICUSvLkz",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/b/csm_turbonegro26_2118d824cd.jpg",uid:1637},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Österreich",shortNameDe:"Österreich",shortNameEn:"Austria",uid:13}],events:[{artists:[{title:"tuXedoo",uid:173}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2624",subtitle:"",title:"Beergarden Stage",uid:9},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:49},{artists:[{title:"tuXedoo",uid:173}],end:"1785494700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785492000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2727}],pathSegment:"tuxedoo",title:"tuXedoo",uid:173},biography:"<p>Thunderous&nbsp;riffs, furious&nbsp;drums and a certain&nbsp;aura&nbsp;of&nbsp;menace — not exactly&nbsp;the&nbsp;sound&nbsp;you&nbsp;expected&nbsp;from&nbsp;the Alps? Tuxedoo&nbsp;are&nbsp;here&nbsp;to&nbsp;prove&nbsp;you&nbsp;wrong. Their brutal mix of&nbsp;Thrash and Nu Metal&nbsp;might&nbsp;place&nbsp;them&nbsp;somewhere&nbsp;between&nbsp;the Bay Area and New York in your mind. In reality, the&nbsp;five-piece comes&nbsp;straight out of&nbsp;peaceful&nbsp;Tyrol. In eight&nbsp;years&nbsp;they’ve&nbsp;already&nbsp;released&nbsp;two EPs and four&nbsp;albums, so everything&nbsp;is&nbsp;set&nbsp;for a proper musical&nbsp;beating. Time to&nbsp;shake&nbsp;those&nbsp;lederhosen&nbsp;loose, Metalheads.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Donnernde Riffs, wütende Drums und eine gewisse Aura der Bedrohung – so habt ihr euch den Sound der Alpen gar nicht vorgestellt? Tuxedoo belehren euch eines Besseren. Der brutale Mix aus Thrash mit Elementen des Nu Metal lässt die fünf Österreicher musikalisch eher in der Bay Area oder New York verorten. Tatsächlich stammen die Buam aber aus dem beschaulichen Tirol und können in ihrer 8 jährigen Schaffenszeit 2 EPs und 4 Alben vorweisen. Es ist also alles angerichtet sich mal ordentlich die Lederhosen ausziehen zu lassen, liebe Metalheads.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/tuxedoo/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HYHN7f9knBA",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"tuxedoo_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/tuxedoo_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36396}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4651,uri:"https://tuxedoo.at"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4652,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/tuxedoometal/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4653,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/tuxedoo_alpencore/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"44irRUOhAfb0ochWsW4sG1",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/b/csm_tuxedoo_26_2cbaa64988.jpg",uid:1681},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Uli Jon Roth",uid:208}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2816",subtitle:"powered by Church of Wacken",title:"Metal Church",uid:12},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1},{artists:[{title:"Uli Jon Roth",uid:208}],end:"1722711600",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722740400",start:"1722664800",title:"Saturday",uid:22},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1722708000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1596},{artists:[{title:"Uli Jon Roth",uid:208}],end:"1785424500",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785420900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:'"50th Anniversary Virgin Killer" Show',uid:2651}],pathSegment:"uli-jon-roth",title:"Uli Jon Roth",uid:208},biography:`<p>The story begins on the&nbsp;<strong>Full Metal Cruise</strong>, drifting between sea and sky, when Uli Jon Roth crossed paths with&nbsp;<strong>Kreator</strong>.</p>\r
<p>Uli, ever the cosmic wanderer, did not know them at first.<br />&nbsp;But they knew him instantly — the string-sorcerer whose sound had shaped their earliest steps into metal.</p>\r
<p>What followed felt less like a conversation and more like an alignment of forces.<br />&nbsp;Within minutes, the idea revealed itself, clear and inevitable:</p>\r
<p><strong>Join together. Return to Wacken. Celebrate the 50th anniversary of&nbsp;</strong><i><strong>Virgin Killer</strong></i><strong>&nbsp;— as one.</strong></p>\r
<p>Thrash meets transcendence. Ferocity meets philosophy. A moment only Wacken can hold.</p>\r
<p>And as the plan settled into place on that ship, everyone present said the same thing:</p>\r
<p><strong>“That’s it. That’s the peak."</strong></p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Die Legende beginnt auf der Full Metal Cruise:</p>\r
<p>Uli Jon Roth, Gitarrenalchemist und ewiger Zeitreisender im Dienst der hohen Kunst, schlendert über das Schiff – und trifft auf Kreator.</p>\r
<p>Uli kennt sie nicht. Kreator kennt ihn sehr wohl.</p>\r
<p>Große Fans, seit Jahren. Das klassische „Wir sind mit deiner Musik aufgewachsen“-Level.</p>\r
<p>Der Rest ist reiner Metal-Instinkt: Man redet, man lacht, man merkt:</p>\r
<p>Da muss was Gemeinsames passieren.</p>\r
<p>Und weil Understatement nie Ulis stärkste Disziplin war, fiel die Wahl nicht etwa auf einen Jam oder eine Session backstage —</p>\r
<p>nein, man beschließt:</p>\r
<p>Wir feiern gemeinsam in WACKEN den 50. Geburtstag von Virgin Killer.</p>\r
<p>Wie sonst?</p>\r
<p>So entsteht eine seltene Allianz: Mille und Fredos die Meister des Thrash,</p>\r
<p>und Uli Jon Roth, der Mann, dessen Gitarrenton selbst Stürme höflich bittet, ruhiger zu sein.</p>\r
<p>Wacken 2026 bekommt damit kein normales Jubiläum, sondern ein Ereignis, das nur schwer zu toppen ist.</p>\r
<p>Oder wie man auf der Cruise hörte, nachdem der Plan stand:</p>\r
\r
<p>„Mehr geht nicht.“</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/uli-jon-roth/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://youtu.be/Rw4QqMF6fcU",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"uli_jon_roth26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/uli_jon_roth26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35817}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4527,uri:"https://www.ulijonroth.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4528,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Uli-Jon-Roth-26843841074/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4529,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/ulijonroth/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2VoP4JXyxNPIoYAFdB5ssQ",subtitle:'50th Anniversary of "Virgin Killer" Show feat. Special Guests',thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/3/b/csm_uli_jon_roth26_db0812a7ce.jpg",uid:1638},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Unzucht",uid:643}],end:"1691077500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691110800",start:"1691042400",title:"Thursday",uid:14},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1691073900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:971},{artists:[{title:"Unzucht",uid:643}],end:"1691093700",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1691110800",start:"1691042400",title:"Thursday",uid:14},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1691091000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1366},{artists:[{title:"Unzucht",uid:643}],end:"1785359700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785356100",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2640}],pathSegment:"unzucht",title:"Unzucht",uid:643},biography:"<p>They bring their musical darkness to the field with ‘Neon Dom’! Four years after their best-of album, UNZUCHT are starting a new chapter and release their first LP with frontman Timm Hindorff. The new songs exude courage, tell of the struggle with inner demons, and yet know that every darkness is followed by light. Immerse yourself in a world of debauchery and desire... you won't regret it.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie bringen ihre musikalische Finsternis mit „Neon Dom“ auf den Acker! Vier Jahre nach ihrem Best Of-Album schlagen UNZUCHT ein neues Kapitel auf und veröffentlichen den ersten Longplayer mit Frontmann Timm Hindorff. Die neuen Songs atmen Mut, zeugen vom Kampf mit inneren Dämonen und wissen dennoch, dass auf jede Dunkelheit ein Licht folgt. Taucht ein in die Welt voller Unzucht und Verlangen…ihr werdet es nicht bereuen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/unzucht/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zEOoc9cua0c",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"unzucht_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/unzucht_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36397}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4654,uri:"https://www.unzucht-music.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4655,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Unzucht/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4656,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/unzucht_official"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2hfInImCCmb7zXIuCE15IN",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/b/2/csm_unzucht_26_5662cb7925.jpg",uid:1682},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Dänemark",shortNameDe:"Dänemark",shortNameEn:"Denmark",uid:56}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Vanir",uid:1174}],end:"1785346200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785342600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2638}],pathSegment:"vanir",title:"Vanir",uid:1174},biography:`<p>Vanir extend their hand and invite you straight to Valhalla.</p>\r
<p>The six Danes weave Norse mythology and Viking spirit into blackened Death Metal epics that set the perfect scene – cold, majestic, and full of heart.</p>\r
<p>Their music burns with the fire of ancient tales and the power of the northern winds.</p>\r
<p>Raise your horns high and join them on the path to glory.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Vanir strecken ihren Arm aus und reichen uns ihre Hand, um uns mit nach Valhalla zu nehmen. Die sechs Dänen, die es sich zur Aufgabe gemacht haben nordische Mythologie und Lebensart zu vertonen, verpacken ihre Erzählungen in ein Black- und Death Metal Gewand, das nicht nur eine beeindruckend passende Szenerie kreiert, sondern auch noch die Herzen der Metalheads erwärmt.&nbsp;</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/vanir/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DyTt4-wguj0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"vanir_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/vanir_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35141}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4422,uri:"https://vanir.dk"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4423,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Vanirband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4424,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/vanirdenmark/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6DCYYeX3Iqic6GnQTXM3n4",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/f/csm_vanir_26_4989af5ab2.jpg",uid:1607},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Velvet Rush",uid:1215}],end:"1785351600",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785348900",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2619}],pathSegment:"velvet-rush",title:"Velvet Rush",uid:1215},biography:"<p>Velvet Rush deliver rock ’n’ roll the direct way: loud riffs, big hooks and enough energy to kick the dust off the festival ground. The kind of band where you suddenly realize you’re already singing along and tapping your foot.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Velvet Rush bringen Rock’n’Roll ohne Umwege. Treibende Riffs, große Melodien und genug Energie, um den Staub vom Festivalboden zu pusten. Das ist die Sorte Band, bei der man plötzlich merkt, dass man schon wieder mitsingt und der Fuß längst mitwippt.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/velvet-rush/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WZCaI5p_ylw",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"velvet_rush_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/velvet_rush_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36398}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4657,uri:"https://www.velvetrush.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4658,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Velvet.Rushband/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4659,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/velvet.rush_/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2MorUzc2WoEC4CA8VKjRuK",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/c/c/csm_velvet_rush_26_79ee43e0e7.jpg",uid:1683},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameDe:"Vereinigte Staaten von Amerika",shortNameEn:"United States",uid:220}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Vended",uid:439}],end:"1659779100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659834000",start:"1659765600",title:"Saturday",uid:10},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1659776400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:681},{artists:[{title:"Vended",uid:439}],end:"1785619800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1408",subtitle:"",title:"Headbangers Stage",uid:7},start:"1785616200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2773}],pathSegment:"vended",title:"Vended",uid:439},biography:`<p>Brutal sounds, an even more brutal voice, Des Moines, Iowa – and a not-so-small dose of shock factor. You’re thinking of S…?! Nope. We’re talking about Vended.</p>\r
<p>Anyone who witnessed their last appearance at Wacken Open Air knows exactly what’s coming our way this summer – and everyone else better brace themselves. Whatever they’ve got in the water over in Iowa, we’ll have some of that too.</p>\r
<p>P.S. Rumor has it that blood really is thicker than water: Fronted by the sons of Slipknot legends Corey Taylor and Shawn “Clown” Crahan, this band carries the family legacy with a vengeance — but with their own raw, untamed edge.</p>\r
<p>.</p>\r
<p>An absolute must-see at Wacken 2026.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Brutale Sounds, eine noch brutalere Stimme, Des Moines, Iowa – und ein nicht zu unterschätzender Schockfaktor. Du denkst an S…?! Falsch gedacht. Die Rede ist von Vended.</p>\r
<p>Wer ihren letzten Auftritt beim Wacken Open Air erlebt hat, weiß ganz genau, was uns in diesem Sommer erwartet – und alle anderen sollten sich besser festhalten. Was auch immer die da drüben in Iowa im Wasser haben, wir nehmen davon auch eine Runde.</p>\r
<p>P.S. Man munkelt ja, Blut sei tatsächlich dicker als Wasser: Angeführt von den Söhnen der Slipknot-Legenden Corey Taylor und Shawn “Clown” Crahan trägt diese Band das Familienerbe mit Wucht weiter – aber mit ihrem ganz eigenen, rohen und ungezähmten Sound.Ein absoluter Pflichttermin auf dem Acker!</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/vended/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQP9akf_Pkk",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"vended_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/vended_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35142}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4425,uri:"https://www.officialvended.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4426,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/vendedofficial"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4427,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/vended_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4428,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@vended"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"17pZeX1Vy9hugVufmKFbCQ",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/7/csm_vended_26_a96222e9bb.jpg",uid:1608},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Österreich",shortNameDe:"Österreich",shortNameEn:"Austria",uid:13}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Visions of Atlantis",uid:305}],end:"1659641400",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659661200",start:"1659592800",title:"Thursday",uid:8},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1659637800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:580},{artists:[{title:"Visions of Atlantis",uid:305}],end:"1659707100",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1659747600",start:"1659679200",title:"Friday",uid:9},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3584",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet I",uid:19},start:"1659704400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:834},{artists:[{title:"Visions of Atlantis",uid:305}],end:"1785328200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1024",subtitle:"",title:"Louder",uid:6},start:"1785324600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2604}],pathSegment:"visions-of-atlantis",title:"Visions of Atlantis",uid:305},biography:`<p>Help — the&nbsp;pirates&nbsp;are&nbsp;coming and they’re&nbsp;setting&nbsp;course&nbsp;for&nbsp;the Holy Ground!</p>\r
<p>Luckily, they’re&nbsp;our&nbsp;pirates: Visions&nbsp;of Atlantis. After their extensive tour with&nbsp;Warkings, they’re&nbsp;making a stop in Wacken. Led by&nbsp;pirate&nbsp;queen Clémentine Delauney and captain Michele Guaitoli, the&nbsp;crew&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;their&nbsp;epic&nbsp;symphonic&nbsp;pirate&nbsp;tales&nbsp;to&nbsp;stages&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;since&nbsp;the&nbsp;start&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;millennium. Boarding parties&nbsp;welcome — we’re&nbsp;ready.</p>`,biographyDe:"<p>Hilfe die Piraten sind los und nehmen Kurs zum Entern des Holy Grounds! Glücklicherweise sind es unsere Piraten, Visions&nbsp;of Atlantis, die nach ihrer ausgiebigen Tour mit Warkings noch ein Stelldichein in Wacken geben. Die Mannschaft um Piratenkönigin Clementine Delauney und Oberpirat Michele Guaitoli versetzen seit Beginn des Millenniums die Bühnen dieser Welt in freudige Schrecken, wenn sie ihre symphonischen und mitreißenden Piraten-Epen auf die Bretter bringen. Entert ruhig, wir sind bereit.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/visions-of-atlantis/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g1HKsJAxIx8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"visions_of_atlantis_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/visions_of_atlantis_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36399}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4660,uri:"https://www.visionsofatlantis.at"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4661,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/visionsofatlantisofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4662,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/visionsofatlantis/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"5kanN1nKzrkW1m2gZmo82x",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/6/csm_visions_of_atlantis_26_2bfe817394.jpg",uid:1684},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Vogelfrey",uid:79}],end:"0",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1564624800",start:"1564560000",title:"Mittwoch",uid:2},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"0",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:40},{artists:[{title:"Vogelfrey",uid:79}],end:"1722434400",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722474000",start:"1722405600",title:"Wednesday",uid:19},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722430800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1513},{artists:[{title:"Vogelfrey",uid:79}],end:"1722451500",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722474000",start:"1722405600",title:"Wednesday",uid:19},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Meet & Greet",uid:9},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"3840",subtitle:"",title:"Meet & Greet II",uid:20},start:"1722448800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:1890},{artists:[{title:"Vogelfrey",uid:79}],end:"1785420000",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785416400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2682}],pathSegment:"vogelfrey",title:"Vogelfrey",uid:79},biography:"<p>They have a clear mission: Make Mittelalter Great Again! What some consider a dark age has been a colourful playground and source of inspiration for Folk Metal institution VOGELFREY for over 20 years. The Hamburg-based band not only looks back, but also ventures into the present – with topical themes, social criticism and yet with the usual dash of humour and irony. Dance around, raise your mead horns and warm up your voices.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie haben eine klare Mission: Make Mittelalter Great Again! Was für die einen ein finsteres Zeitalter darstellt, ist für die Folk-Metal-Institution VOGELFREY eine bunte Spielwiese und Inspiration seit über 20 Jahren. Dabei blicken die Hamburger nicht nur zurück, sondern wagen den Schritt in die Gegenwart – thematisch topaktuell, gesellschaftskritisch und dennoch mit der gewohnten Prise Humor und Ironie. Schwingt das Tanzbein, reißt die Met-Hörner in die Höhe und ölt eure Stimme. VOGELFREY, wir sind dabei!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/vogelfrey/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8FVp4nbv35Y",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"vogelfrey_26_b.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/vogelfrey_26_b.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36147}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4518,uri:"https://www.vogelfrey.net/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4519,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Vogelfrey/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4520,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/vogelfrey_official/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"3pyjoONcLKvzpSCtk3zAkh",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/a/3/csm_vogelfrey_26_b_0c6f4b5859.jpg",uid:1635},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Norwegen",shortNameDe:"Norwegen",shortNameEn:"Norway",uid:158}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Vreid",uid:781}],end:"1722633300",festival:null,festivalday:{end:"1722654000",start:"1722578400",title:"Friday",uid:21},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1722629700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:'"30 Years of Sognametal"',uid:1578},{artists:[{title:"Vreid",uid:781}],end:"1785500100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785546000",start:"1785477600",title:"Friday",uid:36},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"768",subtitle:"",title:"Harder",uid:5},start:"1785497400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2700}],pathSegment:"vreid",title:"Vreid",uid:781},biography:`<p>From&nbsp;the frostbitten depths&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sogn&nbsp;og&nbsp;Fjordane, Vreid&nbsp;emerges — a continuation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Windir’s&nbsp;legacy&nbsp;after&nbsp;the fall of Terje “Valfar” Bakken, now&nbsp;carried&nbsp;forward&nbsp;by&nbsp;Jarle&nbsp;Kvåle (Hvall).</p>\r
<p>Rooted in Black Metal&nbsp;yet&nbsp;deviating&nbsp;with&nbsp;intent, Vreid&nbsp;fuses&nbsp;tremolo-driven&nbsp;riffing, mid-tempo groove structures, and militaristic&nbsp;rhythmic&nbsp;patterns. Their&nbsp;sound&nbsp;trades&nbsp;raw&nbsp;chaos&nbsp;for&nbsp;precision—layered&nbsp;guitars, stark harmonic&nbsp;shifts, and an atmosphere&nbsp;shaped&nbsp;as&nbsp;much&nbsp;by&nbsp;Norwegian&nbsp;history&nbsp;as&nbsp;by&nbsp;distortion.</p>\r
<p>No&nbsp;nostalgia. Just evolution&nbsp;through&nbsp;steel, discipline, and cold&nbsp;resolve.</p>\r
<p>Vreid&nbsp;operates&nbsp;beyond&nbsp;trend&nbsp;cycle: more&nbsp;campaign&nbsp;than band, more&nbsp;doctrine&nbsp;than&nbsp;noise.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p>Aus den frostgezeichneten Tiefen von Sogn&nbsp;og&nbsp;Fjordane erhebt sich Vreid — als Fortführung des Erbes von Windir nach dem Verlust von Terje “Valfar” Bakken, weitergetragen von Jarle&nbsp;Kvåle (Hvall).</p>\r
<p>Im Black Metal verwurzelt, aber bewusst erweitert, verbindet Vreid&nbsp;tremolobasierte Riffs mit Midtempo-Grooves und marschartigen Rhythmen. Ihr Sound ersetzt rohes Chaos durch Präzision—geschichtete Gitarren, markante Harmoniewechsel und eine Atmosphäre, geprägt von norwegischer Geschichte und klirrender Kälte.</p>\r
<p>Keine Nostalgie. Nur Evolution aus Stahl, Disziplin und kalter Entschlossenheit.</p>\r
<p>Vreid steht außerhalb von Trends: mehr Feldzug als Band, mehr Doktrin als Noise.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/vreid/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gc0ZVZrL6G8",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"vreid_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/vreid_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36696}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4712,uri:"https://www.vreid.no"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4713,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/vreidofficial/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4714,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/vreidofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"2KvwC4Kmp2U8XnKr5Yr1hm",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/8/0/csm_vreid_26_f92e6e9af1.jpg",uid:1702},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1753615200",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753664400",start:"1753596000",title:"Sunday",uid:30},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1753614000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Beergarden",uid:2283},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1753611600",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753664400",start:"1753596000",title:"Sunday",uid:30},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1753610400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"Beergarden",uid:2290},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1753872300",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1753923600",start:"1753855200",title:"Wednesday",uid:24},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1753869600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2386},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1754131500",festival:{title:"WOA 2025",uid:9},festivalday:{end:"1754182800",start:"1754114400",title:"Saturday",uid:27},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1754128800",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2533},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1785321900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785319200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2634},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1785581100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785578400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2775},{artists:[{title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212}],end:"1785064800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785114000",start:"1785045600",title:"Sunday",uid:31},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785063600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2792}],pathSegment:"wacken-firefighters",title:"Wacken Firefighters",uid:212},biography:"<p>They belong to Wacken like the patch on the jacket, like the Landgasthof into the village, like the hose to the fire engine. The WACKEN FIREFIGHTERS are back on the Holy Ground again this year to continue their 20-year festival tradition ‘Metal meets Brass’. The marching band of the Freiwillige Feuerwehr Wacken has a stunning setlist from Egerländer polkas and marches to Rock and Metal sounds. When the conductor raises his baton, we'll raise our horns!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Sie gehören nach Wacken wie der Patch auf die Kutte, wie der Landgasthof in die Ortsmitte, wie der Schlauch zum Feuerwehrauto. Die WACKEN FIREFIGHTERS sind auch dieses Jahr wieder auf dem Holy Ground, um ganz nach dem Motto „Metal meets Brass“ ihre über 20-jährige Festivaltradition zu pflegen. Der Musikzug der Freiwilligen Feuerwehr Wacken hat wieder eine umfassende Setlist in petto – von Egerländer Polkas, über Märsche bis zu Rock und Metal-Klängen. Wenn der Dirigent seinen Taktstock hebt, reißen wir die Pommesgabel in die Höhe!</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/wacken-firefighters/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kyTJfGlBHJo",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"wacken_firefighters_25.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2025/wacken_firefighters_25.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36400}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4663,uri:"https://www.wacken-firefighters.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4664,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/MZFF.Wacken.Firefighters"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4665,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/wackenfirefighters/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/0/6/csm_wacken_firefighters_25_5f6d39317e.jpg",uid:1685},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Belgien",shortNameDe:"Belgien",shortNameEn:"Belgium",uid:20}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Witchlords",uid:1262}],end:"1785340200",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785373200",start:"1785304800",title:"Wednesday",uid:34},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"1536",subtitle:"",title:"W:E:T Stage",uid:8},start:"1785339000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"MB Belgium",uid:2616}],pathSegment:"witchlords",title:"Witchlords",uid:1262},biography:`<p class="text-justify">Witchlords is a four-piece power metal band from Belgium, forged in 2019 when battle-brothers Kristof Dedene (vocals, guitar) and Thomas Lambeir (drums) bonded over a shared love of tabletop wargaming and classic metal. Their peaceful alliance turned berserk with debut album Demons in the Dark — a record that nods to the early days of Helloween, Blind Guardian, and Primal Fear. Carl Van Poyer (bass) and Pieter Moris (guitar) later joined to complete the line-up.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Recommended for fans of Helloween, Gamma Ray, Blind Guardian, Primal Fear, Iron Maiden, Judas Priest, Visigoth, Eternal Champion, HeroQuest, Warhammer, Dungeons &amp; Dragons — and other awesome power metal bands and tabletop games. With a passion for both, Witchlords takes you down into the dungeons of your soul, to face the demons that lurk within.</p>`,biographyDe:`<p class="text-justify">Witchlords ist eine vierköpfige Power-Metal-Band aus Belgien, geschmiedet 2019, als die Kampfbrüder Kristof Dedene (Gesang, Gitarre) und Thomas Lambeir (Schlagzeug) ihre gemeinsame Liebe zu Tabletop-Wargaming und klassischem Metal entdeckten. Aus ihrem friedlichen Bund wurde Berserkerwut: das Debütalbum Demons in the Dark, eine Verbeugung vor den frühen Tagen von Helloween, Blind Guardian und Primal Fear. Später stießen Carl Van Poyer (Bass) und Pieter Moris (Gitarre) dazu und komplettierten das Line-up.</p>\r
<p class="text-justify">Empfohlen für Fans von Helloween, Gamma Ray, Blind Guardian, Primal Fear, Iron Maiden, Judas Priest, Visigoth, Eternal Champion, HeroQuest, Warhammer, Dungeons &amp; Dragons – und allen anderen großartigen Power-Metal-Bands und Tabletop-Spielen. Mit ihrer Leidenschaft für beides führen Witchlords ihre Hörer hinab in die Verliese der eigenen Seele, um sich den Dämonen zu stellen, die dort lauern.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/witchlords/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZKb91ESx7zo",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"witchlords_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/witchlords_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37102}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4808,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/witchlords"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4809,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/Witchlords"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"0Xpf14NWhbA0cnah3Y4aDp",subtitle:"Metal Battle Belgium",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/9/csm_witchlords_26_c2f8cf6e6c.jpg",uid:1743},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Wüstenberg",uid:1216}],end:"1785408300",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785405600",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2680}],pathSegment:"wuestenberg",title:"Wüstenberg",uid:1216},biography:"<p>FRANZ WÜSTENBERG, who has already enjoyed a decade of success as frontman for The O'Reillys and the Paddyhats, has finally released his eagerly awaited debut album ‘The King's Gambit’. Wüstenberg did not promise too much when he pondered his new beginning in an old 19th-century stone house. Authentic Folk Rock with depth and soulfulness, with loud e-guitars, dreamy mandolin and much more. Stage free for the likeable Northern Lights and his six-piece band.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>FRANZ WÜSTENBERG, welcher bereits erfolgreich eine Dekade als Frontmann bei The O’Reillys and the Paddyhats sang, hat mit „The King’s Gambit“ endlich sein heiß ersehntes Debütalbum von den Ketten gelassen. Wüstenberg versprach nicht zu viel, als er in einem alten Bruchsteinhaus aus dem 19. Jahrhundert über seinen Neubeginn sinnierte. Authentischer Folk Rock mit Tiefgang und Lebensfreude, mit lauter E-Gitarre, verträumter Mandoline und vielem mehr. Bühne frei für das sympathische Nordlicht und seine sechsköpfige Band.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/wuestenberg/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wdCiLBRAkzs",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"wuestenberg_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/wuestenberg_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36401}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4666,uri:"https://www.wuestenberg-music.com/de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4667,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/wuestenbergmusic"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4668,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/wuestenberg_music/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"6YQBDUiQeOg2Pp4XzGmtbm",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/1/csm_wuestenberg_26_7a5a7ede3d.jpg",uid:1686},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Großbritannien",shortNameDe:"Großbritannien",shortNameEn:"United Kingdom",uid:74}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Wytch Hazel",uid:1155}],end:"1785431700",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785429000",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2691}],pathSegment:"wytch-hazel",title:"Wytch Hazel",uid:1155},biography:"<p>The fighters&nbsp;of&nbsp;the light gather&nbsp;under&nbsp;the&nbsp;banner&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wytch Hazel and arrive in Wacken armed&nbsp;with&nbsp;twin&nbsp;lead&nbsp;guitars&nbsp;worthy&nbsp;of Iron Maiden and a knack for&nbsp;unforgettable&nbsp;hooks. The British band proudly&nbsp;carries&nbsp;the&nbsp;torch&nbsp;of&nbsp;the NWOBHM, riffing&nbsp;their&nbsp;way&nbsp;through&nbsp;the&nbsp;lands&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;past 15 years. With their&nbsp;latest&nbsp;album “V: Lamentations,” they’ve&nbsp;cemented&nbsp;their&nbsp;reputation&nbsp;as a true&nbsp;hit&nbsp;machine — now&nbsp;ready&nbsp;to&nbsp;storm&nbsp;the Holy Ground under&nbsp;the&nbsp;banner&nbsp;of light.</p>",biographyDe:`<p>Die Kämpfer des Lichts haben sich unter dem Banner Wytch Hazel vereinigt und kommen mit zweistimmigen Lead Gitarren a la Iron Maiden und einer Hitgarantie nach Wacken, um uns von all dem Bösen zu befreien.</p>\r
<p>Die britischen Barden stehen ganz in der Tradition der NWOBHM und riffen sich seit 15 Jahren durch die Landen. Mit ihrem aktuellen Album V: Lamentations zementieren sie ihren Ruf als Hitmaschine und sind nun bereit unter dem Banner des Lichts den Holy Ground zu stürmen.</p>`,detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/wytch-hazel/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=79FMltWsgX0",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"Wytch_Hazel-WOA26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/Wytch_Hazel-WOA26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:34829}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4669,uri:"https://wytchhazel.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4308,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/wytchhazel/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4309,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/wytchhazel/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"4EwBNQKEzshM5Yxs6cyzpt",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/2/5/csm_Wytch_Hazel-WOA26_3a3c5566d4.jpg",uid:1573},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweiz",shortNameDe:"Schweiz",shortNameEn:"Switzerland",uid:41}],events:[{artists:[{title:"xoxo",uid:1251}],end:"1785182400",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785200400",start:"1785132000",title:"Monday",uid:32},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"256",subtitle:"powered by LGH Wacken",title:"LGH Clubstage",uid:21},start:"1785179700",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2823}],pathSegment:"xoxo",title:"xoxo",uid:1251},biography:"<p>Don’t let the innocent name fool you - there are no sweet kisses hidden here, just what might be the most colorful beatdown in Swiss Metal history. Formed in Zurich in 2023 when four cute but fiercely angry people crossed paths, XOXO live by the motto “Cute, Queer and Violent.” The quintet blasts a high-octane mix of Hardcore, Metalcore, and Deathcore straight at you, topped off with a thick layer of pink glitter. With over 40 international shows under their belt and brand-new album material in tow, the Zurich crew is rolling into the Landgasthof to completely tear up the mosh pit!</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Hinter diesem unschuldigen Namen verstecken sich keine Küsschen, sondern die wohl bunteste Abreibung der Schweizer Metalgeschichte. Gegründet 2023 in Zürich, als fünf süße, aber verdammt wütende Menschen zufällig aufeinanderprallten, haben sich XOXO dem Motto „Cute, Queer and Violent“ verschrieben. Das Quartett ballert euch einen hochexplosiven Mix aus Hardcore, Metalcore und Deathcore um die Ohren, der kurzerhand mit einer dicken Schicht pinkem Glitzer überstreut wurde. Nach über 40 internationalen Shows auf dem Tacho und mit brandneuem Album-Material im Gepäck, rücken die Zürcher im Landgasthof an, um die Moshpits dieser Welt ordentlich aufzumischen.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/xoxo/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"xoxo_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/xoxo_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:37049}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4772,uri:"https://xoxoviolence.bandcamp.com/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4773,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/xoxo.vlnce/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"1aIubMSIRI3qYQSSqyctVu",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/d/1/csm_xoxo_26_a6bd6336bb.jpg",uid:1730},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Year of the Goat",uid:1217}],end:"1785448800",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2560",subtitle:"",title:"Wasteland Stage",uid:11},start:"1785445200",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2694}],pathSegment:"year-of-the-goat",title:"Year of the Goat",uid:1217},biography:"<p>Year Of The Goat sound like an occult rock band hosting a midnight sermon for heavy rock. Big melodies, dark vibes and plenty of 70s magic. When the Swedes hit the stage it starts to feel like a ritual… just with more guitars and fewer candles.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Year Of The Goat klingen ein bisschen so, als würde eine okkulte Rockband mitten in der Nacht eine Messe für Heavy Rock lesen. Große Melodien, dunkle Vibes und ordentlich 70er-Magie. Wenn die Schweden spielen, wird die Bühne zum Pilgerort, nur ohne Kerzen und mit einer Menge mehr Gitarren</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/year-of-the-goat/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3utyUuudA30",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!1,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"year_of_the_goat_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/year_of_the_goat_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36402}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4670,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/yearofthegoat/"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4671,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/yearofthegoatofficial/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"56sorIyBAwXaDPifwqtCub",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/4/e/csm_year_of_the_goat_26_f271ba4dd9.jpg",uid:1687},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Schweden",shortNameDe:"Schweden",shortNameEn:"Sweden",uid:186}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Yngwie Malmsteen",uid:1168}],end:"1785429900",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785459600",start:"1785391200",title:"Thursday",uid:35},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"512",subtitle:"",title:"Faster",uid:4},start:"1785425400",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2649}],pathSegment:"yngwie-malmsteen",title:"Yngwie Malmsteen",uid:1168},biography:"<p>Yngwie isn’t a guitarist – he’s a storm in a tuxedo.<br />His solos are operas, his arpeggios a religious rite.<br />Since <i>“Rising Force”</i> he’s burned scales for slowing him down.<br />He doesn’t play – he duels with physics.<br />Vain? Absolutely. But genius was never humble- and does not need to: Yngwie will prove this by delivering a Greatest Hits special show.&nbsp;<br />When his strings ignite, the world shatters beautifully.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Yngwie ist kein Gitarrist – er ist ein Sturm im Smoking.<br />Seine Soli sind Opern, seine Arpeggios religiöse Erfahrung.<br />Seit <i>“Rising Force”</i> brennt er die Tonleitern nieder, weil sie ihn bremsen.<br />Er spielt nicht, er duelliert sich mit der Physik.<br />Eitel? Sicher. Aber Genie war nie bescheiden – das beweist er in dem er uns bei dieser Show ein Greatest Hits Set liefert. Wer hat&nbsp; - der kann!Wenn seine Saiten glühen, zerplatz der der Rest der Welt in 1000 glitzernde Scherben.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/yngwie-malmsteen/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2e-n9-b7qAQ",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"yngwie_malmsteen_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/yngwie_malmsteen_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:35129}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4383,uri:"https://www.yngwiemalmsteen.com"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Facebook",uid:1},uid:4384,uri:"https://www.facebook.com/officialyngwiemalmsteen"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4385,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/yngwiemalmsteen_official"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Youtube",uid:6},uid:4386,uri:"https://www.youtube.com/@officialyngwiemalmsteen622"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"5DpSoH5zCXNRqYai7pmcGG",spotifyartist:"",subtitle:"Greatest Hits Set",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/9/0/csm_yngwie_malmsteen_26_451945c4f5.jpg",uid:1597},{artist:{country:[{nameLocalized:"Deutschland",shortNameDe:"Deutschland",shortNameEn:"Germany",uid:54}],events:[{artists:[{title:"Zeltinger Band",uid:1220}],end:"1785599100",festival:{title:"WOA 2026",uid:10},festivalday:{end:"1785632400",start:"1785564000",title:"Saturday",uid:37},images:null,media:null,performance:{title:"Concert",uid:1},stage:{description:"",latitude:"",longitude:"",pid:167,sorting:"2304",subtitle:"",title:"Wackinger Stage",uid:10},start:"1785595500",subtitle:"",sysLanguageUid:"-1",teaser:"",title:"",uid:2778}],pathSegment:"zeltinger-band",title:"Zeltinger Band",uid:1220},biography:"<p>A breeze&nbsp;from Cologne will sweep&nbsp;across&nbsp;the Holy Ground when&nbsp;the&nbsp;legendary Zeltinger Band travels&nbsp;north&nbsp;from Colonia to Wacken. The group&nbsp;around&nbsp;frontman Jürgen Zeltinger has&nbsp;long&nbsp;been&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;Cologne’s&nbsp;cultural DNA — and has&nbsp;been&nbsp;going strong for&nbsp;almost 50 years. Lines like “Ich poliere Kritikern die Fressen, für die Band mach’ ich das Abendessen” have&nbsp;etched&nbsp;the&nbsp;band&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;collective&nbsp;memory&nbsp;of&nbsp;&nbsp;fans. Now&nbsp;they’re&nbsp;adding&nbsp;another&nbsp;chapter&nbsp;to&nbsp;their&nbsp;long&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;stories — right&nbsp;here on the Holy Ground.</p>",biographyDe:"<p>Ein bisschen Kölle weht über den Holy Ground, wenn die legendäre Zeltinger Band sich aufmacht den langen Weg aus Colonia in den hohen Norden zurückzulegen. Die Truppe um Frontmann Jürgen Zeltinger gehört zum kölschen Kulturgut und mittlerweile auch schon fast 50 Lenzen auf dem Buckel. Mit Textzeilen wie „ich poliere Kritikern die Fressen, für die Band mach' ich das Abendessen“ hat sich die Zeltinger Band ins kollektive jecke Gedächtnis eingebrannt. Nun wird die Zeltinger Band den Holy Ground beehren. Ein weiteres Kapitel in der an Anekdoten nicht armen Geschichte dieser Kombo.</p>",detailLink:"/de/line-up/bands/band/zeltinger-band/",externalMediaRatio:"16by9",externalMediaSource:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fww9y0cOW74",extraDay:!1,festival:{runningOrderActive:!0,uid:10},firsttime:!0,images:[{originalResource:{alternative:"",description:"",name:"zeltinger_26.jpg",publicUrl:"/fileadmin/user_upload/bandimages/bands2026/zeltinger_26.jpg",title:"",type:2,uid:36412}}],networkuri:[{socialnetwork:{title:"Homepage",uid:8},uid:4677,uri:"http://www.zeltinger-band.de"},{socialnetwork:{title:"Instagram",uid:5},uid:4678,uri:"https://www.instagram.com/zeltingerband/"}],performance:[{title:"Concert",uid:1}],spotifyalbum:"",spotifyartist:"12cJGU9ktOShfMV5scsdHM",subtitle:"",thumbnail:"/fileadmin/_processed_/1/0/csm_zeltinger_26_74420c1905.jpg",uid:1690}];export{e as default};
